ulky%20for%20that%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20Luna%20is%20thin%20enough%20for%20a%20road%20trip.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22best%20weighted%20blanket%202022%20luna%20blanket%20budget%20affordable%20cheap%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62a898a16053710019ea2359%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20affordable%20Luna%20Weighted%20Blanket%20is%20ideal%20for%20people%20new%20to%20weighted%20blankets.%3Cp%3EJen%20Gushue%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20our%20scale%2C%20the%20blanket%20was%20a%20true%2015%20pounds%2C%20but%20that%20weight%20was%20dispersed%20over%20a%20queen-size%20surface%20area%2C%20making%20it%20feel%20lighter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20one%20of%20the%20most%20straightforward%20blankets%20to%20clean.%20The%20entire%20thing%20fits%20into%20our%20compact%20washer-dryer%20and%20was%20fully%20dry%20within%20one%20cycle%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20got%20softer%20after%20just%20one%20wash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20cooling%5C%22%3EBest%20cooling%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20sleep%20warm%20or%20simply%20want%20a%20weighted%20blanket%20option%20that%20doesn't%20contribute%20to%20your%20overheating%2C%20a%20weighted%20blanket%20that%20emphasizes%20breathable%20materials%20will%20become%20your%20new%20favorite.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Gravity%20Cooling%20Blanket%20has%20a%20removable%20100%25%20lyocell%20(Eucalyptus)%20cover%20that%20has%20a%20silky%2C%20soft%2C%20cool-to-the-touch%20feel%2C%20is%20undeniably%20breathable%20andnaturally%20moisture-wicking.%20A%20zipper%20makes%20it%20easy%20to%20remove%20for%20washing%2C%20and%20buttons%20help%20hold%20the%20blanket%20in%20place%20to%20prevent%20bunching.%20The%20microscopic%20glass%20beads%20are%20sewn%20in%20a%20gridded%20design%20for%20even%20weight%20distribution.%20The%20glass%20beads%2C%20however%2C%20make%20a%20subtle%20bean%20bag%20sound%20as%20you%20move%20around%20the%20blanket.%C2%A0%20It's%20also%20worth%20noting%20that%20the%20silky%20fabric%20cover%20can%20slide%20off%20the%20bed%20if%20the%20blanket%20is%20shifted%20around%20too%20much%20due%20to%20the%20weight%20of%20the%20blanket.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELying%20underneath%20is%20immediately%20calming%2C%20and%20we%20didn't%20have%20any%20issues%20overheating%3B%20though%20the%20design%20is%20more%20or%20less%20cool%20to%20the%20touch%20and%20refreshing%20as%20opposed%20to%20actively%20cooling.%20The%20moisture-wicking%20keeps%20sweat%20at%20bay%2C%20but%20we%20want%20to%20manage%20the%20expectation%20that%20the%20blanket%20will%20cool%20you%20down.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gravity%20blanket%20on%20a%20bed%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65dfa1706080194819fb04e8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22540%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Gravity%20Cooling%20Blanket%20is%20aesthetically%20pleasing%20and%20does%20an%20excellent%20job%20of%20keeping%20you%20cool.%3Cp%3EGravity%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20comes%20in%20six%20colors.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20forest%20green%20we%20tried%20is%20richly%20pigmented%20and%20also%20looks%20good%20when%20out%20on%20display.%20It's%20available%20in%20a%20single-person%2048%26quot%3B%20x%2072%26quot%3B%C2%A0%20size%20of%2015%20and%2020%20pounds%20or%20a%20super-heavy%2035-pound%20full%2Fqueen%20size.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20washing%2C%20the%20cover%20is%20secured%20with%20a%20hidden%20zipper%20and%20interior%20snaps%20that%20can%20be%20easily%20removed%20and%20tossed%20in%20the%20wash.%20The%20weighted%20inner%2C%20however%2C%20should%20be%20hand-washed%20and%20left%20to%20air%20fry.%20We%20haven't%20noticed%20any%20signs%20of%20wear%20since%20washing%2C%20but%20some%20reviewers%20mentioned%20pilling.%20Despite%20having%20a%20duvet%20cover%20design%2C%20Gravity%20does%20not%20currently%20offer%20replacement%20covers%20to%20swap%20fabrics%20or%20colors.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20our%20full%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fgravity-cooling-weighted-blanket-review%5C%22%3EGravity%20Cooling%20Weighted%20Blanket%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20comforter%5C%22%3EBest%20comforter%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20sleep%20under%20a%20stack%20of%20blankets%20or%20compromise%20your%20bedroom's%20look%2C%20you'll%20want%20a%20weighted%20comforter%2C%20and%20Brooklinenmakes%20the%20best%20one%20we%20tried.%20It%20looks%20and%20feels%20like%20a%20traditional%20plush%20comforter%20but%20with%20an%20extra%2020%20pounds%20of%20weight%20integrated%20with%20tiny%20glass%20beads.%20The%20blanket%20is%20made%20of%20400-thread-count%20cotton%20sateen%2C%20so%20it's%20soft%20enough%20to%20throw%20on%20your%20bed%20without%20a%20duvet%20cover.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20being%20said%2C%20we%20recommend%20adding%20a%20duvet%20cover%20%E2%80%94%20corner%20loops%20make%20it%20easy%20to%20tie%20on%20%E2%80%94%20because%20the%20blanket%20is%20dry-cleaning%20only%2C%20which%20could%20run%20you%20anywhere%20from%20%2420%20to%20%2450%2C%20depending%20on%20where%20you%20live.%20Brooklinen%20offers%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiipgf_112818_best-weighted-blankets-20%26h%3Df8726cf67b51ea419b5dd72847f4a49ee2ae35988ff68c2a00d07cdadb536cb8%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f41fbb%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fbest-weighted-blanket%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.brooklinen.com%252Fcollections%252Fduvet-covers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eduvet%20covers%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20same%20fabrications%20as%20their%20popular%20sheets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221397%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20pretends%2