%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fhomesmart-king-sized-weighted-blanket-product-review%5C%22%3EHomeSmart%20King-Size%20Weighted%20Blanket%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20heated%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20heated%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWeighted%20blankets%20are%20great%20for%20that%20hygge%20experience%2C%20but%20when%20you%20add%20heat%2C%20you%20take%20the%20coziness%20to%20a%20whole%20new%20level.%20The%20brand%20that%20makes%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-electric-blanket%5C%22%3Ebest%20electric%20blanket%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20our%20guide%20also%20makes%20the%20best%20heated%20weighted%20blanket.%20The%20Pure%20Enrichment%20WeightedWarmth%20Weighted%20Throw%20Blanket%20was%20the%20one%20we%20kept%20reaching%20for%20on%20cold%20winter%20nights.%20In%20fact%2C%20reporter%20James%20Brains's%20wife%20loved%20this%20weighted%20heated%20blanket%20so%20much%20she%20didn't%20want%20to%20give%20it%20back%20to%20him%20to%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%2052%20inches%20by%2060%20inches%2C%20it's%20a%20little%20bit%20too%20small%20to%20cover%20most%20people%20completely%2C%20but%20it%20got%20the%20job%20done%20while%20lounging%20and%20watching%20Ted%20Lasso.%20As%20an%20antsy%20individual%20who%20likes%20to%20move%20around%2C%20the%20Pure%20Enrichment%20heated%20weighted%20blanket%20kept%20Brains%20still%20while%20nestled%20underneath.%20The%20micromink%20and%20sherpa%20sides%20were%20both%20comfortable%2C%20though%20we%20prefer%20the%20sherpa%20side's%20plush%20comfort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Pure%20Enrichment%20WeightedWarmth%20blanket%20has%20four%20heat%20settings%3A%20warm%2C%20low%2C%20medium%2C%20and%20high%2C%20my%20favorite%20setting%20reaching%20105%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%20quickly.%20The%209-foot%20cord%20is%20long%20enough%20to%20reach%20electrical%20outlets%20without%20needing%20an%20extension%20cord%20or%20sacrificing%20comfort.%20After%20two%20hours%2C%20the%20blanket%20automatically%20shuts%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221520%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20smiles%20while%20lounging%20under%20the%20Pure%20Enrichment%20WeightedWarmth%20weighted%20blanket%20on%20a%20bed%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65df9b2390413ab8e1d7a49b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221140%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20may%20have%20to%20buy%20a%20second%20Pure%20Enrichment%20WeightedWarmth%20weighted%20blanket%20because%20my%20wife%20and%20I%20both%20loved%20the%20combination%20of%20heat%20and%20heft.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20relies%20on%20glass%20beads%20for%20its%20weight%20and%20tips%20the%20scales%20at%2013%20pounds%2C%20which%20we%20found%20was%20sufficient%20for%20its%20size.%20We%20also%20like%20the%20five-year%20warranty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20negative%20is%20the%20care%20instructions%2C%20which%20are%20so%20long%20and%20detailed%20that%20they%20require%20a%206-inch-by-6-inch%20explainer%20sown%20into%20the%20blanket.%20For%20cleaning%20details%2C%20see%20the%20Specifics%20box%20above.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20eco-friendly%5C%22%3EBest%20eco-friendly%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERelax%20soundly%20knowing%20you're%20cuddled%20up%20with%20a%20sustainably%20made%20blanket%20of%20all-natural%20materials%2C%20with%20no%20polyester%20in%20sight.%20The%20Baloo%20Weighted%20Comforter%20is%20OEKO-TEX%C2%AE%20certified%20with%20a%20cotton%20shell%20filled%20with%20lead-free%20glass%20beads%20for%20weight.%20Baloo%20aims%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bcarbon%20neutral%20and%20ocean%20positive%26quot%3B%20by%20partnering%20with%20Sustainable%20Surf%20to%20support%20reforestation%20projects.%20It%20backs%20the%20comforter%20with%20a%20lifetime%20warranty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20comforter%20is%20just%20outstanding%20to%20sleep%20under.%20We%20tested%20the%20full%2Fqueen%20in%2020%20pounds%2C%20which%20weighed%20closer%20to%2022%20pounds.%20At%2084%20inches%20by%2081%20inches%20by%20our%20measure%2C%20it%20was%20large%20enough%20to%20cover%20our%206-foot-tall%20tester%20completely.%20While%20sleeping%20with%20the%20Baloo%20Weighted%20Comforter%2C%20I%20experienced%20excellent%20sleep%20quality%2C%20with%20minimal%20restless%20moments.%20He%20reported%20that%20the%20comforter%20kept%20him%20cool%20through%20the%20night%2C%20despite%20a%20tendency%20to%20overheat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221520%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Baloo%20Weighted%20Comforter%20is%20spread%20out%20on%20a%20queen-sized%20mattress.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65df9c31ce7f1785b2e4b973%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221140%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Baloo%20Weighted%20Comforter%20is%20made%20of%20eco-friendly%20materials%20and%20is%20virtually%20indistinguishable%20from%20a%20nonweighted%20blanket.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Baloo%20Weighted%20Comforter%20features%20loops%20for%20a%20duvet%20cover.%20Or%2C%20you%20can%20forego%20the%20cover%20and%20just%20wash%20the%20entire%20blanket%20when%20it%20gets%20dirty.%20We%20didn't%20notice%20any%20degradation%20in%20the%20blanket%20after%20washing%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20pricey%2C%20we%20think%20the%20Baloo%20comforter%20is%20an%20excellent%20option%2C%20considering%20its%20eco-friendly%20credentials.%20We%20just%20wish%20it%20was%20available%20in%20more%20colors.%20Baloo%2C%20however%2C%20does%20offer%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiipgf_112818_best-weighted-blankets-20%26h%3D97d75f732dbd3acb42649ff5ddf372991925f84914b78416984f5cb9bb8a40d9%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f41fbb%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fbest-weighted-blanket%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fbalooliving.com%252Fproducts%252Fweighted-blanket%253Fvariant%253D44422816432347%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblanket-sized%20version%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20too.%20Pay%20attention%20to%20measurements%2C%20though%2C%20as%20while%20the%20blanket%20version%20is%20available%20in%20full%2Fqueen%20and%20king%20sizes%2C%20these%20models%20simply%20cover%20the%20top%20of%20the%20bed%20instead%20of%20draping%20like%20a%20comforter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20to%20look%20for%5C%22%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20weighted%20blanket%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221492%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20collection%20of%20weighted%20blankets%20together.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fa5c15df7d1cb0019e3a584%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221119%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Gravity%20Cooling%2C%20Helix%2C%20and%20Brooklyn%20Bedding%20weighted%20blankets%20were%20among%20the%20others%20we%20tested.%3Cp%3EJen%20Gushue%2FAlyssa%20Powell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20the%20main%20factors%20to%20consider%20when%20shopping%20for%20a%20weighted%20blanket%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeight%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESelect%20a%20blanket%20that's%20roughly%2010%25%20of%20your%20body%20weight.%20You%20should%20be%20able%20to%20move%20freely%20under%20the%20blanket%20if%20you%20can't%2C%20choose%20a%20lighter%20weight.%20You'll%20likely%20want%20something%20heavier%20if%20you%20share%20a%20weighted%20blanket%20with%20a%20partner.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESize%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIf%20you're%20sharing%20a%20blanket%20with%20a%20partner%20with%20a%20similar%20body%20weight%2C%20you'll%20want%20a%20weighted%20blanket%20that%20covers%20your%20entire%20bed.%20If%20you%20and%20your%20partner%20are%20very%20different%20weights%2C%20consider%20two%20smaller%20separate%20blankets%20in%20a%20throw%20or%20twin%20size.%20Remember%20that%20a%2015-pound%20throw%20blanket%20feels%20much%20heavier%20than%20a%2015-pound%20comforter%20since%20a%20larger%20blanket%20distributes%20its%20weight%20over%20a%20larger%20surface%20area.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaterial%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWeighted%20blankets%20are%20available%20in%20various%20materials%2C%20from%20cotton%20and%20Tencel%20to%20microfiber%20or%20polyester.%20Depending%20on%20whether%20you%20want%20a%20blanket%20with%20a%20more%20breathable%20design%20or%20something%20cozier%2C%20consider%20the%20outer%20fabric.%20Some%20comforter-sized%20designs%20are%20also%20designed%20to%20be%20used%20with%20duvet%20covers%20or%20may%20even%20come%20with%20their%20own%2C%20in%20which%20case%2C%20designs%20with%20loops%20will%20make%20it%20easy%20to%20add%20a%20cover%20of%20your%20choice.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFill%20type%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBesides%20considering%20weight%2C%20size%2C%20and%20outer%20material%2C%20the%20inner%20fill%20is%20important.%20Weighted%20blankets%20rely%20on%20micro%20glass%20beads%2C%20plastic%20pellets%2C%20or%20steel%20shot%20beads%2C%20or%2C%20like%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Bearaby's%20knit%20design%2C%20the%20weight%20of%20its%20fabric.%20We%20don't%20prefer%20one%20fill%20over%20another%20regarding%20function%2C%20but%20steel%20and%20glass%20are%20generally%20more%20sustainable%20than%20plastic.%20Ideally%2C%20the%20fill%20shouldn't%20shift%20too%20much%20within%20the%20blanket%20or%20create%20a%20lot%20of%20noise%20when%20shifting%20under%20the%20blanket.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20test%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20test%20weighted%20blankets%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221344%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Four%20weighted%20blankets%20folded%20up.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6182e65023745d001824ea24%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221008%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOur%20team%20has%20tested%20dozens%20of%20weighted%20blankets%20in%20our%20search%20for%20the%20best.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAside%20from%20the%20general%20coziness%20and%20comfort%20provided%20by%20each%20weighted%20blanket%2C%20we%20also%20evaluated%20material%20quality%2C%20value%2C%20weight%20options%2C%20and%20aesthetics.%20For%20example%2C%20a%20blanket%20that%20came%20in%20more%20color%20and%20weight%20options%20beat%20out%20a%20blanket%20of%20equal%20quality%20that%20came%20in%20fewer%20options.%20We%20also%20considered%20return%20policies%2C%20sleep%20trials%2C%20and%20how%20easy%20these%20blankets%20were%20to%20clean.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20following%20are%20three%20tests%20we%20ran%20each%20blanket%20through%20to%20assess%20general%20user%20experience%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESleep%20test%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20One%20of%20us%20slept%20with%20each%20weighted%20blanket%20for%20at%20least%20three%20consecutive%20nights.%20We%20noted%20how%20well%20we%20slept%20overall%20and%20how%20the%20blanket%20regulated%20our%20sleep%20temperature.%20We%20also%20assessed%20how%20well%20the%20blanket%20stayed%20in%20place%20and%20how%20easy%20it%20was%20to%20adjust%20while%20lying%20under%20it.%20This%20test%20also%20included%20making%20the%20bed%20daily%20(hauling%20a%20weighted%20blanket%20is%20harder%20than%20it%20looks).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWash%20test%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20We%20washed%20every%20machine-washable%20weighted%20blanket%20or%20cover%20at%20least%20once%20to%20ensure%20they%20held%20up%20well%20and%20didn't%20shrink%2C%20shed%2C%20or%20otherwise%20show%20signs%20of%20wear.%20We%20noted%20if%20the%20added%20weight%20made%20them%20more%20challenging%20to%20haul%20into%20and%20out%20of%20the%20washing%20machine.%20We%20also%20discovered%20that%20one%20of%20the%20machine-washable%20blankets%20was%20so%20bulky%20it%20didn't%20fit%20into%20the%20washing%20machine.%20For%20those%20blankets%20that%20weren't%20machine-washable%2C%20we%20noted%20the%20care%20instructions%20and%20factored%20that%20into%20the%20cons%20of%20the%20blanket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeight%20test%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20We%20wanted%20to%20ensure%20each%20blanket%20was%20the%20advertised%20weight.%20We%20stepped%20on%20the%20scale%20with%20and%20without%20the%20blanket%20to%20get%20an%20accurate%20reading.%20The%20difference%20in%20weight%20gave%20us%20the%20blanket's%20weight.%20We%20then%20noted%20any%20discrepancies%20in%20the%20advertised%20weight%20versus%20the%20actual%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3EWeighted%20blanket%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhich%20weighted%20blanket%20is%20the%20best%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20hard%20for%20the%20one-size-fits-all%20approach%20because%20we're%20all%20just%20so%20unique%20and%20have%20different%20physiologies%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rebecca-robbins.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERebecca%20Robbins%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20sleep%20researcher%2C%20author%2C%20and%20instructor%20in%20medicine%20at%20Harvard%20Medical%20School.%20She%20suggests%20looking%20for%20brands%20with%20sleep%20trials%20or%20buyer-friendly%20return%20policies%20so%20you%20can%20test%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20often%20should%20I%20wash%20my%20weighted%20blanket%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EBrian%20Sansoni%2C%20Senior%20Vice%20President%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cleaninginstitute.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20American%20Cleaning%20Institute%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20recommends%20treating%20weighted%20blankets%20like%20any%20comforter%2C%20washing%20them%20once%20or%20twice%20a%20year%20if%20they%20have%20a%20cover.%20If%20they%20don't%20have%20a%20removable%20cover%2C%20clean%20the%20entire%20blanket%20roughly%20once%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAre%20weighted%20blankets%20good%20for%20anxiety%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20theory%2C%20the%20answer%20is%20yes.%20However%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.health.harvard.edu%2Fmind-and-mood%2Fanxiety-and-stress-weighing-heavily-at-night-a-new-blanket-might-help%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eno%20randomized%20clinical%20trials%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20speak%20to%20the%20efficacy%20of%20weighted%20blankets%20in%20treating%20anxiety%20since%20it%20would%20be%20obvious%20to%20participants%20whether%20or%20not%20they%20were%20using%20a%20weighted%20blanket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20theory%20is%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fmental-health%2Fweighted-blanket-benefits%5C%22%3Eweighted%20blankets%20help%20reduce%20some%20anxiety%20symptoms%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20like%20quickened%20breathing%20or%20heart%20rate%2C%20by%20easing%20your%20autonomic%20nervous%20system.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20overall%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20bearaby%20cotton%20napper%20folded%20on%20a%20made%20bed.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fa5bd45f7d1cb0019e3a563%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJen%20Gushue%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20weight%20of%20the%20Bearaby%20Napper%20comes%20entirely%20from%20the%20dense%20organic%20cotton%20strands%20hand-knit%20into%20one%20of%20the%20most%20aesthetically-minded%20weighted%20blankets%20we've%20seen.%20It's%20available%20in%20six%20colors%20and%20weight%20sizes%20ranging%20from%2010%20to%2025%20pounds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20hefty%20blanket.%20The%20blanket%20we%20tested%2C%20advertised%20as%20the%2015-pound%20version%2C%20actually%20tipped%20the%20scales%20at%2024%20pounds.%20We%20contacted%20the%20company%20to%20verify%20that%20they%20sent%20the%20correct%20item%2C%20and%20they%20assured%20us%20they%20did.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20necessarily%20bad%20that%20they're%20heavier%20than%20advertised%2C%20but%20it's%20something%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%20when%20you%20order.%C2%A0%20A%20blanket%20this%20heavy%20%E2%80%94%20and%20bulky%20%E2%80%94%20can%20be%20tough%20to%20shift%20around%2C%20and%20if%20it's%20going%20to%20live%20on%20your%20couch%2C%20it%20will%20take%20up%20quite%20a%20bit%20of%20space.%20We%20moved%20it%20to%20the%20bed.%20The%20blanket%20is%20designed%20for%20one%2C%20but%20we%20found%20it%20drapes%20nicely%20over%20two%20people.%20Bearaby%20also%20offers%20a%20six%20or%20eight-pound%20kid%20size%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiipgf_112818_best-weighted-blankets-20%26h%3Dbe2ef538fdf38fde696f646c9a63f92962899558b58c6c20f48842ccc9f87c61%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f41fbb%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fbest-weighted-blanket%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fbearaby.com%252Fproducts%252Fthe-nappling%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENappling%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20a%2030-pound%20design%20to%20fit%20queen%20and%20king%20sized%20beds%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiipgf_112818_best-weighted-blankets-20%26h%3De8a043be737121dc1c37d273da56a1402001822a48501fe1d748c3155ffefcca%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f41fbb%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fbest-weighted-blanket%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fbearaby.com%252Fproducts%252Fqueen-size-weighted-blanket%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHugger%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20open%20weave%20makes%20it%20prone%20to%20stretching%20if%20you%20need%20to%20pull%20it%20up.%20It%20hasn't%20become%20misshapen%20in%20any%20significant%20way%2C%20thankfully.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20quite%20a%20cooling%20blanket%20%E2%80%94%20Bearaby%20does%20offer%20one%20called%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.