s%20guide%20and%20ran%20our%20hands%20across%20each%20one%2C%20and%20the%20BlanQuil%20felt%20noticeably%20cooler%20than%20all%20the%20others.%20Plus%2C%20it%20did%20the%20best%20job%20of%20dissipating%20heat%20and%20getting%20back%20to%20its%20cool%20baseline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20it's%20slightly%20bigger%20than%20a%20twin%20bed%2C%20it's%20not%20a%20blanket%20that's%20intended%20to%20be%20shared.%20Glass%20beads%20add%20weight%2C%20but%20there's%20no%20beanbag%20feeling%2C%20and%20we've%20never%20felt%20them%20shift%20in%20a%20way%20that%20causes%20the%20blanket%20to%20feel%20lumpy%20or%20uneven.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20zipper%20on%20the%20removable%2C%20washable%20cover%20of%20the%20first%20version%20of%20the%20design%20was%20weak%2C%20couldn't%20handle%20the%20weight%20of%20the%20blanket%2C%20and%20broke%20just%20a%20couple%20of%20months%20into%20its%20use.%20But%20BlanQuil%20has%20since%20reinforced%20the%20zipper%2C%20and%20we've%20yet%20to%20have%20a%20problem%20with%20it.%20We%20even%20stress%20tested%20it%20by%20holding%20the%20weight%20of%20the%20blanket%20against%20the%20zipper%2C%20and%20it%20held%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20it's%20one%20of%20the%20best%20we've%20used%2C%20the%20cooling%20cover's%20material%20has%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20sheen%20to%20it%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20slick%2C%20so%20it%20slides%20off%20the%20bed%20easily%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20if%20you%20toss%20and%20turn%20at%20night.%20As%20soon%20as%20it%20gets%20off-center%2C%20the%20blanket's%20weight%20will%20cause%20it%20to%20slide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20our%20full%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fblanquil-chill-weighted-blanket-review%5C%22%3EBlanQuil%20Chill%20weighted%20blanket%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20comforter%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Brooklinen%20weighted%20comforter%20on%20a%20nicely%20made%20bed%2C%20one%20of%20the%20best%20weighted%20blankets%20in%202022.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fa5bcf5f7d1cb0019e3a560%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJen%20Gushue%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20sleep%20under%20a%20stack%20of%20blankets%20or%20compromise%20your%20bedroom's%20look%2C%20you'll%20want%20a%20weighted%20comforter%2C%20and%20Brooklinen%20makes%20the%20best%20one%20we%20tried.%20It%20looks%20and%20feels%20like%20a%20traditional%20plush%20comforter%20but%20with%20an%20extra%2020%20pounds%20of%20weight%20integrated%20with%20tiny%20glass%20beads.%20The%20blanket%20itself%20is%20made%20of%20400-thread-count%20cotton%20sateen%2C%20so%20it's%20soft%20enough%20to%20throw%20on%20your%20bed%20without%20a%20duvet%20cover.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20being%20said%2C%20we%20recommend%20adding%20a%20duvet%20cover%20%E2%80%94%20corner%20loops%20make%20it%20easy%20to%20tie%20on%20%E2%80%94%20because%20the%20blanket%20is%20dry-clean%20only%2C%20which%20could%20run%20you%20anywhere%20from%20%2420%20to%20%2450%20depending%20on%20where%20you%20live.%20Brooklinen%20offers%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiipgf_112818_best-weighted-blankets-20%26h%3Df8726cf67b51ea419b5dd72847f4a49ee2ae35988ff68c2a00d07cdadb536cb8%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f41fbb%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fbest-weighted-blanket%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.brooklinen.com%252Fcollections%252Fduvet-covers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eduvet%20covers%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20same%20fabrications%20of%20their%20popular%20sheets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2020-pound%20queen%20comforter%20we%20tested%20weighed%20closer%20to%2024%20pounds%2C%20but%20the%20extra%20weight%20didn't%20make%20too%20much%20of%20a%20difference%20once%20we%20laid%20it%20out%20on%20the%20bed.%20Sleeping%20under%20it%20was%20dreamy.%20We%20felt%20enveloped%20by%20the%20cushy%20fill%20but%20not%20too%20overwhelmed%20or%20overheated.%20It%20was%20difficult%20to%20adjust%20due%20to%20the%20weight%20and%20size%2C%20but%20we%20found%20this%20typical%20for%20nearly%20every%20comforter-sized%20weighted%20blanket%20we%20tested.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20pricey%2C%20this%20comfortable%20weighted%20blanket%20is%20worth%20the%20investment%2C%20mainly%20because%20it%20will%20entirely%20replace%20your%20comforter.%20If%20you%20find%20it's%20not%20right%20for%20you%2C%20Brooklinen%20has%20an%20incredibly%20lenient%20return%20policy%2C%20accepting%20returns%20for%20any%20reason%20in%20any%20condition%20within%20365%20days%20of%20your%20purchase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20our%20full%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbrooklinen-weighted-comforter-review%5C%22%3EBrooklinen%20Weighted%20Comforter%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20extra-heavy%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gravity's%2035-pound%20weighted%20blanket%20on%20a%20nicely%20made%20bed.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fa5bdb5f7d1cb0019e3a566%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJen%20Gushue%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20first%20received%20the%20Gravity%2035-pound%20queen%2Fking%20size%20blanket%2C%20we%20thought%20it%20would%20feel%20way%20too%20heavy%2C%20but%20we%20found%20it%20pretty%20manageable.%20It%20did%20tend%20to%20slide%20down%20the%20bed%20as%20we%20slept%2C%20and%20we'd%20often%20awake%20a%20foot%20lower%20than%20usual%20after%20chasing%20the%20blanket%20around%20through%20the%20night.%20It%20was%20simply%20too%20heavy%20to%20pull%20up%20or%20adjust%20while%20laying%20under%20it%2C%20though%20someone%20stronger%20will%20likely%20not%20have%20this%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20issue%20with%20this%20blanket%20was%20that%20the%20included%20micro-plush%20duvet%20cover%20felt%20oddly%20greasy%20out%20of%20the%20package.%20It%20left%20a%20film%20on%20our%20hands%20as%20we%20tried%20to%20smooth%20it%20out%20over%20the%20bed.%20But%20the%20zip-on%20cover%20is%20removable%20and%20washable%2C%20and%20a%20run%20through%20the%20wash%20resolved%20the%20issue.%20We%20can't%20imagine%20hauling%20such%20a%20heavy%20blanket%20into%20and%20out%20of%20a%20washing%20machine%2C%20so%20the%20removable%20cover%20is%20a%20huge%20plus.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Gravity%20blanket%20is%20low-profile%20without%20any%20excess%20fill%2C%20so%20it%20won't%20add%20a%20lot%20of%20bulk%20to%20your%20bed.%20That%20said%2C%20it's%20not%20as%20plush%20or%20cozy%20as%20the%2030%20lb.%20king%20size%20Brooklinen%20comforter%2C%20which%20does%20also%20come%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiipgf_112818_best-weighted-blankets-20%26h%3D2f8cca3e42af79b99fd667f93903584e467e6608b929bed6863634552ccaf280%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f41fbb%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fbest-weighted-blanket%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.brooklinen.com%252Fproducts%252Fweighted-comforter%253Fvariant%253D31930420756570%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E30-pound%20version%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20though%20it's%20much%20more%20expensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20brand%20also%20makes%20%26quot%3Bsingle%26quot%3B%20size%20weighted%20blankets%20that%20measure%2048-inches%20by%2072-inches.%20We%20tested%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiipgf_112818_best-weighted-blankets-20%26h%3Debe8b4af01664415a46267fac0c1e4f45c2aa1079335508af9b35ba1761817cf%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f41fbb%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fbest-weighted-blanket%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fgravityblankets.com%252Fproducts%252Fgravity-blanket%253Fvariant%253D32643696033866%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E15-pounder%20with%20a%20cooling%20cover%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20found%20it%20performed%20well%2C%20but%20nothing%20made%20it%20stand%20out%20from%20the%20pack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20our%20full%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fgravity-weighted-blanket-review%5C%22%3EGravity%20weighted%20blanket%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20king-size%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223570%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20dog%20lying%20on%20a%20bed%20covered%20by%20the%20HomeSmart%20weighted%20blanket.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6168707241af0d00193eb304%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222677%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20HomeSmart%20Products%20King%20Size%20Weighted%20Blanket%20is%20ideal%20for%20larger%20individuals%20and%20couples.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20a%20larger%20person%2C%20you%20may%20have%20trouble%20finding%20a%20weighted%20blanket%20that%20can%20cover%20you%20completely.%20Even%20queen-size%20blankets%20might%20be%20too%20small.%20This%20was%20not%20a%20problem%20with%20the%20HomeSmart%20Products%20King%20Size%20Weighted%20Blanket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%2088%20inches%20by%20104%20inches%20and%20with%20weight%20options%20up%20to%2050%20pounds%2C%20it's%20the%20ideal%20blanket%20for%20couples%20who%20want%20to%20enjoy%20the%20comfort%20of%20a%20weighted%20blanket%20without%20sacrificing%20intimacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20HomeSmart%20blanket%20features%20micro%20glass%20beads%20sewn%20into%205-by-5-inch%20pockets%20to%20keep%20the%20weight%20evenly%20distributed.%20The%20blanket%20is%20machine%20washable%20and%20dryable.%20We've%20washed%20it%20several%20times%20over%20the%20last%20two-and-a-half%20years%20and%20have%20found%20it's%20an%20effortless%20endeavor.%20If%20you%20want%20to%20add%20a%20duvet%20cover%2C%20the%20blanket%20has%2010%20loops%20for%20tying%20one%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20tested%20the%2015-pound%20and%2025-pound%20comforters%20and%20enjoyed%20both%2C%20though%20the%2025-pounder%20was%20almost%20too%20restrictive.%20We%20prefer%20the%2015-pounder.%20Thanks%20to%20its%20breathability%2C%20it's%20a%20great%20year-round%20blanket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20HomeSmart%20Weighted%20Blanket%20isn't%20without%20its%20flaws.%20The%2025-pound%20blanket%20started%20to%20leak%20beads%20after%2018%20months%20of%20use.%20This%20was%20likely%20due%20to%20one%20of%20our%20pets%20working%20a%20hole%20into%20it.%20We%20tried%20to%20reach%20customer%20service%20but%20couldn't%20get%20ahold%20of%20anyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20our%20full%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fhomesmart-king-sized-weighted-blanket-product-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereview%20of%20the%20HomeSmart%20King-Size%20Weighted%20Blanket.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20weighted%20blanket%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221492%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20collection%20of%20weighted%20blankets%20together.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fa5c15df7d1cb0019e3a584%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221119%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Gravity%20Cooling%2C%20Helix%2C%20and%20Brooklyn%20Bedding%20weighted%20blankets%20were%20among%20the%20others%20we%20tested.%3Cp%3EJen%20Gushue%2FAlyssa%20Powell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20the%20main%20factors%20to%20consider%20when%20shopping%20for%20a%20weighted%20blanket%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeight%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESelect%20a%20blanket%20that's%20roughly%2010%25%20of%20your%20body%20weight.%20You%20should%20be%20able%20to%20move%20freely%20under%20the%20blanket.%20If%20you%20can't%2C%20choose%20a%20lighter%20weight.%20If%20you're%20sharing%20a%20weighted%20blanket%20with%20a%20partner%2C%20you'll%20likely%20want%20something%20a%20bit%20heavier.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESize%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIf%20you're%20sharing%20a%20blanket%20with%20a%20partner%20with%20a%20similar%20body%20weight%2C%20you'll%20want%20a%20weighted%20blanket%20that%20covers%20your%20entire%20bed.%20If%20you%20and%20your%20partner%20are%20very%20different%20weights%2C%20consider%20two%20smaller%20separate%20blankets%20in%20a%20throw%20or%20twin%20size.%20Keep%20in%20mind%20that%20a%C2%A015-pound%20throw%20blanket%20feels%20much%20heavier%20than%20a%2015-pound%20comforter%20since%20a%20larger%20blanket%20distributes%20its%20weight%20over%20a%20larger%20surface%20area.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaterial%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EWeighted%20blankets%20are%20available%20in%20a%20range%20of%20materials%2C%20from%20cotton%20and%20Tencel%20to%20microfiber%20or%20polyester.%20Depending%20whether%20you%20you%20want%20a%20blanket%20with%20a%20more%20breathable%20design%20or%20something%20cozier%2C%20consider%20the%20outer%20fabric.%20Some%20comforter-sized%20designs%20are%20also%20designed%20to%20be%20used%20with%20duvet%20covers%2C%20or%20may%20even%20come%20with%20their%20own%2C%20in%20which%20case%2C%20designs%20with%20loops%20will%20make%20it%20easy%20to%20add%20a%20cover%20of%20your%20choice.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFill%20type%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIn%20addition%20to%20considering%20weight%2C%20size%2C%20and%20outer-material%2C%20the%20inner%20fill%20is%20important%20to%20consider.%20Weighted%20blankets%20rely%20on%20micro%20glass%20beads%2C%20plastic%20pellets%2C%20or%20steel%20shot%20beads%2C%20or%20like%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Bearaby's%20knit%20design%2C%20the%20weight%20of%20its%20fabric.%20We%20don't%20have%20a%20preference%20for%20one%20fill%20over%20the%20other%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20function%2C%20but%20steel%20and%20glass%20are%20generally%20more%20sustainable%20than%20plastic.%20Ideally%2C%20the%20fill%20shouldn't%20shift%20too%20much%20within%20the%20blanket%2C%20or%20create%20a%20lot%20of%20noise%20when%20shifting%20under%20the%20blanket.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20we%20test%20weighted%20blankets%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221344%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Four%20weighted%20blankets%20folded%20up.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6182e65023745d001824ea24%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221008%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOur%20team%20has%20tested%20dozens%20of%20weighted%20blankets%20in%20our%20search%20for%20the%20best.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAside%20from%20the%20general%20coziness%20and%20comfort%20provided%20by%20each%20weighted%20blanket%2C%20we%20also%20evaluated%20things%20like%20quality%20of%20material%2C%20value%2C%20weight%20options%2C%20and%20aesthetics.%20For%20example%2C%20a%20blanket%20that%20came%20in%20more%20color%20and%20weight%20options%20beat%20out%20a%20blanket%20of%20equal%20quality%20that%20came%20in%20fewer%20options.%20We%20also%20considered%20return%20policies%2C%20sleep%20trials%2C%20and%20how%20easy%20these%20blankets%20were%20to%20clean.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20following%20are%20three%20tests%20we%20ran%20each%20blanket%20through%20to%20assess%20general%20user%20experience%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESleep%20test%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20One%20of%20us%20slept%20with%20each%20weighted%20blanket%20for%20at%20least%20three%20consecutive%20nights.%20We%20noted%20how%20well%20we%20slept%20overall%20and%20how%20the%20blanket%20regulated%20our%20sleep%20temperature.%20We%20also%20assessed%20how%20well%20the%20blanket%20stayed%20in%20place%20and%20how%20easy%20it%20was%20to%20adjust%20while%20lying%20under%20it.%20This%20test%20also%20included%20making%20the%20bed%20every%20day%20(hauling%20a%20weighted%20blanket%20is%20harder%20than%20it%20looks).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWash%20test%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20We%20washed%20every%20weighted%20blanket%20or%20cover%20that%20was%20machine%20washable%20at%20least%20once%20to%20ensure%20they%20held%20up%20well%20in%20the%20wash%20and%20didn't%20shrink%2C%20shed%2C%20or%20otherwise%20show%20signs%20of%20wear.%20We%20noted%20if%20the%20added%20weight%20made%20them%20more%20challenging%20to%20haul%20into%20and%20out%20of%20the%20washing%20machine.%20We%20also%20discovered%20that%20one%20of%20the%20machine-washable%20blankets%20was%20so%20bulky%20it%20didn't%20fit%20into%20the%20washing%20machine.%20For%20those%20blankets%20that%20weren't%20machine-washable%2C%20we%20noted%20the%20care%20instructions%20and%20factored%20that%20into%20the%20cons%20of%20the%20blanket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeight%20test%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20We%20wanted%20to%20ensure%20each%20blanket%20was%20the%20advertised%20weight.%20To%20get%20an%20accurate%20reading%2C%20we%20stepped%20on%20the%20scale%20with%20and%20without%20the%20blanket.%20The%20difference%20in%20weight%20gave%20us%20the%20blanket's%20weight.%20We%20then%20noted%20any%20discrepancies%20in%20the%20advertised%20weight%20versus%20the%20actual%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWeighted%20blanket%20FAQs%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhich%20weighted%20blanket%20is%20the%20best%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20hard%20for%20the%20one-size-fits-all%20approach%20because%20we're%20all%20just%20so%20unique%20and%20have%20different%20physiologies%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rebecca-robbins.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERebecca%20Robbins%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20sleep%20researcher%2C%20author%2C%20and%20instructor%20in%20medicine%20at%20Harvard%20Medical%20School.%20She%20suggests%20looking%20for%20brands%20with%20sleep%20trials%20or%20buyer-friendly%20return%20policies%20so%20you%20can%20test%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20often%20should%20I%20wash%20my%20weighted%20blanket%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EBrian%20Sansoni%2C%20Senior%20Vice%20President%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cleaninginstitute.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20American%20Cleaning%20Institute%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20recommends%20treating%20weighted%20blankets%20like%20any%20comforter%2C%20washing%20it%20once%20or%20twice%20a%20year%20if%20it%20has%20a%20cover.%20If%20it%20doesn't%20have%20a%20removable%20cover%2C%20clean%20the%20entire%20blanket%20roughly%20once%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAre%20weighted%20blankets%20good%20for%20anxiety%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20theory%2C%20the%20answer%20is%20yes.%20However%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.health.harvard.edu%2Fmind-and-mood%2Fanxiety-and-stress-weighing-heavily-at-night-a-new-blanket-might-help%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eno%20randomized%20clinical%20trials%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20speak%20to%20the%20efficacy%20of%20weighted%20blankets%20in%20treating%20anxiety%2C%20since%20it%20would%20be%20obvious%20to%20participants%20whether%20or%20not%20they%20were%20using%20a%20weighted%20blanket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20theory%20is%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pennmedicine.org%2Fupdates%2Fblogs%2Fhealth-and-wellness%2F2019%2Ffebruary%2Fweighted-blankets%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eweighted%20blankets%20help%20reduce%20some%20anxiety%20symptoms%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20like%20quickened%20breathing%20or%20heart%20rate%2C%20by%20putting%20your%20autonomic%20nervous%20system%20at%20ease.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-weighted-blanket%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A170915658