o-invest-rs-4-000-crore-in-chennai-data-center-park-across-phases-124022900013_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCan't%20Pay%20Attention%20To%20A%20Country%20Soaked%20In%20Red%26quot%3B%3A%20India%20On%20Pakistan%20At%20UN%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20befitting%20reply%20to%20Pakistan%2C%20India%20exercised%20its%20'Right%20of%20Reply'%20in%20response%20to%20references%20to%20New%20Delhi%20stating%20that%20the%20nation%20that%20has%20institutionalized%20the%20systemic%20persecution%20of%20its%20minorities%20and%20has%20a%20truly%20abysmal%20human%20rights%20record%20has%20no%20right%20to%20comment%20on%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExercising%20the%20'Right%20of%20Reply'%20at%20the%20High-Level%20Segment%20of%20the%2055th%20Regular%20Session%20of%20the%20UN%20Human%20Rights%20Council%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20First%20Secretary%20Anupama%20Singh%20said%20that%20regarding%20Pakistan's%20lengthy%20mentions%20of%20India%2C%20it%20is%20very%20regrettable%20that%20the%20Council's%20forum%20has%20once%20again%20been%20abused%20to%20propagate%20flagrantly%20false%20accusations%20about%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20regard%20to%20the%20extensive%20references%20to%20India%20made%20by%20Pakistan%2C%20we%20note%20that%20it%20is%20deeply%20unfortunate%20for%20the%20Council's%20platform%20to%20have%20once%20again%20been%20misused%20to%20make%20patently%20false%20allegations%20against%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIndia%20exercises%20Right%20of%20Reply%20against%20Pakistan%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FHRC55%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23HRC55%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FrdTMVWYmFT%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FrdTMVWYmFT%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20India%20at%20UN%2C%20Geneva%20(%40IndiaUNGeneva)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIndiaUNGeneva%2Fstatus%2F1762871120372384037%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2028%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20entire%20Union%20Territories%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20Ladakh%20is%20an%20integral%20and%20inalienable%20part%20of%20India%2C%20and%20the%20constitutional%20measures%20taken%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20to%20ensure%20socio-economic%20development%20and%20good%20governance%20in%20the%20Union%20Territory%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20are%20matters%20internal%20to%20India.%20Pakistan%20has%20no%20locus%20standi%20to%20pronounce%20on%20matters%20that%20are%20internal%20to%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETerming%20Pakistan's%20human%20rights%20record%20as%20%26quot%3Btruly%20abysmal%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20First%20Secretary%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20country%20that%20has%20institutionalized%20the%20systemic%20persecution%20of%20its%20own%20minorities%20and%20has%20a%20truly%20abysmal%20human%20rights%20record%2C%20commenting%20on%20India%2C%20which%20is%20demonstrably%20making%20great%20strides%20in%20achieving%20economic%20progress%20and%20social%20justice%2C%20is%20not%20merely%20ironical%20but%20perverse.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20glaring%20example%20was%20the%20large%20scale%20brutality%20perpetrated%20against%20the%20minority%20Christian%20community%20in%20Jaranwala%20city%2C%20Pakistan%20in%20August%202023%2C%20when%2019%20churches%20were%20gutted%20and%2089%20Christian%20houses%20burnt%20down.%20Three%2C%20a%20country%20that%20hosts%20and%20even%20celebrates%20UNSC-sanctioned%20terrorists%2C%20commenting%20on%20India%20whose%20pluralistic%20ethos%20and%20democratic%20credentials%20are%20exemplars%20for%20the%20world%2C%20is%20a%20contrast%20for%20everyone%20to%20see%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Singh%20also%20said%20that%20the%20government%20has%20failed%20to%20serve%20the%20actual%20interests%20of%20its%20citizens%2C%20and%20added%20that%20Pakistan%20sponsors%20terrorism%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20cannot%20pay%20any%20further%20attention%20to%20a%20country%20that%20speaks%20while%20being%20soaked%20in%20red%20the%20red%20of%20the%20bloodshed%20from%20the%20terrorism%20it%20sponsors%20around%20the%20world%3B%20the%20red%20of%20its%20debt-riddled%20national%20balance%20sheets%3B%20and%20the%20red%20of%20the%20shame%20its%20own%20people%20feel%20for%20their%20government%20having%20failed%20to%20serve%20their%20actual%20interests%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2055th%20Regular%20Session%20of%20the%20UN%20Human%20Rights%20Council%20is%20taking%20place%20from%20February%2026-April%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20had%20in%20August%20last%20year%20said%20that%20an%20environment%20free%20of%20terror%20and%20hostilities%20was%20imperative%20for%20normal%20ties%20with%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnswering%20queries%20after%20the%20then%20Pakistan%20Prime%20Minister%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20had%20expressed%20his%20willingness%20to%20hold%20talks%20with%20India%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20had%20said%20that%20India%20wants%20normal%20ties%20with%20all%20its%20neighbouring%20countries%20including%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20desire%20normal%20neighbourly%20relations%20with%20all%20our%20neighbours%2C%20including%20Pakistan.%20For%20this%20an%20environment%20free%20of%20terror%20and%20hostility%20is%20imperative%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20MEA%20spokesperson%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExternal%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20had%20said%20in%20an%20earlier%20interview%20with%20the%20news%20agency%20ANI%20that%20Pakistan's%20future%20will%20be%20largely%20determined%20by%20its%20own%20actions%20and%20choices%20and%20it%20is%20for%20the%20neighbouring%20country%20to%20find%20a%20way%20out%20of%20its%20economic%20troubles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20is%20currently%20grappling%20with%2