ister%2C%20Virbhadra%20Singh's%20Son%20Hits%20Pause%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20signs%20of%20a%20thaw%20in%20the%20infighting-riddled%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20unit%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20state%20minister%20Vikramaditya%20Singh%20has%20decided%20not%20to%20%26quot%3Bpress%20his%20resignation%26quot%3B%20hours%20after%20tendering%20it.%20He%20pointed%20out%2C%20however%2C%20that%20there%20is%20a%20difference%20between%20taking%20back%20his%20resignation%20and%20deciding%20not%20to%20press%20for%20it%20being%20accepted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESix%20Congress%20MLAs%20had%20cross-voted%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20BJP%20candidate%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20election%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20party%20suffering%20a%20stunning%20defeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20a%20possible%20threat%20to%20the%20survival%20of%20the%20Sukhvinder%20Singh%20Sukhu%20government%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20had%20announced%20his%20resignation%20as%20the%20Public%20Works%20minister%20on%20Wednesday%20morning.%20The%20minister%20had%20accused%20Mr%20Sukhu%20of%20%26quot%3Bnegligence%26quot%3B%20towards%20MLAs%20and%20disrespecting%20his%20late%20father%20and%20former%20chief%20minister%20Virbhadra%20Singh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20day%20of%20high%20drama%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20said%20in%20the%20evening%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20spoken%20to%20the%20observers%20that%20were%20sent%20by%20the%20party%20high%20command.%20The%20organisation%20is%20more%20important%20than%20one%20individual.%20Keeping%20the%20organisation%20strong%20is%20every%20individual's%20responsibility.%20In%20the%20larger%20interest%20of%20the%20party%20and%20the%20unity%20of%20the%20party%2C%20I%20will%20not%20press%20my%20resignation%20that%20was%20rejected%20by%20the%20chief%20minister%20earlier%20today.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20reporters%20asked%20him%20whether%20this%20meant%20the%20threat%20to%20the%20government%20was%20over%2C%20the%20minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20no%20crisis%20to%20begin%20with.%20It%20was%20a%20creation.%20A%20solution%20can%20be%20found%20to%20everything%20if%20people%20work%20together%20and%20take%20a%20positive%20approach.%20We%20are%20here%20to%20serve%20the%20people%20of%20the%20state%20and%20governing%20is%20the%20way%20to%20do%20that.%20Strengthening%20the%20government%20and%20serving%20the%20people%20by%20doing%20so%20is%20everyone's%20responsibility.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESounding%20a%20cautionary%20note%20while%20speaking%20to%20news%20agency%20ANI%2C%20the%20minister%20said%20there%20is%20a%20difference%20between%20taking%20back%20his%20resignation%20and%20deciding%20not%20to%20press%20it.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20said%20I%20have%20spoken%20to%20the%20observers%20and%20I%20will%20not%20be%20pressing%20my%20resignation%20until%20a%20final%20decision%20is%20taken.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajiv%20Shukla%2C%20Congress'%20Himachal%20in-charge%2C%20however%2C%20said%20that%20the%20government%20has%20a%20majority%20and%20there%20is%20no%20threat%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Disrespect'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20had%20asserted%20that%20the%202022%20Assembly%20polls%20in%20Himachal%20were%20fought%20and%20won%20in%20the%20name%20of%20his%20father%20and%20former%20chief%20minister%20Virbhadra%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20the%20tallest%20Congress%20leader%20in%20the%20state.%20After%20the%20Congress%20won%2040%20out%20of%20the%2068%20Seats%2C%20Vikramaditya%20Singh%20and%20his%20mother%20Pratibha%20SIngh%2C%20who%20is%20the%20state%20party%20chief%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsukhvinder-singh-sukhu-himachal-congress-virbhadra-singh-14-month-wait-then-strike-himachal-royals-open-new-front-for-congress-5143207%5C%22%3Ewere%20among%20the%20frontrunners%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20chief%20minister's%20post%2C%20but%20lost%20out%20to%20Mr%20Sukhu.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20past%20year%2C%20I%20have%20not%20said%20a%20word%20on%20the%20government's%20functioning.%20But%20it%20is%20my%20responsibility%20to%20the%20people%20to%20speak%20out%20now...%20The%20way%20the%20government%20has%20functioned%2C%20the%20negligence%20towards%20MLAs%2C%20the%20drowning%20of%20their%20voices%20has%20led%20us%20to%20this%20point%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20emotional%20Mr%20Singh%20had%20also%20accused%20the%20government%20of%20disrespecting%20Virbhadra%20Singh%2C%20alleging%20that%20it%20failed%20to%20find%20land%20to%20erect%20his%20statue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThreat%20Parried%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sukhu%20government%20faced%20a%20major%20test%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20a%20day%20after%20six%20Congress%20MLAs%20cross-voted%20for%20the%20BJP%20Rajya%20Sabha%20candidate%2C%20Harsh%20Mahajan.%20Three%20Independents%20who%20were%20backing%20the%20government%20also%20voted%20for%20Mr%20Mahajan%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20tie%20of%2034%20votes%20each%20between%20him%20and%20the%20Congress'%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20spelled%20trouble%20for%20the%20government%2C%20which%20needed%20to%20get%20the%20Budget%20passed%20on%20Wednesday%20and%20knew%20that%20not%20being%20able%20to%20do%20so%20would%20prove%20that%20it%20lacked%20a%20majority%20in%20the%20House.%20It%20managed%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhimachal-pradesh-congress-crisis-rajya-sabha-election-congress-buys-time-in-himachal-state-budget-passed-amid-coup-fears-5144297%5C%22%3Estave%20off%20that%20threat%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20however%2C%20after%2015%20BJP%20MLAs%20were%20expelled%20from%20the%20Assembly%20for%20%26quot%3Bsloganeering%20and%20misconduct%26quot%3B%2C%20allowing%20the%20Congress%20to%20have%20a%20working%20majority.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Assembly%20was%20also%20then%20adjourned%20sine%20die%2C%20foiling%20a%20reported%20plan%20by%20the%20BJP%20to%20move%20a%20no-confidence%20