nesday%20said%20the%20AAP%20dispensation's%20allegations%20of%20stalling%20the%20proposed%20scheme%20were%20%26quot%3Bwhite%20lies%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20chief%20minister%20as%20well%20as%20AAP%20government%20ministers%20Atishi%20and%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj%20had%20accused%20the%20LG%20and%20the%20BJP%20of%20stalling%20the%20scheme%20through%20the%20officers%20concerned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%2C%20in%20reply%20to%20the%20LG%2C%20wrote%20back%20an%20'open%20letter'%20to%20him%2C%20saying%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20pained%20by%20the%20language%26quot%3B%20of%20his%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhatever%20our%20differences%2C%20political%20backgrounds%2C%20however%20diverse%20our%20perspectives%3B%20this%20kind%20of%20offensive%20language%20is%20not%20acceptable%20from%20one%20constitutional%20functionary%20to%20another.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20a%20single%20piece%20of%20paper%20on%20the%20scheme%20was%20brought%20to%20the%20notice%20of%20the%20LG%2C%20officially%20or%20unofficially%2C%20Mr%20Saxena%20claimed%20in%20his%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWater%2C%20finance%2C%20urban%20development%2C%20all%20these%20departments%20concerned%20with%20the%20scheme%2C%20being%20transferred%20subjects%2C%20are%20totally%20under%20the%20chief%20minister's%20control%20and%20the%20LG%20has%20no%20role%20whatsoever%2C%20Mr%20Saxena%20wrote%20to%20Mr%20Kejriwal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Raj%20Niwas%20posted%20the%20'open%20letter'%20by%20the%20LtG%20on%20the%20X%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20LG%20writes%20open%20letter%20to%20CM%20Kejriwal%3B%20says%20Water%2C%20Finance%2C%20UD%20Departments%20totally%20under%20your%20control%2C%20I've%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20it.%20Take%20decisions%2C%20and%20don't%20blame%20others.%20Benefit%20all%2027%20lakh%20consumers%2C%20why%20only%2010%20lakh%3F%20Return%20the%20bills%20paid%20by%2017%20lakh%20honest%20consumers%20with%20interest.%26quot%3B%20The%2017%20lakh%20consumers%20paid%20Rs%2013%2C186%20crore%20to%20the%20Delhi%20Jal%20Board%20(DJB)%20as%20water%20bills%20since%202012%2C%20Saxena%20said%20asking%20the%20chief%20minister%20to%20return%20the%20amount%20to%20them%20with%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20LG%20also%20objected%20to%20a%20resolution%20passed%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Assembly%20on%20February%2019%20that%20the%20BJP%20exercises%20%26quot%3Bdirect%20control%26quot%3B%20over%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20completely%20unacceptable%20and%20irresponsible%20assertion%20which%20does%20not%20behove%20of%20the%20members%20who%20endorsed%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Saxena%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20charged%20that%20a%20%26quot%3Bfalse%20narrative%26quot%3B%20was%20being%20peddled%20by%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20his%20ministers%20that%20the%20scheme%20was%20stalled%20by%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20statements%20are%20white%20lies%2C%20again%20an%20example%20of%20typical%20'abuse%20and%20scoot%20game'%20which%20you%20seem%20to%20have%20mastered%20and%20made%20a%20career%20out%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20retorted%20the%20LG%20to%20charges%20on%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20LG%20claimed%20that%20no%20decision%20was%20taken%20by%20the%20Delhi%20government%20regarding%20the%20one-time%20settlement%20'scheme'%2C%20and%20charged%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Binefficiency%20and%20failures%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20his%20government%20were%20being%20deliberately%20put%20on%20him%20and%20the%20Centre%20to%20divert%20public%20attention%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20scheme%20was%20approved%20by%20the%20DJB%20on%20January%2013%2C%202023%2C%20and%20was%20sent%20for%20comments%20by%20the%20finance%20department%20on%20January%2025%2C%202024%2C%20after%20a%20gap%20of%20one%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20concerned%20sent%20the%20file%20to%20the%20chief%20secretary%20as%20late%20as%20February%2021%2C%202024%2C%20clearly%20indicating%20that%20the%20supposed%20'scheme'%20was%20still%20in%20the%20process%20of%20formulation%20and%20was%20far%20from%20reaching%20any%20finality%2C%20said%20the%20LG.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20is%20forced%20to%20wonder%20as%20to%20why%20the%20minister%20kept%20sitting%20on%20the%20proposed%20scheme%20for%20one%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%2C%20in%20his%20'open%20letter'%20to%20Mr%20Saxena%2C%20hoped%20they%20will%20be%20%26quot%3Bable%20to%20maintain%20a%20cordial%20and%20constructive%20working%20relationship%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20Delhi's%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20myself%20discussed%20this%20matter%20with%20you%20more%20than%20once%20and%20brought%20it%20to%20your%20notice%20that%20the%20officers%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Jal%20Board%2C%20the%20Urban%20Development%20Department%20and%20the%20Finance%20Department%20are%20creating%20a%20constitutional%20crisis%20by%20not%20bringing%20the%20proposal%20to%20the%20Council%20of%20Ministers%2C%20despite%20the%20directions%20of%20the%20minister%20in%20charge%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20claimed%20that%20LG%20exercised%20all%20powers%20over%20officers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20consequence%2C%20the%20officers%20respond%20to%20your%20directions%20whether%20given%20orally%20or%20in%20writing.%20This%20is%20the%20reason%20why%20I%20have%20brought%20multiple%20issues%20to%20your%20notice%2C%20where%20matters%20of%20public%20interest%20are%20being%20held%20up%20by%20officers%2C%20including%20this%20issue%20of%20water%20bills%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kejriwal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20chief%20minister%20requested%20the%20LG%20to%20take%20an%20%26quot%3Bexemplary%20action%26quot%3B%20against%20at%20least%20one%20officer%20so%20that%20it%20sends%20a%20message%20to%20the%20administrative%20machinery%20to%20fall%20in%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlease%20do%20not%20let%20the%20people%20of%20Delhi%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20h