0in%20the%20state%20bordering%20troubled%20Myanmar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20letter%20to%20Manipur%20Chief%20Minister%20N%20Biren%20Singh%2C%20the%20Naga%20MLAs%20said%20the%20Tribal%20Affairs%20and%20Hills%20Minister%20Letpao%20Haokip%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Babsent%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20past%2010%20months%2C%20and%20this%20portfolio%20is%20key%20to%20bringing%20peace%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Haokip%20is%20among%20the%2010%20Kuki-Zo%20MLAs%20who%20have%20been%20seeking%20a%20separate%20administration%20carved%20out%20of%20Manipur%2C%20a%20demand%20that%20for%20a%20long%20time%20Kuki-Zo%20insurgent%20groups%2C%20too%2C%20have%20been%20negotiating%20with%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2010%20Kuki-Zo%20MLAs%20also%20face%20criticism%20from%20their%20own%20community%20for%20supporting%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20government%20headed%20by%20Biren%20Singh%2C%20who%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20tribes%20hold%20responsible%20for%20the%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20clashes%20broke%20out%20between%20the%20hill-majority%20Kuki-Zo%20tribes%20and%20the%20valley-majority%20Meiteis%20in%20May%202023%2C%20Kuki-Zo%20civil%20society%20groups%20such%20as%20the%20Indigenous%20Tribal%20Leaders%20Forum%20(ITLF)%20and%20the%20Committee%20on%20Tribal%20Unity%20(CoTU)%20have%20also%20joined%20the%20call%20for%20a%20separate%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20single%20demand%20has%20brought%20the%20insurgent%20groups%2C%20the%2010%20Kuki-Zo%20MLAs%2C%20and%20the%20civil%20society%20groups%20on%20the%20same%20page.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fvkl1bcig_churachandpur_625x300_23_September_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20you%20are%20aware%20of%20the%20difficulties%20faced%20by%20the%20innocent%20citizens%20of%20Manipur%20due%20to%20un