22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bridge%20Too%20Far%3F%20Meant%20To%20Be%20Linked%2C%202%20Mumbai%20Flyovers%20Have%20A%206-Foot%20Gap%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAligning%20and%20linking%20two%20important%20flyovers%20has%20proven%20to%20be%20a%20bridge%20too%20far%20for%20the%20Mumbai%20civic%20body%2C%20which%20is%20now%20facing%20ridicule%20for%20leaving%20a%20vertical%20gap%20of%20nearly%20six%20feet%20between%20them.%20The%20misstep%20has%20also%20sparked%20a%20political%20row%2C%20with%20the%20opposition%20asking%20the%20government%20whether%20it%20expects%20Mumbaikars%20to%20make%20a%20long%20jump%20in%20their%20vehicles%20to%20reach%20the%20other%20flyover.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20arm%20of%20the%20important%20Gokhale%20Bridge%2C%20which%20connects%20Andheri%20East%20and%20West%2C%20was%20thrown%20open%20to%20vehicular%20traffic%20on%20Monday%20evening%2C%20with%20the%20Brihanmumbai%20Municipal%20Corporation%20(BMC)%20calling%20it%20an%20architectural%20marvel%20and%20claiming%20that%20it%20was%20built%20over%20the%20%26quot%3Bcountry's%20busiest%20railway%20tracks%26quot%3B%20without%20disrupting%20local%20and%20long-distance%20train%20services.%20The%20BMC%20is%20currently%20run%20by%20an%20administrator%2C%20who%20reports%20to%20the%20state%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20portion%20of%20the%20bridge%20had%20collapsed%20in%202018%2C%20killing%20two%20people%2C%20and%20it%20was%20demolished%20in%202022%20to%20be%20reconstructed.%20Before%20it%20was%20taken%20apart%2C%20the%20bridge%20linked%20to%20the%20Barfiwala%20Flyover%2C%20which%20is%20used%20by%20traffic%20from%20the%20area%20to%20head%20towards%20Juhu%20and%20then%20proceed%20to%20key%20suburbs%20like%20Bandra.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20news%20of%20the%20Gokhale%20Bridge%20being%20opened%20surfaced%2C%20commuters%20welcomed%20the%20possibility%20of%20their%20travel%20time%20being%20cut%20short%20again.%20The%20joy%20gave%20way%20to%20shock%2C%20however%2C%20when%20it%20turned%20out%20that%20the%20Barfiwala%20Flyover%20was%20not%20joined%20because%20of%20the%20height%20difference%20and%20the%20bridge%20would%20not%20serve%20the%20purpose%20that%20a%20majority%20of%20vehicles%20used%20it%20for.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F5dk6r5b8_mumbai-bridge-2_625x300_28_February_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAttacking%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%20led%20by%20Eknath%20Shinde%20-%20who%20had%20split%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20in%202022%20and%20led%20to%20the%20toppling%20of%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20government%20-%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Udhhav%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray)%20leader%20Aaditya%20Thackeray%20said%20the%20height%20difference%20was%20a%20result%20of%20a%20corrupt%20regime%20and%20that%20the%20ministers%20had%20inaugurated%20a%20%26quot%3Bhalf%20ready%2C%20embarrassingly%20delayed%20bridge%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EShocking%20what%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmybmc%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40mybmc%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20the%20BJP%20sponsored%20khoke%20sarkar%20and%20the%20corrupt%20administrator%20has%20fallen%20to.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnYes%20truly%20first%20in%20India%2C%20probably%20the%20world%20that%20the%202%20bridges%20that%20were%20to%20be%20joined%20have%20a%20difference%20of%206%20ft%20in%20height%20between%20the%202!%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20guardian%20ministers%20have%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fo7rChOLvQW%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fo7rChOLvQW%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Aaditya%20Thackeray%20(%40AUThackeray)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAUThackeray%2Fstatus%2F1762426959613788584%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2027%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes%20truly%20first%20in%20India%2C%20probably%20the%20world%20that%20the%202%20bridges%20that%20were%20to%20be%20joined%20have%20a%20difference%20of%206%20ft%20in%20height%20between%20the%202!%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20minister%20posted%20on%20X.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeam%20Uddhav%20leader%20Anand%20Dubey%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20Gokhale%20Bridge%20had%20been%20shut%20for%20nearly%2016%20months%2C%20since%20November%202022%2C%20and%20was%20still%20misaligned.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIs%20there%20no%20coordination%20between%20the%20BMC%2C%20the%20railways%20and%20the%20contractor%3F%20There%20is%20a%20height%20difference%20of%201.5%20metres%20between%20the%20bridges.%20What%20does%20the%20government%20want%3F%20Do%20they%20expect%20Mumbaikars%20to%20make%20a%20long%20jump%20and%20reach%20the%20flyover%3F%20The%20state%20government%20is%20not%20only%20careless%2C%20but%20has%20also%20cheated%20Mumbaikars%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Railway%20Directive'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Shinde%20faction%20of%20the%20Sena%20has%2C%20however%2C%20claimed%20that%20the%20misalignment%20occurred%20because%20of%20the%20Railways'%20new%20policy%2C%20which%20necessitated%20raising%20the%20Gokhale%20Bridge%20by%20an%20additional%201.5%20metres%20because%20it%20was%20being%20built%20over%20railway%20tracks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20bridge%2C%20due%20to%20the%20new%20policy%20of%20the%20Railways%2C%20the%20height%20of%20the%20bridge%20had%20to%20be%20increased%20by%201.5%20meters.%20When%20the%20bridge%20was%20first%20constructed%2C%20its%20design%20was%20prepared%20along%20with%20the%20Barfiwala%20Flyover.%20But%20because%20the%20height%20of%20the%20bridge%20was%20increased%2C%20the%20flyover%20is%20now%20below%20it.%20We%20will%20seek%20help%20from%20the%20IIT%20and%20the%20Veermata%20Jijabai%20Technological%20Institute%20(VJTI)%20and%20construct%20a%20ramp%20if%20necessary%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Team%20Shinde%20leader%20and%20local%20MLA%C2%A0%20Amit%20Satam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESena%20Spokesperson%20Krishna%20Hegde%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BBy%20December%20this%20year%2C%20all%20the%20improvements%20will%20be%20completed%20and%20the%20bridge%20will%20be%20completely%20opened.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommuters%2C%20however%2C%20aren't%20convinced.%20%26quot%3BWe%20had%20to%20endure%20long%20traffic%20jams%20because%20the%20bridge%20had%20been%20shut.%20It%20used%20to%20take%20five%20minutes%20to%20get%20from%20Andheri%20East%20to%20West%20but%20the%20duration%20went%20up%20to%20nearly%20an%20hour%20when%20the%20bridge%20was%20demolished.%20Now%20that%20the%20bridge%20has%20finally%20been%20constructed%2C%20they%20have%20made%20such%20a%20big%20mistake.%20Even%20if%20they%20construct%20a%20ramp%2C%20can%20it%20be%20done%20without%20closing%20off%20the%20bridge%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20asked%20a%20local%20resident.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709141100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fa0fubg5o_mumbai-misaligned-bridge_625x300_28_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fmumbai-news%2Fgokhale-bridge-barfiwala-flyover-andheri-bridge-too-far-meant-to-be-linked-2-mumbai-flyovers-have-a-6-foot-gap-5145079%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Aligning%20and%20linking%20two%20important%20flyovers%20has%20proven%20to%20be%20a%20bridge%20too%20far%20for%20the%20Mumbai%20civic%20body%2C%20which%20is%20now%20facing%20ridicule%20for%20leaving%20a%20vertical%20gap%20of%20nearly%20six%20feet%20between%20them.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fmumbai-news%2Fgokhale-bridge-barfiwala-flyover-andheri-bridge-too-far-meant-to-be-linked-2-mumbai-flyov