row-account-124022801163_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Retired%20Judge%20Appointed%20Ombudsman%20of%20UP%20University%20a%20Month%20After%20Handing%20Gyanvapi%20Basement%20to%20Hindus%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F28214930%2FVishvesha.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Less%20than%20a%20month%20after%20he%20handed%20over%20the%20basement%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20in%20Varanasi%20to%20Hindus%20for%20worship%20on%20the%20last%20day%20of%20his%20working%20career%2C%20retired%20judge%20Ajaya%20Krishna%20Vishvesha%20has%20been%20appointed%20the%20ombudsman%20of%20a%20public%20university%20in%20Lucknow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVishvesha%20retired%20from%20service%20as%20Varanasi%20district%20judge%20on%20January%2031.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2027%2C%20the%20Dr%20Shakuntala%20Misra%20National%20Rehabilitation%20University%20%E2%80%93%20a%20government-run%20university%20with%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20as%20chairperson%20%E2%80%93%20appointed%20Vishvesha%20as%20its%20%3Cem%3Elokpal%3C%2Fem%3E%20(ombudsman)%20for%20a%20tenure%20of%20three%20years%2C%20university%20officials%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20university%20lokpal%20is%20tasked%20with%20settling%20the%20grievances%20of%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrijendra%20Singh%2C%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%20assistant%20registrar%2C%20confirmed%20that%20Vishvesha%20had%20been%20appointed%20as%20lokpal%20for%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lokpal%E2%80%99s%20task%20is%20%E2%80%9Cresolving%20conflict%20among%20students%20for%20their%20betterment%2C%E2%80%9D%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUniversity%20spokesperson%20Yashwant%20Viroday%20said%20Vishvesha%20was%20appointed%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20recent%20guidelines%20issued%20by%20the%20University%20Grants%20Commission%20(UGC)%2C%20which%20mandated%20that%20each%20university%20shall%20appoint%20an%20ombudsperson%20for%20the%20redressal%20of%20student%20grievances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20on%20what%20basis%20Vishvesha%20was%20picked%2C%20Viroday%20said%20the%20UGC%20guidelines%20mandated%20that%20the%20lokpal%20should%20be%20a%20retired%20vice-chancellor%2C%20retired%20professor%20or%20a%20retired%20district%20judge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%9Cfirst%20priority%20should%20be%20given%20to%20a%20judicial%20person%2C%E2%80%9D%20Viroday%20said%20citing%20UGC%20guidelines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20day-to-day%20cases%20of%20grievances%20and%20disputes%20are%20usually%20settled%20at%20the%20proctor%20level%2C%20but%20some%20cases%20need%20a%20%E2%80%9Cspecialist%E2%80%9D%2C%20Viroday%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVishvesha%20will%20be%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%20first%20ombudsman.%20He%20will%20not%2C%20however%2C%20be%20the%20first%20judge%20linked%20to%20the%20contentious%20temple-mosque%20disputes%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20to%20take%20up%20a%20post-retirement%20public-funded%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%202021%2C%20less%20than%20seven%20months%20after%20he%20acquitted%20all%2032%20accused%20in%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20demolition%20case%2C%20retired%20district%20judge%20Surendra%20Kumar%20Yadav%20was%20appointed%20as%20a%20deputy%20Lok%20Ayukta%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20by%20the%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYadav%20also%20worked%20on%20a%20case%20relating%20to%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20demolition%20on%20his%20last%20working%20day%20before%20retirement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20judge%20of%20a%20special%20CBI%20court%2C%20Yadav%20had%20on%20September%2030%2C%202020%2C%20acquitted%20senior%20BJP%20leaders%20L.K.%20Advani%2C%20Murli%20Manohar%20Joshi%2C%20Uma%20Bharti%2C%20Kalyan%20Singh%20and%20others%20in%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20demolition%20case%2C%20almost%2028%20years%20after%20the%20December%206%2C%201992%20criminal%20act%2C%20for%20lack%20of%20credible%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVishvesha%2C%20as%20district%20judge%2C%20had%20on%20January%2031%20allowed%20Hindus%20to%20worship%20inside%20a%20sealed%20basement%20of%20the%20Mughal-era%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20caretakers%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20termed%20the%20order%20illegal%20and%20inappropriate.%20They%20challenged%20it%2C%20as%20well%20as%20its%20swift%20implementation%20within%20a%20matter%20of%20hours%20by%20the%20Varanasi%20administration%2C%20in%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%2C%20however%2C%20did%20not%20stop%20the%20Hindu%20prayers%20in%20the%20basement%20of%20the%20mosque%20and%20on%20February%2026%20ruled%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20continuation%20of%20%3Cem%3Epuja%3C%2Fem%3E%20at%20the%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20overruled%20the%20objections%20and%20arguments%20of%20the%20mosque%E2%80%99s%20management%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Rohit%20Ranjan%20Agarwal%20dismissed%20a%20plea%20filed%20by%20the%20caretakers%20of%20the%20mosque%20challenging%20the%20controversial%20district%20court%20order%20handing%20over%20a%20southern%20cellar%20of%20the%20mosque%20to%20Hindus%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20pending%20suits%20in%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid-Kashi%20Vishwanath%20Temple%20matter%2C%20in%20which%20Hindu%20plaintiffs%20are%20seeking%20religious%20rights%20within%20the%20mosque%20as%20well%20as%20its%20ultimate%20possession%20from%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20arguing%20the%20case%20in%20the%20high%20court%2C%20the%20caretakers%20of%20the%20mosque%20raised%20questions%20of%20propriety%20and%20legality%20over%20Vishvesha%20delivering%20such%20an%20order%20on%20the%20final%20day%20of%20his%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Committee%20of%20Management%20Anjuman%20Intezamia%20argued%20that%20the%20January%2017%20order%20by%20Vishvesha%2C%20in%20which%20he%20appointed%20the%20district%20magistrate%20as%20the%20receiver%20of%20the%20basement%2C%20was%20modified%20on%20January%2031%2C%20his%20last%20working%20day%2C%20to%20give%20Hindus%20access%20to%20the%20basement%20for%20prayers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20a%20modification%20could%20not%20have%20been%20made%20by%20him%20on%20his%20last%20working%20day%2C%20the%20masjid%20committee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Agarwal%2C%20however%2C%20ruled%20that%20there%20was%20no%20illegality%20in%20Vishvesha%E2%80%99s%20order%20and%20noted%20that%20%E2%80%9Can%20attempt%20has%20been%20made%20to%20malign%20the%20image%20and%20impute%20motive%20to%20the%20order%20passed%20by%20the%E2%80%9D%20court%20below%20on%20January%2031%20%E2%80%9Con%20the%20ground%20that%20the%20officer%20concerned%20had%20passed%20the%20order%20on%20last%20day%20of%20working.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVishvesha%20had%20merely%20corrected%20an%20omission%20or%20accidental%20slip%20by%20issuing%20a%20fresh%20order%20on%20January%2031%20after%20having%20disposed%20the%20application%20on%20January%2017%20without%20addressing%20the%20full%20relief%20sought%20by%20the%20plaintiff%20Shailendra%20Kumar%20Pathak%2C%20a%20Hindu%20priest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPathak%20had%20filed%20the%20application%20seeking%20rights%20to%20worship%20the%20Maa%20Shringar%20Gauri%20as%20well%20as%20other%20visible%20and%20invisible%20deities%20he%20claimed%20were%20in%20the%20cellar%20of%20the%20mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20a%20new%20channel%20days%20after%20he%20retired%2C%20Vishvesha%20said%20he%20had%20issued%20the%20order%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20law%20and%20after%20following%20established%20legal%20principles%20and%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20reporter%20of%20Times%20Now%20Navbharat%20asked%20Vishvesha%20that%20the%20mosque%20side%20did%20not%20see%20it%20as%20a%20mere%20coincidence%20that%20he%20gave%20such%20an%20order%20on%20his%20last%20working%20day%2C%20Vishvesha%20said%20a%20judge%20like%20himself%20only%20worked%20as%20per%20the%20established%20judicial%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20order%20was%20within%20the%20four%20corners%20of%20law%20and%20the%20procedure%20of%20the%20court%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Vishvesha%2C%20who%20had%20also%20ordered%20the%20Archaeological%20Survey%20of%20India%20to%20conduct%20a%20survey%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20premises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20Haridwar%2C%20Vishvesha%20had%20taken%20over%20as%20Varanasi%20district%20judge%20in%20August%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Dr%20Shakuntala%20Misra%20National%20Rehabilitation%20University%2C%20located%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Lucknow%2C%20was%20established%20by%20the%20Divyangjan%20Sashaktikaran%20Vibhag%20of%20the%20state%20government%20through%20an%20ordinance%20dated%20August%2029%2C%202008.%20The%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20of%20Mayawati%20was%20in%20power%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ordinance%20was%20later%20replaced%20by%20an%20act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20university%20describes%20itself%20as%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20first%20university%20of%20its%20kind%2C%20which%20also%20provides%20accessible%20and%20quality%20higher%20education%20to%20challenged%20students%2C%20in%20a%20completely%20barrier-free%20environment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709137391000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F28214930%2FVishvesha.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fajaya-krishna-vishvesha-handed-gyanvapi-cellar-hindus-ombudsman-university-in-lucknow%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ajaya%20Krishna%20Vishvesha%20has%20been%20appointed%20ombudsman%20of%20the%20Dr%20Shakuntala%20Misra%20National%20Rehabilitation%20University%20in%20Lucknow.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fajaya-krishna-vishvesha-handed-gyanvapi-cellar-hindus-ombudsman-university-in-lucknow%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22One%20dead%20and%20two%20missing%20after%20small%20boat%20incid