%20by%20West%20Bengal%20in%20response%20to%20earlier%20directives%20aimed%20at%20addressing%20this%20critical%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Prakash%20Shrivastava%2C%20Chairperson%20of%20the%20NGT%20bench%2C%20expressed%20deep%20concern%20after%20examining%20reports%20filed%20by%20the%20District%20Magistrates%20of%20several%20West%20Bengal%20districts%2C%20including%20North%2024%20Parganas%2C%20Murshidabad%2C%20Nadia%2C%20Malda%2C%20Hooghly%2C%20Purba%20Burdwan%2C%20Howrah%2C%20Purba%20Medinipur%2C%20and%20South%2024%20Parganas.%20The%20reports%20revealed%20a%20lack%20of%20adequate%20sewage%20treatment%20facilities%20across%20the%20state%2C%20with%20some%20districts%2C%20like%20Purba%20Medinipur%2C%20shockingly%20lacking%20even%20a%20single%20Sewage%20Treatment%20Plant%20(STP).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NGT%20has%20warned%20the%20West%20Bengal%20authorities%20of%20potential%20fines%20if%20they%20fail%20to%20demonstrate%20significant%20progress%20in%20tackling%20the%20issue%20of%20untreated%20sewage%20flowing%20into%20the%20Ganga.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20perusal%20of%20these%20reports%2C%20we%2C%20in%20general%2C%20find%20that%20no%20adequate%20facilities%20for%20treatment%20of%20sewage%20generated%20per%20day%20have%20been%20set%20up%20and%20that%20even%20the%20timeline%20for%20achieving%20the%20target%20of%20100%20per%20cent%20treatment%20of%20sewage%20has%20not%20been%20disclosed%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%2C%20also%20comprising%20judicial%20member%20Sudhir%20Agarwal%20and%20expert%20members%20A%20Senthil%20Vel%20and%20Afroz%20Ahmad%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20order%20passed%20on%20February%2021%2C%20the%20bench%20said%2C%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bsurprising%20%26quot%3B%20that%20not%20even%20a%20single%20Sewage%20Treatment%20Plant%20(STP)%20was%20set%20up%20in%20some%20districts%20like%20Purba%20Medinipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20condition%20that%20has%20been%20reflected%20in%20these%20reports%20is%20far%20from%20satisfactory%20and%20shows%20that%20258.67%20million%20litres%20per%20day%20(MLD)%20of%20untreated%20sewage%20is%20directly%20flowing%20in%20the%20river%20Ganga%20in%20the%20state%20of%20West%20Bengal%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20green%20panel%20directed%20the%20DMs%20of%20nine%20districts%2C%20through%20which%20the%20river's%20mainstream%20flowed%2C%20to%20file%20affidavits%20setting%20a%20deadline%20for%20achieving%20the%20target%20of%20100%20per%20cent%20treatment%20of%20sewage%20generated%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DMs%20also%20have%20to%20disclose%20the%20manner%20and%20extent%20of%20utilisation%20of%20funds%20received%20from%20the%20National%20Mission%20for%20Clean%20Ganga%20(NMCG)%2C%20besides%20steps%20taken%20for%20demarcation%20of%20floodplains%20in%20their%20districts%2C%20the%20tribunal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20also%20find%20that%20the%20entire%20stretch%20of%20river%20Ganga%20in%20West%20Bengal%20contains%20high%20fecal%20coliform%2C%20making%20the%20water%20unfit%20for%20bathing%20and%20thereby%20not%20meeting%20primary%20water%20quality%20criteria%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tribunal%20directed%20the%20NMCG%20to%20carry%20out%20a%20performance%20audit%20of%20each%20of%20the%20districts%20on%20generation%20and%20treatment%20of%20waste%20and%20the%20extent%20of%20pollution%20each%20was%20causing%20in%20the%20river.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20find%20any%20progress%20in%20the%20reduction%20of%20discharge%20of%20pollutants%20to%20the%20River%20Ganga%20in%20any%20of%20the%20districts.%20Therefore%2C%20if%20in%20the%20next%20report%20sufficient%20progress%20is%20not%20shown%2C%20then%20the%20tribunal%20may%20not%20have%20any%20option%20but%20to%20impose%20Environmental%20Compensation%20(EC)%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20tribunal%20said.%20It%20ordered%20the%20DMs%20concerned%20and%20the%20NMCG%20to%20file%20fresh%20reports%20within%20eight%20weeks%20and%20posted%20the%20matter%20for%20further%20proceedings%20on%20May%202.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20inputs%20from%20PTI)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709136000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Ft1snkrl8_ganga_625x300_28_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fganga-in-west-bengal-declared-unfit-for-bathing-due-to-untreated-sewage-ngt-warns-of-fines-5145392%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20NGT%20has%20warned%20the%20West%20Bengal%20authorities%20of%20potential%20fines%20if%20they%20fail%20to%20demonstrate%20significant%20progress%20in%20tackling%20the%20issue%20of%20untreated%20sewage%20flowing%20into%20the%20Ganga.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fganga-in-west-bengal-declared-unfit-for-bathing-due-to-untreated-sewage-ngt-warns-of-fines-5145392%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fganga-in-west-bengal-declared-unfit-for-bathing-due-to-untreated-sewage-ngt-warns-of-fines-5145392%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fganga-in-west-bengal-declared-unfit-for-bathing-due-to-untreated-sewage-ngt-warns-of-fines-5145392%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rohit-Prajakta%20wrap%20up%20Mismatched%20season%203%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709135914000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108081436%2Cimgsize-33232.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fmismatched-season-3-rohit-saraf-shares-heartstealing-pictures-with-prajakta-koli-as-they-wrap-up-the-hyderabad-schedule%2Farticleshow%2F108081442.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108081442.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ERohit%20Saraf%2