20human%20life%20and%20people's%20problems%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20said%20on%20Wednesday%20at%20an%20event%20organised%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20Bar%20Association%20(SCBA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENewly-appointed%20judges%20Justices%20Satish%20Chandra%20Sharma%2C%20Augustine%20George%20Masih%2C%20Sandeep%20Mehta%2C%20and%20Prasanna%20B%20Varale%20were%20welcomed%20at%20the%20event.%20Chief%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20said%20that%20with%20their%20elevation%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20once%20again%20working%20at%20its%20maximum%20mandated%20strength%20of%2034%20judges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20also%20recited%20lines%20from%20a%20ghazal%20by%20the%20legendary%20Jagjit%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20like%20to%20welcome%20them%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20In%20what%20has%20come%20to%20become%20my%20tradition%20for%20events%20at%20the%20bar%2C%20I%20would%20like%20to%20conclude%2C%20Tere%20aane%20ki%20jab%20khabar%20mehke%2C%20teri%20khushbu%20se%20saara%20ghar%20mehke%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20importantly%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20will%20benefit%20from%20the%20diversity%20of%20their%20experience%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20decision-making%20is%20somewhat%20like%2C%20to%20borrow%20the%20words%20of%20scholar%20Catharine%20Wells%2C%20'riding%20a%20bicycle'.%20'If%20you%20are%20teetering%20out%20of%20control%2C%20it%20is%20unlikely%20that%20a%20complicated%20theory%20will%20help%20to%20restore%20the%20balance'.%20In%20the%20moments%20of%20imbalance%2C%20we%20are%20unlikely%20to%20find%20solutions%20in%20very%20complicated%20theoretical%20statements%20of%20the%20law%20or%20policy%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20stabilising%20influence%20in%20such%20moments%20of%20crisis%20is%20often%20a%20very%20simple%20idea%20of%20justice.%20The%20strength%20of%20a%20simple%20idea%20lies%20in%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20comes%20from%20the%20vast%20experience%20of%20a%20judge%20-%20as%20a%20lawyer%2C%20as%20a%20student%20of%20the%20law%20and%20as%20a%20discerning%20observing%20member%20of%20this%20society.%20Legal%20power%20is%20not%20enough%20for%20a%20judge.%20The%20stronger%20tool%20is%20their%20desire%20to%20understand%20human%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20journeys%20of%20Justice%20Sharma%2C%20Justice%20Masih%2C%20Justice%20Mehta%2C%20and%20Justice%20Varale%20demonstrate%20their%20commitment%20to%20understanding%20human%20life%20and%20to%20improving%20it%20with%20the%20help%20of%20our%20laws%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20there%20is%20a%20vast%20body%20of%20literature%20on%20how%20judges%20must%20decide%20and%20what%20goes%20into%20legal%20decision-making%20in%20general.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20the%20knowledge%20of%20the%20law%20and%20the%20context%20of%20its%20enactments%20are%20important%2C%20it%20is%2C%20ultimately%2C%20the%20understanding%20of%20people's%20problems%20that%20makes%20us%20better%20lawyers%20and%20judges%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Sharma%20said%20his%20elevation%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20was%20the%20highest%20honour%20for%20him.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20dream%20come%20true.%20To%20serve%20in%20the%20top%20court%20of%20the%20land%20is%20unarguably%20the%20highest%20honour%20for%20any%20person%20in%20the%20legal%20profession%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Masih%20said%20legal%20profession%20is%20an%20area%20where%2C%20if%20one%20works%20hard%2C%20one%20can%20achieve%20what%20one%20wants%20and%20talent%20and%20efforts%20will%20be%20recognised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20always%20chance%20of%20you%20moving%20up.%20We%20always%20hear%20so%20much%20about%20who%20has%20been%20elevated%20to%20the%20bench.%20But%20here's%20a%20person%20standing%20in%20front%20of%20you%20who%20had%20no%20connection%20with%20law%20and%20is%20a%20first-generation%20lawyer%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Masih%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Mehta%20thanked%20the%20senior%20judges%20with%20whom%20he%20has%20sat%20as%20a%20part%20of%20a%20bench%20so%20far.%20%26quot%3BThey%20have%20guided%20me%20in%20the%20nitty-gritty%20in%20an%20entirely%20new%20work%20environment%2C%20helping%20me%20overcome%20challenges%2C%20which%20is%20really%20quite%20daunting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Varale%20described%20the%20Bar%20and%20Bench%20as%20the%20two%20wheels%20of%20the%20chariot%20of%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAttorney%20General%20R%20Venkataramani%20said%20that%20during%20Chief%20Justice%20Chandrachud's%20tenure%2C%2015-16%20judges%20have%20been%20appointed%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESCBA%20president%20Adish%20C%20Aggarwala%20praised%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20collegium%20for%20picking%20talented%20judges.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709131320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fv69008hg_dy-chandrachud_625x300_28_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flegal-power-not-enough-chief-justice-welcomes-newly-appointed-judges-5144947%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Legal%20power%20is%20not%20enough%20for%20a%20judge%20for%20whom%20the%20stronger%20tool%20is%20their%20desire%20to%20understand%20human%20life%20and%20people's%20problems%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20said%20on%20Wednesday%20at%20an%20event%20organised%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20Bar%20Association.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flegal-power-not-enough-chief-justice-welcomes-newly-appointed-judges-5144947%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flegal-power-not-enough-chief-justice-welcomes-newly-appointed-judges-514494