w.livemint.com%2Fmarket%2Fstock-market-news%2Fpatanjali-foods-share-price-dips-over-4-as-supreme-court-issues-contempt-notice-11709092870352.html%5C%22%3Edropped%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20around%204%25%2C%20%3Ci%3ELivemint%3C%2Fi%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98No%20ads%20of%20medical%20products%E2%80%99%3A%20SC%20to%20Patanjali%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20first%20heard%20the%20petition%20by%20the%20IMA%20last%20year%2C%20it%20ordered%20Patanjali%20to%20cease%20all%20its%20%E2%80%9Cfalse%20and%20misleading%E2%80%9D%20advertisements.%20The%20top%20court%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmisleading-advertisements-fine-false-cure-claims-supreme-court-patanjali%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20any%20violation%20would%20result%20in%20an%20imposition%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%201%20crore%20on%20every%20product%20for%20which%20a%20false%20claim%20is%20made%20regarding%20its%20ability%20to%20cure%20a%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatanjali%20had%20then%20assured%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20it%20would%20not%20make%20statements%20against%20any%20system%20of%20medicine%2C%20or%20make%20any%20statements%20regarding%20the%20medical%20efficacy%20of%20Patanjali%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20continued%20to%20run%20such%20advertisements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%2C%20hence%2C%20issued%20contempt%20of%20court%20notices%20against%20Patanjali%20Ayurved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20also%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-issues-contempt-notice-to-patanjali-ayurved-its-md-for-misleading-ads-on-medicinal-cures-250636%5C%22%3E%20banned%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20company%20from%20running%20advertisements%20of%20products%20claiming%20to%20cure%20such%20diseases%2C%20%3Ci%3ELiveLaw%20%3C%2Fi%3Ereported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98Govt%20sitting%20with%20its%20eyes%20closed%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20that%20the%20%E2%80%98entire%20country%20was%20being%20taken%20for%20a%20ride%E2%80%99%20by%20such%20misleading%20advertisements.%20As%20earlier%20mentioned%2C%20the%20apex%20court%20also%20came%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20Union%20government%20for%20lack%20of%20action%20on%20the%20misleading%20advertisements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20government%20is%20sitting%20with%20its%20eyes%20closed.%20This%20is%20very%20unfortunate.%20The%20government%20will%20have%20to%20take%20some%20immediate%20action%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3ENDTV%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgovernment-sitting-with-eyes-closed-must-take-action-says-supreme-court-on-patanjali-misleading-and-false-ads-case-5136445%5C%22%3Equoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20court%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgovernment-sitting-with-eyes-closed-must-take-action-says-supreme-court-on-patanjali-misleading-and-false-ads-case-5136445%5C%22%3Ewill%20be%20next%20heard%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20March%2015%2C%20the%3Cem%3E%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EShare%20price%20of%20Patanjali%20Foods%20drops%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20share%20prices%20of%20Patanjali%20Foods%2C%20an%20FMCG%20company%2C%20fell%20by%20around%204%25%20on%20Wednesday%20morning%2C%20as%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20issued%20a%20contempt%20notice%20to%20Patanjali%20Ayurved%20and%20its%20managing%20director%20Acharya%20Balakrishna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20company%20claimed%20that%20its%20business%20operations%20and%20financial%20performance%20would%20not%20be%20impacted%20by%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20observations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20observations%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20do%20not%20relate%20to%20Patanjali%20Foods%20Ltd%20(PFL)%2C%20which%20is%20an%20independent%20listed%20entity%20and%20operates%20in%20the%20space%20of%20edible%20oil%20and%20food%20FMCG%20product