%20metro%20train%20by%20an%20official%20at%20Bengaluru's%20Rajajinagar%20station%20because%20of%20his%20%26quot%3Buntidy%26quot%3B%20clothes%2C%20the%20National%20Human%20Rights%20Commission%20has%20taken%20suo%20motu%20cognizance%20of%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NHRC%2C%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20said%20it%20has%20observed%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20contents%20of%20the%20media%20report%2C%20if%20true%2C%20amount%20to%20a%20violation%20of%20human%20rights%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BNo%20person%20can%20be%20denied%20access%20to%20public%20transport%20based%20on%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20clothes%20he%20or%20she%20is%20wearing.%20If%20someone%20possesses%20any%20objectionable%20material%2C%20he%20could%20be%20stopped%20only%20as%20per%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Commission%20has%20issued%20notices%20to%20the%20Karnataka%20Chief%20Secretary%20and%20the%20Managing%20Director%20of%20Bengaluru%20Metro%20Rail%20Corporation%20Limited%20(BMRCL)%20and%20asked%20for%20a%20detailed%20report%20within%20four%20weeks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20should%20include%20steps%20taken%20or%20proposed%20to%20ensure%20such%20incidents%20do%20not%20recur%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rights%20body%20also%20posted%20about%20the%20incident%20on%20X%20and%20wrote%3A%20%26quot%3BNHRC%20takes%20suo%20motu%20cognizance%20of%20the%20reported%20stopping%20of%20a%20farmer%20from%20boarding%20the%20metro%20train%20by%20an%20official%20due%20to%20his%20untidy%20attire.%20The%20Commission%20observes%20no%20one%20can%20be%20denied%20access%20to%20public%20transport%20based%20on%20his%20attire.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ENHRC%20takes%20suo%20motu%20cognizance%20of%20the%20reported%20stopping%20of%20a%20farmer%20from%20boarding%20the%20metro%20train%20by%20an%20official%20due%20to%20his%20untidy%20attire.%