0very%20recently%2C%20the%20star%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20duo%20was%20part%20of%20the%20side.%20While%20Ishan%20Kishan%20was%20last%20part%20of%20the%20Test%20squad%20during%20India's%20Tour%20of%20South%20Africa%20in%20December%2C%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20played%20the%20first%20two%20Tests%20of%20the%20ongoing%20series%20against%20England.%20Yet%2C%20the%20BCCI%20removed%20the%20two%20senior%20player%20from%20the%20contracts%20list.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20BCCI%20made%20it%20a%20point%20to%20single%20out%20the%20duo's%20absence%20with%20the%20following%20line%20in%20the%20list%3A%20%26quot%3BPlease%20note%20that%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20and%20Ishan%20Kishan%20were%20not%20considered%20for%20the%20annual%20contracts%20in%20this%20round%20of%20recommendations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20why%20were%20Ishan%20Kishan%20and%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20dropped%20from%20BCCI's%20Annual%20Player%20Contracts%20for%20Team%20India%20(Senior%20Men)%20for%20the%202023-24%20season%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIshan%20Kishan's%20case%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20was%20no%20official%20reason%20given%20on%20why%20Ishan%20Kishan%20and%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20were%20dropped%2C%20one%20line%20in%20BCCI's%20release%20gives%20a%20strong%20hint.%20%26quot%3BThe%20BCCI%20has%20recommended%20that%20all%20athletes%20give%20precedence%20to%20participating%20in%20domestic%20cricket%20during%20periods%20when%20they%20are%20not%20representing%20the%20national%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BCCI%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Ishan%20Kishan%20had%20left%20India's%20Tour%20of%20South%20Africa%2C%20the%20BCCI%20had%20said%20on%20December%2017%3A%20%26quot%3BMr%20Ishan%20Kishan%20has%20requested%20the%20BCCI%20to%20be%20released%20from%20the%20upcoming%20Test%20series%20against%20South%20Africa%20citing%20personal%20reasons.%20The%20wicket-keeper%20has%20subsequently%20been%20withdrawn%20from%20the%20Test%20squad.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20was%20expected%20that%20Ishan%20Kishan%20would%20play%20domestic%20cricket%20from%20his%20time%20away%20from%20the%20national%20team%2C%20the%20wicketkeeper-batter%20chose%20to%20remain%20absent%20from%20his%20state%20team%20Jharkhand's%20Ranji%20Trophy%20matches.%20Despite%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20coach%20Rahul%20Dravid%20clearly%20mentioning%20that%20he%20need%20to%20play%20some%20form%20of%20cricket%20to%20regain%20his%20place%20in%20the%20Indian%20squad%2C%20Ishan%20Kishan%20ignored%20the%20instruction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20he%20only%20made%20a%20return%20to%20competitive%20cricket%20on%20Tuesday%20at%20the%20DY%20Patil%20T20%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBCCI%20secretary%20Jay%20Shah%20had%20also%20mentioned%20that%20it%20is%20mandatory%20for%20centrally%20contracted%20players%2C%20who%20are%20not%20in%20the%20national%20team%2C%20to%20play%20red-ball%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShreyas%20Iyer's%20case%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20middle%20order%20batter%20has%20been%20battling%20poor%20form%20in%20Test%20cricket.%20He%20was%20dropped%20from%20the%20last%20three%20Tests%20against%20England%20after%20failing%20to%20leave%20a%20mark%20in%20the%20first%20two%20games.%C2%A0%26quot%3BIf%20Shreyas%20was%20to%20be%20rested%20because%20of%20injury%2C%20the%20BCCI%20medical%20bulletin%20would%20have%20had%20an%20update.%20Since%20there%20are%20no%20updates%2C%20it%20can%20be%20concluded%20that%20he%20has%20got%20the%20axe%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%20had%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI%20then.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20Iyer%20made%20himself%20unavailable%20for%20Mumbai's%20Ranji%20Trophy%20quarterfinals%20citing%20injury%20concerns%20but%20the%20National%20Cricket%20Academy%20(NCA)%20has%20said%20that%20he%20has%20no%20'fresh%20injuries'%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20Indian%20Express.%20The%20report%20cited%20an%20email%20from%20Nitin%20Patel%2C%20the%20head%20of%20sports%20science%20and%20medicine%20at%20the%20NCA%2C%20who%20told%20selectors%20that%20Iyer%20was%20'fit'.%20It%20also%20quoted%20Mumbai%20Cricket%20Association%20sources%20saying%20that%20Iyer%20had%20cited%20back%20pain%20as%20the%20reason%20behind%20missing%20the%20Ranji%20Trophy%20quarterfinal%20match%20against%20Baroda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShreyas%20Iyer%20was%20fit%20and%20available%20for%20selection%20as%20per%20the%20handover%20report%20of%20the%20Indian%20team%20after%20the%202nd%20Test%20match%20against%20England.%20There%20are%20currently%20no%20fresh%20injuries%20reported%20as%20well%20after%20his%20departure%20from%20Team%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20Patel%20wrote%20in%20his%20email%20according%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20BCCI%20omitting%20both%20from%20its%20contract%20list%2C%20the%20national%20body%20might%20be%20acting%20tough%20to%20a%20send%20a%20stern%20message%20to%20all%20players%20who%20has%20national%20team%20aspirations.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709127720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fsm30qqc8_ishan-kishan-shreyas-iyer_625x300_28_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fwhy-ishan-kishan-and-shreyas-iyer-were-axed-from-bcci-contract-list-a-case-of-bcci-acting-tough-explained-5144453%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20prominent%20players%20-%20Ishan%20Kishan%20and%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20-%20have%20not%20been%20included%20by%20BCCI%20in%20its%20Annual%20Player%20Contracts%20for%20Team%20India%20(Senior%20Men)%20for%20the%202023-24%20season%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fixing%20Pak's%20economy%20will%20be%20top%20priority%3A%20Nawaz%20Sharif%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709127582000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108078867%2Cimgsize-596804.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Ffixing-pakistans-economy-t