20us%20in%20sync%20with%20the%20seasons.%20Leaplings%2C%20born%20on%20this%20rare%20day%2C%20celebrate%20unique%20birthdays.%20The%20Earth%20takes%20around%20365.2422%20days%20to%20orbit%20the%20sun%20each%20year%2C%20and%20the%20additional%20six%20hours%20annually%20accumulate%20over%20time.%20Leap%20days%20ensure%20our%20alignment%20with%20the%20seasons%2C%20preventing%20potential%20chaos%20for%20farmers%2C%20crops%2C%20and%20school%20holidays.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fwhats-in-a-leap-year-eternal-youth-wedding-bells-and-tech-bugs%2Farticleshow%2F108076164.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fwhats-in-a-leap-year-eternal-youth-wedding-bells-and-tech-bugs%2Famp_articleshow%2F108076164.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fwhats-in-a-leap-year-eternal-youth-wedding-bells-and-tech-bugs%2Famp_articleshow%2F108076164.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Disconcerting%20Trend%20Over%20the%20Undermining%20of%20Scientific%20Institutions%2C%20Threat%20to%20Scientific%20Temper'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F28175801%2Fimage-1880.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20group%20of%20former%20scientists%20and%20academicians%20have%20raised%20concerns%20over%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdisconcerting%20trend%20of%20undermining%20scientific%20institutions%20and%20the%20constitutional%20idea%20of%20promoting%20scientific%20temper.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20the%20abrupt%20closure%20of%20key%20institutions%20engaged%20in%20science%20communication%20to%20the%20promotion%20of%20pseudoscience%2C%20compounded%20by%20significant%20delays%20in%20the%20disbursement%20of%20funds%20and%20changes%20in%20school%20science%20syllabi%2C%20India%20is%20witnessing%20a%20systematic%20threat%20to%20its%20scientific%20foundation%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20said%20in%20a%20panel%20discussion%20on%20February%2026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20discussion%2C%20titled%20%E2%80%98Decoding%20Threat%20to%20Science%20and%20Scientific%20Temper%E2%80%99%2C%20was%20organised%20by%20%E2%80%98In%20Defence%20of%20Science%E2%80%99%20group%2C%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20raised%20concerns%20over%20key%20institutions%20like%20Vigyan%20Prasar%20and%20NISTADS%20being%20abruptly%20closed%20or%20merged%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20move%20diminished%20avenues%20for%20science%20communication.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20were%20unique%20institutions%20in%20the%20developing%20world%20and%20had%20accumulated%20vast%20expertise%20in%20their%20respective%20areas%20of%20work.%20Another%20science%20outreach%20organisation%2C%20the%20Indian%20Science%20Congress%20Association%20(ISCA)%20has%20been%20subjected%20to%20official%20apathy.%20The%20loss%20of%20these%20institutions%20will%20have%20far-reaching%20implications%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20scientific%20capabilities%20and%20global%20standing%20in%20the%20field%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20speakers%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20of%20pseudoscience%20endorsed%20by%20official%20agencies%20jeopardises%20public%20trust%20and%20undermines%20genuine%20scientific%20expertise%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEqually%20troubling%20is%20the%20promotion%20of%20pseudoscience%20over%20evidence-based%20research%20and%20established%20scientific%20principles.%20With%20a%20rise%20in%20the%20endorsement%20of%20unproven%20remedies%20and%20practices%20by%20official%20agencies%20and%20their%20funding%20by%20national%20research%20funding%20agencies%2C%20there%20is%20a%20risk%20of%20misleading%20the%20public%20and%20eroding%20trust%20in%20genuine%20scientific%20expertise.%20Such%20actions%20not%20only%20undermine%20public%20trust%20in%20science%2C%20and%20people%E2%80%99s%20health%20and%20safety%20but%20also%20jeopardize%20the%20credibility%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20scientific%20community.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20further%20said%20that%20bureaucratic%20delays%20in%20funding%20disbursement%20hamper%20research%20initiatives%2C%20while%20changes%20to%20school%20science%20syllabi%20prioritize%20ideological%20agendas%20over%20factual%20accuracy%2C%20hindering%20scientific%20literacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EReproduced%20below%20is%20the%20full%20statement.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStatement%20released%20by%20Scientists%20and%20Concerned%20Citizens%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20Delhi%2C%20February%2026%2C%202024%3A%20Developments%20in%20recent%20years%20in%20India%20have%20caused%20concern%20within%20the%20scientific%20community%20and%20academic%20circles%2C%20pointing%20to%20a%20disconcerting%20trend%20of%20undermining%20scientific%20institutions%20and%20the%20constitutional%20idea%20of%20promoting%20scientific%20temper.%20From%20the%20abrupt%20closure%20of%20key%20institutions%20engaged%20in%20science%20communication%20to%20the%20promotion%20of%20pseudoscience%2C%20compounded%20by%20significant%20delays%20in%20the%20disbursement%20of%20funds%20and%20changes%20in%20school%20science%20syllabi%2C%20India%20is%20witnessing%20a%20systematic%20threat%20to%20its%20scientific%20foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20closure%20of%20Vigyan%20Prasar%20(VP)%2C%20which%20was%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20groundbreaking%20science%20communication%20and%20science%20popularisation%20efforts%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20merger%20of%20the%20National%20Institute%20for%20Science%2C%20Technology%20and%20Development%20Studies%20(NISTADS)%20with%20a%20new%20entity%2C%20seem%20to%20be%20directed%20at%20ending%20the%20only%20avenues%20of%20connecting%20science%20with%20society%20through%20well-informed%20channels.%20They%20were%20unique%20institutions%20in%20the%20developing%20world%20and%20had%20accumulated%20vast%20expertise%20in%20their%20respective%20areas%20of%20work.%20Another%20science%20outreach%20organisation%2C%20the%20Indian%20Science%20Congress%20Association%20(ISCA)%20has%20been%20subjected%20to%20official%20apathy.%20The%20loss%20of%20these%20institutions%20will%20have%20far-reaching%20implications%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20scientific%20capabilities%20and%20global%20standing%20in%20the%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEqually%20troubling%20is%20the%20promotion%20of%20pseudoscience%20over%20evidence-based%20research%20and%20established%20scientific%20principles.%20With%20a%20rise%20in%20the%20endorsement%20of%20unproven%20remedies%20and%20practices%20by%20official%20agencies%20and%20their%20funding%20by%20national%20research%20funding%20agencies%2C%20there%20is%20a%20risk%20of%20misleading%20the%20public%20and%20eroding%20trust%20in%20genuine%20scientific%20expertise.%20Such%20actions%20not%20only%20undermine%20public%20trust%20in%20science%2C%20and%20people%E2%80%99s%20health%20and%20safety%20but%20also%20jeopardize%20the%20credibility%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20scientific%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20the%20bureaucratic%20delays%20in%20the%20disbursement%20of%20funds%20for%20scientific%20research%20projects%20and%20fellowships%20have%20left%20many%20young%20scientists%20and%20researchers%20in%20a%20precarious%20position.%20Without%20adequate%20funding%2C%20vital%20research%20initiatives%20are%20being%20hampered%2C%20leading%20to%20setbacks%20in%20critical%20areas.%20The%20decline%20in%20the%20budget%20allocated%20to%20science%20and%20higher%20education%20in%20general%2C%20and%20civilian%20R%26amp%3BD%20in%20particular%2C%20over%20the%20last%20decade%20does%20not%20augur%20well%20for%20Indian%20science%20as%20well%20as%20society.%20The%20continuous%20erosion%20of%20academic%20freedom%20is%20another%20matter%20of%20concern.%20All%20this%20could%20jeopardize%20India%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20address%20pressing%20societal%20challenges%20and%20capitalize%20on%20emerging%20opportunities%20using%20science.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20these%20challenges%2C%20changes%20to%20school%20science%20syllabi%20have%20raised%20concerns%20about%20the%20quality%20and%20accuracy%20of%20science%20education%20in%20India.%20Alterations%20that%20prioritize%20ideological%20agendas%20over%20scientific%20facts%20risk%20hindering%20the%20development%20of%20a%20scientifically%20literate%20populace.%20This%20could%20have%20long-term%20implications%20for%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20foster%20a%20culture%20of%20innovation%20and%20critical%20thinking%20among%20its%20youth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20advocates%20for%20evidence-based%20decision-making%20and%20scientific%20integrity%2C%20we%20feel%20that%20safeguarding%20scientific%20institutions%2C%20promoting%20rigorous%20research%20practices%2C%20ensuring%20timely%20funding%2C%20and%20upholding%20the%20integrity%20of%20science%20education%20are%20paramount%20to%20using%20science%20and%20technology%20for%20national%20development%2C%20and%20for%20the%20global%20competitiveness%20of%20Indian%20R%26amp%3BD.%20We%20urge%20the%20citizens%20to%20raise%20their%20voices%20against%20these%20disturbing%20trends.%20It%20is%20our%20constitutional%20duty%20to%20protect%20scientific%20institutions%20and%20promote%20scientific%20temper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EName%20Designation%20Affiliation%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEr.%20Anuj%20Sinha%20Former%20Scientist%20In-charge%20NCSTC%20(DST)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Director%20Vigyan%20Prasar%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr.%20Ashok%20Jain%20Former%20Director%20CSIR-NISTADS%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20D%20Raghunandan%2C%20Delhi%20Science%20Forum%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProf.%20Dinesh%20Abrol%20Former%20Chief%20Scientist%20CSIR-NISTADS%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr.%20Dinesh%20C%20Sharma%20Journalist%20%26amp%3B%20Author%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProf.%20Gauhar%20Raza%20Former%20Chief%20Scientist%20C