https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fisrael-presses-on-with-settlement-plans-despite-us-criticism%2Farticleshow%2F108072385.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Building%20the%20Yard%3A%20Policy%20Considerations%20for%20AI%20in%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F08091601%2Fartificial-intelligence-2167835_1280.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EArtificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%20has%20immense%20potential%20to%20enhance%20human%20capabilities%20and%20drive%20growth%20in%20several%20industries.%20It%20is%20projected%20to%20greatly%20improve%20governance%2C%20healthcare%2C%20and%20education%20outcomes.%20However%2C%20this%20potential%20may%20not%20be%20realised%20if%20the%20building%20blocks%20of%20AI%20remain%20concentrated%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20a%20few%20dominant%20companies%20or%20the%20countries%20in%20which%20they%20are%20located.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20priorities%20for%20AI%20adoption%20in%20India%20can%20be%20quite%20different.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penguin.co.in%2Fbook%2Fin-service-of-the-republic%2F%5C%22%3EVijay%20Kelkar%20and%20Ajay%20Shah%20propose%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20toughest%20challenges%20for%20a%20state%20%E2%80%93%20such%20as%20the%20tax%20system%20%E2%80%93%20involve%20processes%20that%20feature%20a%20high%20number%20of%20transactions%2C%20the%20need%20for%20discretion%2C%20high%20stakes%20for%20individuals%2C%20and%20some%20degree%20of%20secrecy.%20AI%20adoption%20could%20reduce%20the%20complexity%20of%20such%20challenges%20on%20some%20of%20these%20dimensions%2C%20such%20as%20the%20transaction%20volume%20and%20discretion.%20This%20makes%20it%20easier%20to%20overcome%20state%20capacity%20limitations%20and%20deliver%20better%20governance%20and%20public%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20widespread%20AI%20adoption%20could%20also%20negatively%20affect%20the%20availability%20of%20low-skilled%20jobs%20upon%20which%20a%20large%20part%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20labour%20force%20depends.%20Thus%2C%20the%20opportunities%20and%20challenges%20for%20India%20might%20be%20significantly%20different%20from%20those%20of%20developed%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETechnology%20and%20geopolitics%20are%20becoming%20increasingly%20intertwined.%20Many%20countries%20have%20identified%20critical%20and%20emerging%20technologies%20that%20are%20essential%20for%20national%20security%20and%20economic%20growth.%20AI%20features%20on%20the%20lists%20of%20all%20countries%20that%20have%20made%20such%20declarations%2C%20including%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftrumpwhitehouse.archives.gov%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2FNational-Strategy-for-CET.pdf%5C%22%3EUnited%20States%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fgovernment%2Fpublications%2Fthe-uk-as-a-science-and-technology-superpower%2Fthe-uk-as-a-science-and-technology-superpower-accessible-html-version-of-letter%5C%22%3EUnited%20Kingdom%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdefence-industry-space.ec.europa.eu%2Fsystem%2Ffiles%2F2023-10%2FC_2023_6689_1_EN_annexe_acte_autonome_part1_v9.pdf%5C%22%3EEuropean%20Union%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.industry.gov.au%2Fpublications%2Flist-critical-technologies-national-interest%5C%22%3EAustralia%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.europarl.europa.eu%2FRegData%2Fetudes%2FATAG%2F2023%2F751417%2FEPRS_ATA(2023)751417_EN.pdf%5C%22%3EJapan%3C%2Fa%3E.%20These%20technologies%20are%20not%20just%20an%20area%20of%20focus%20but%20also%20of%20strategic%20interest.%20For%20instance%2C%20US%20policymakers%20are%20operationalising%20the%20idea%20of%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fbriefing-room%2Fspeeches-remarks%2F2022%2F10%2F13%2Fremarks-by-national-security-advisor-jake-sullivan-on-the-biden-harris-administrations-national-security-strategy%2F%5C%22%3Ea%20small%20yard%20with%20a%20high%20fence%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20for%20critical%20technologies%2C%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20keeping%20the%20chokepoints%20for%20foundational%20technologies%20under%20US%20control.%20From%20their%20longstanding%20approach%20of%20staying%20a%20few%20generations%20ahead%20of%20rivals%20in%20critical%20technologies%2C%20the%20American%20focus%20is%20now%20to%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fbriefing-room%2Fspeeches-remarks%2F2022%2F09%2F16%2Fremarks-by-national-security-advisor-jake-sullivan-at-the-special-competitive-studies-project-global-emerging-technologies-summit%2F%5C%22%3Emaintain%20as%20large%20of%20a%20lead%20as%20possible%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20these%20considerations%2C%20for%20India%20to%20pursue%20its%20national%20interests%2C%20it%20will%20have%20to%20find%20ways%20to%20maintain%20strategic%20autonomy%20with%20respect%20to%20this%20critical%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EInputs%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20development%20of%20AI%20systems%20requires%20different%20inputs%3A%20data%2C%20computation%2C%20models%2C%20and%20applications.%20These%20inputs%20can%20be%20visualized%20as%20layers%2C%20with%20data%20and%20computation%20contributing%20to%20the%20model%2C%20which%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20supports%20the%20applications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F28150030%2Fimage-1879.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22818%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F28150030%2Fimage-1879.png%20607w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F28150030%2Fimage-1879-300x246.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-699309%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22670%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EFigure%201%3A%20The%20components%20of%20the%20AI%20supply%20chain%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompanies%20involved%20in%20developing%20AI%20models%20or%20applications%20face%20entry%20barriers%20at%20each%20of%20these%20stages.%20It%20is%20not%20uncommon%20for%20a%20single%20company%20to%20control%20multiple%20stages%20through%20vertical%20integration.%20For%20instance%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fgovernment%2Fpublications%2Fai-foundation-models-initial-report%5C%22%3EGoogle%20exemplifies%20a%20high%20level%20of%20integration%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20the%20different%20stages%20of%20the%20supply%20chain.%20Its%20operations%20range%20from%20developing%20and%20training%20its%20own%20AI%20models%20on%20proprietary%20computing%20infrastructure%20using%20vast%20amounts%20of%20data%2C%20including%20proprietary%20data.%20It%20also%20offers%20cloud%20services%20and%20has%20integrated%20its%20AI%20systems%20into%20various%20applications%20for%20both%20web%20and%20Android%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20this%20context%2C%20if%20India%20is%20to%20build%20a%20thriving%20domestic%20industry%20with%20local%20companies%20that%20can%20compete%20with%20global%20giants%2C%20AI%20governance%20will%20need%20to%20ensure%20unfettered%20access%20to%20the%20different%20stages%20of%20the%20supply%20chain.%20A%20number%20of%20primary%20considerations%20are%20necessary%20for%20each%20stage%20of%20the%20supply%20chain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EData%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModels%20trained%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farxiv.org%2Fabs%2F2101.00027%5C%22%3Elarge%2C%20diverse%2C%20and%20high-quality%20data%20sets%20tend%20to%20perform%20better%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Studies%20estimate%20that%20for%20training%20large%20language%20models%2C%20high-quality%20data%20from%20sources%20such%20as%20books%2C%20academic%20papers%2C%20news%20articles%2C%20and%20Wikipedia%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farxiv.org%2Fabs%2F2211.04325%5C%22%3Elikely%20to%20be%20exhausted%20by%202027%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Thus%2C%20access%20to%20proprietary%20data%20can%20be%20a%20key%20differentiator%20for%20training%20AI%20models.%20This%20includes%20data%20such%20as%20the%20extensive%20code%20repositories%20available%20on%20GitHub%2C%20the%20sorted%20and%20categorised%20web%20index%20compiled%20by%20search%20engines%20from%20their%20web%20crawling%20activities%20or%20the%20audio%20and%20video%20recordings%20from%20video%20conferencing%20applications%20such%20as%20Zoom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBig%20tech%20platforms%20tend%20to%20be%20monopolies%20or%20duopolies%20due%20to%20the%20network%20effects.%20This%20market%20consolidation%20is%20evident%20across%20various%20platforms%2C%20ranging%20from%20search%20engines%20and%20social%20media%20to%20ride-sharing%20and%20food-delivery%20services.%20The%20scale%20and%20insight%20into%20user%20behavior%20from%20access%20to%20proprietary%20data%20help%20these%20companies%20innovate%20better%20than%20competitors.%20When%20developing%20AI%20applications%2C%20access%20to%20proprietary%20data%20gives%20these%20companies%20an%20edge.%20It%20also%20helps%20them%20integrate%20the%20AI%20applications%20into%20their%20existing%20offerings%2C%20thereby%20further%20consolidating%20market%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResearch%20also%20shows%20that%20issues%20with%20fairness%20exist%20in%20AI%20use%20cases%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F31649194%2F%5C%22%3Emedical%20diagnoses%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fproceedings.mlr.press%2Fv81%2Fbuolamwini18a%2Fbuolamwini18a.pdf%5C%22%3Egender%20classification%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.science.org%2Fdoi%2F10.1126%2Fsciadv.aao5580%5C%22%3Erecidivism%20prediction%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20other%20areas%20where%20certain%20groups%20are%20underrepresented%20in%20the%20training%20data.%20This%20can%20lead%20to%20higher%20error%20rates%20and%20biased%20outcomes%20for%20minorities%2C%20women%2C%20the%20elderly%2C%20and%20vulnerable%20populations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20India%E2%80%99s%20incredible%20diversity%2C%20the%20government%20could%20play%20an%20important%20role%20in%20creating%20publicly%20accessible%20open%20datasets%20that%20are%20representative%20of%20the%20population.%20Such%20datasets%20can%20have%20significant%20positive%20externalities%20for%20both%20research%20and%20commercial%20applications.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbhashini.gov.in%2Fabout-bhashini%5C%22%3EBhashini%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20one%20such%20initiative%20under%20the%20Indian%20government%20that%20attempts%20to%20capture%20the%20diversity%20of%20Indian%20languages%20and%20provide%20open-source%20databases%20and%20tools%20for%20real-time%20translation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EComputation%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAI%20training%20and%20usage%20typically%20relies%20on%20cloud%20computing%20services%20for%20computational%20infrastructure%2C%20a%20preferred%20choice%20for%20developers%20and%20users%20over%20owning%20the%20hardware.%20Cloud%20Service%20Providers%20(CSPs)%20often%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fainowinstitute.org%2Fpublication%2Fpolicy%2Fcompute-and-ai%5C%22%3Eoffer%20substantial%20discounts%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20computing%20resources%20for%20AI%20research%20and%20development%2C%20aiming%20to%20secure%20a%20strong%20market%20position%20as%20the%20sector%20expands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20its%20advantages%2C%20this%20model%20raises%20concerns.%20Due%20to%20the%20economies%20of%20scale%2C%20major%20CSPs%20such%20as%20Amazon%20Web%20Services%2C%20Microsoft%20Azure%2C%20and%20Google%20Cloud%20dominate%20the%20market%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcanalys.com%2Fnewsroom%2Fglobal-cloud-services-q3-2023%5C%22%3Ecollectively%20holding%20a%2065%25%20share%20globally%3C%2Fa%3E.%20While%20this%20market%20concentration%20is%20not%20a%20cause%20for%20concern%2C%20the%20leading%20CSPs%20also%20compete%20in%20other%20stages%20of%20the%20AI%20supply%20chain%2C%20including%20developing%20models%20and%20applications.%20Ensuring%20that%20vertical%20integration%20with%20cloud%20computing%20services%20does%20not%20hinder%20competition%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20supply%20chain%20is%20crucial.%20Competition%20regulators%20%E2%80%93%20including%20in%20India%20%E2%80%93%20must%20be%20vigilant%20about%20anti-competitive%20practices%20such%20as%20restrictive%20contracts%2C%20high%20costs%20for%20switching%20services%2C%20or%20unfair%20pricing%20strategies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20upstream%2C%20NVIDIA%2C%20a%20chip%20manufacturer%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.networkworld.com%2Farticle%2F971778%2Fnvidia-still-crushing-the-data-center-market.html%5C%22%3Eholds%20more%20than%2090%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20market%20share%20for%20GPUs%2C%20the%20semiconductor%20chips%20essential%20for%20AI-related%20tasks.%20This%20market%20dominance%20stems%20from%20NVIDIA%E2%80%99s%20early%20entry%20into%20the%20market%20and%20the%20widespread%20adoption%20of%20its%20proprietary%20computing%20platform%2C%20CUDA.%20While%20intense%20competition%20is%20likely%20to%20create%20alternatives%20in%20the%20long%20term%2C%20this%20remains%20a%20geopolitical%20risk%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20mitigated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EModels%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bain.com%2Finsights%2Ffrom-buzz-to-reality-the-accelerating-pace-of-ai-in-india%2F%5C%22%3E%20report%20from%20Bain%20%26amp%3B%20Company%3C%2Fa%3E%20highlights%20that%20India%20is%20a%20leading%20AI%20talent%20hub%2C%20accounting%20for%2016%25%20of%20the%20global%20AI%20workforce%2C%20and%20positioning%20it%20among%20the%20top%20three%20in%20the%20world.%20However%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20notable%20scarcity%20of%20top-tier%20AI%20researchers%20in%20India%2C%20those%20engaged%20in%20generating%20intellectual%20property%20or%20in%20designing%20and%20training%20AI%20algorithms.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmacropolo.org%2Fdigital-projects%2Fthe-global-ai-talent-tracker%2F%5C%22%3EResearch%20by%20MacroPolo%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20US%20think%20tank%2C%20indicates%20that%20over%2080%20percent%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20premier%20AI%20researchers%20relocate%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20trends%20suggest%20that%20due%20to%20the%20shortfall%20in%20specialised%20skills%2C%20coupled%20with%20the%20barriers%20in%20the%20data%20and%20computation%20stages%2C%20Indian%20companies%20%E2%80%93%20which%20rely%20heavily%20on%20Indian%20talent%20%E2%80%93%20would%20find%20it%20challenging%20to%20create%20world%20class%20models.%20However%2C%20they%20will%20be%20able%20to%20compete%20effectively%20in%20other%20engineering%20skill-based%20tasks%20such%20as%20developing%20applications%20based%20on%20AI%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20developing%20cutting-edge%20AI%20models%20demands%20substantial%20data%2C%20computing%20power%2C%20and%20technical%20expertise%2C%20and%20the%20industry%20can%20mobilize%20these%20resources%20better%20than%20academia.%20This%20trend%20is%20underscored%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faiindex.stanford.edu%2Freport%2F%5C%22%3EStanford%20AI%20Index%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20reveals%20that%20in%202022%2C%20industry%20entities%20produced%20thirty-two%20significant%20machine%20learning%20models%2C%20in%20contrast%20to%20academia%2C%20which%20contributed%20only%20three.%20Thus%2C%20government%20interventions%20to%20build%20AI%20capabilities%20should%20consider%20both%20the%20industry%20and%20academia%20as%20key%20contributors%20to%20innovation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EApplication%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20addressing%20concerns%20in%20other%20stages%20of%20the%20AI%20ecosystem%20will%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20a%20competitive%20market%20in%20the%20application%20stage.%20However%2C%20a%20framework%20to%20better%20manage%20risks%20associated%20with%20AI%20systems%20is%20required%20to%20ensure%20they%20are%20built%20responsibly.%20Alignment%20with%20AI%20risk%20management%20frameworks%2C%20such%20as%20the%20one%20developed%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fairc.nist.gov%2FAI_RMF_Knowledge_Base%2FPlaybook%5C%22%3EUS%E2%80%99s%20National%20Institute%20of%20Standards%20and%20Technology%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20can%20help%20systematically%20assess%20and%20mitigate%20risks%20across%20the%20development%20life%20cycle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20global%20efforts%20are%20underway%20to%20better%20understand%20and%20govern%20AI%2C%20the%20Indian%20state%20needs%20to%20consider%20its%20unique%20conditions%20and%20the%20current%20geopolitical%20climate%20to%20take%20measures%20to%20ensure%20access%20to%20the%20technology%20and%20the%20benefits%20it%20has%20to%20offer.%20This%20article%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftakshashila.org.in%2Fresearch%2Fa-pathway-to-ai-governance%5C%22%3Ediscussion%20document%20on%20which%20it%20is%20based%3C%2Fa%3E%20focus%20on%20AI%20governance%20from%20a%20national%20interest%20perspective%2C%20highlighting%20some%20of%20the%20primary%20concerns%20at%20each%20stage%20of%20the%20AI%20supply%20chain.%20Recognizing%20these%20concerns%20is%20crucial%2C%20as%20they%20lay%20the%20groundwork%20for%20shaping%20targeted%20policy%20measures%20tailored%20to%20each%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EBharath%20Reddy%20is%20a%20researcher%20in%20the%20High-Tech%20Geopolitics%20programme%20at%20the%20Takshashila%20Institution.%20He%20is%20a%20co-author%20with%20Nitin%20Pai%2C%20Satya%20Shoova%20Sahu%2C%20Rijesh%20Panicker%20and%20Sridhar%20Krishna%20on%20Takshashila%E2%80%99s%20discussion%20document%20on%20AI%20Governance.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIndia%20in%20Transition%3C%2Fem%3E%20(%3Cem%3EIiT%3C%2Fem%3E)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcasi.sas.upenn.edu%2Fiit%2Fbharathreddy%5C%22%3Eis%20published%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Center%20for%20the%20Advanced%20Study%20of%20India%20(CASI)%20of%20the%20University%20of%20Pennsylvania.%20All%20viewpoints%2C%20positions%2C%20and%20conclusions%20expressed%20in%20%3Cem%3EIiT%3C%2Fem%3E%20are%20solely%20those%20of%20the%20author(s)%20and%20not%20specifically%20those%20of%20CASI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcasi.sas.upenn.edu%2Fiit%2Fbharathreddy%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20CASI%20website.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709114794000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F08091601%2Fartificial-intelligence-2167835_1280.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fbuilding-the-yard-policy-considerations-for-ai-in-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22AI%20is%20projected%20to%20greatly%20improve%20governance%2C%20healthcare%2C%20and%20education%20outcomes.%20However%2C%20this%20potential%20may%20not%20be%20realised%20if%20the%20building%20blocks%20of%20AI%20remain%20concentrated%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20a%20few%20dominant%20firms%20or%20the%20countries%20in%20which%20they%20are%20located.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fbuilding-the-yard-policy-considerations-for-ai-in-india%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Teaching%20kids%20about%20money%3A%207%20valuable%20lessons%20for%20parents%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709113447000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108071100%2Cimgsize-890048.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Ffinancial-literacy%2Fsavings%2Fteaching-kids-about-money-7-valuable-lessons-for-parents%2Farticleshow%2F108071158.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Teaching%20kids%20about%20money%20is%20crucial%20for%20financial%20literacy.%20Parents%20should%20lead%20by%20example%20and%20teach%20the%20importance%20of%20non-material%20joys.%20Avoid%20mindless%20gifting%20and%20assigning%20a%20price%20tag%20to%20everyday%20tasks.%20Assert%20authority%20and%20establish%20boundaries.%20Teach%20about%20opportunity%20cost%20and%20fairness.%20Allow%20kids%20to%20make%20choices.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20BUSINESS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Ffinancial-literacy%2Fsavings%2Fteaching-kids-about-money-7-valuable-lessons-for-parents%2Farticleshow%2F108071158.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UN%20Human%20Rights%20Council's%2055th%20Summit%20Kicks%20Off%20with%20'Renewed%20Action%20for%20Peace'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F28140350%2Fimage1170x530cropped.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EUnited%20Nations%20High%20Commissioner%20for%20Human%20Rights%2C%20Volker%20T%C3%BCrk%2C%20has%20issued%20%E2%80%9Ceight%20key%20messages%E2%80%9D%20towards%20protecting%20human%20rights%20across%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20opening%20of%20the%2055th%20session%20of%20the%20Human%20Rights%20Council%2C%20which%20kicked%20off%20on%20Monday%2C%20February%2026%2C%20T%C3%BCrk%E2%80%99s%20eight%20key%20messages%20are%20towards%20guiding%20renewed%20action%20for%20peace%3B%20economies%20that%20work%20for%20people%20and%20planet%3B%20effective%20governance%3B%20and%20guardrails%20for%20digital%20and%20scientific%20progress.%20The%20messages%20are%20part%20of%20a%20vision%20statement%20released%20by%20T%C3%BCrk%20and%20titled%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohchr.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2024-02%2Fhc-visionstatement-2024.pdf%5C%22%3EHuman%20Rights%3A%20A%20Path%20for%20Solutions%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20vision%20statement%20helps%20broaden%20the%20way%20the%20world%20thinks%20about%20rights%2C%20in%20ways%20that%20can%20transform%20societies%20and%20the%20global%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2055th%20session%20of%20the%20Human%20Rights%20Council%20kicked%20off%20on%20Monday%2C%20February%2026%2C%20and%20will%20continue%20until%20April%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReproduced%20below%20is%20the%20full%20statement%20of%20Volker%20T%C3%BCrk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20of%20the%20General%20Assembly%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnSecretary-General%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnPresident%20of%20the%20Human%20Rights%20Council%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnExcellencies%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnDistinguished%20delegates%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20Council%20enters%20into%20session%20at%20a%20time%20of%20seismic%20global%20shocks.%20Conflicts%20are%20battering%20the%20lives%20of%20millions%20of%20civilians%2C%20and%20carving%20even%20deeper%20fault-lines%20across%20and%20between%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pain%20and%20the%20slaughter%20of%20so%20many%20people%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20Ukraine%2C%20Sudan%2C%20Myanmar%2C%20Haiti%20and%20so%20many%20other%20places%20around%20the%20world%20are%20unbearable.%20And%20when%20we%20discuss%2C%20in%20the%20coming%20weeks%2C%20country%20after%20country%2C%20we%20must%20remember%20their%20faces%20and%20their%20anguish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20time%20of%20such%20atrocious%20violations%2C%20is%20it%20na%C3%AFve%20to%20demand%20that%20all%20States%20uphold%20their%20human%20rights%20commitments%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOr%20is%20it%20crucial%20%E2%80%93%20the%20most%20important%2C%20the%20most%20consequential%2C%20the%20most%20urgent%20task%20that%20any%20of%20us%20could%20possibly%20undertake%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAre%20these%20not%2C%20in%20reality%2C%20our%20only%20guarantees%2C%20essential%2C%20and%20profoundly%20rooted%2C%20anchoring%20our%20societies%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20turbulence%20and%20disarray%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMember%20States%20and%20many%20partners%20came%20together%20at%20the%20December%20high-level%20event%20to%20commemorate%2075%20years%20of%20the%20Universal%20Declaration%20of%20Human%20Rights.%20This%20was%20an%20important%20moment%20of%20reflection%20on%20the%20successes%20and%20failures%20to%20implement%20human%20rights%2C%20and%20how%20we%20can%20do%20better%20in%20the%20future.%20It%20was%20the%20culmination%20of%20a%20rich%2C%20year-long%20engagement%20across%20the%20world%20which%20resounded%20with%20demands%20that%20the%20world%20deliver%20on%20the%20promises%20of%20the%20Universal%20Declaration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDemands%20for%20action%20to%20end%20conflicts.%20To%20eradicate%20discrimination.%20To%20heal%20our%20distorted%20economies%20and%20our%20battered%20environment.%20Demands%20for%20quality%20services%2C%20such%20as%20education%20and%20healthcare.%20For%20an%20end%20to%20corruption.%20For%20a%20voice%20in%20one%E2%80%99s%20own%20future.%20And%20over%20and%20over%20again%2C%20demands%20that%20States%20change%20course%20%E2%80%93%20to%20bring%20humanity%20the%20benefits%20of%20greater%20justice%2C%20more%20inclusive%20development%2C%20greater%20equality%2C%20and%20peace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%20that%20two-day%20event%2C%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3E153%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0Member%20States%20had%20issued%20concrete%20pledges%2C%20alongside%20civil%20society%20groups%2C%20UN%20bodies%2C%20businesses%20and%20others%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohchr.org%2Fen%2Fhuman-rights-75%2Fpledge%2Fhuman-rights-75-pledges%5C%22%3Eover%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3E770%20pledges%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20all.%20They%20ranged%20from%20commitments%20to%20increase%20women%E2%80%99s%20leadership%20and%20employment%20equality%2C%20to%20tackling%20extreme%20poverty%2C%20ensuring%20transitional%20justice%2C%20and%20improving%20access%20to%20education%2C%20healthcare%20and%20social%20protections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20important%20was%20the%20outpouring%20of%20support%20from%20members%20of%20the%20public%2C%20in%20every%20corner%20of%20the%20globe.%20The%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.opensocietyfoundations.org%2Fuploads%2Fbe67f098-4fdf-45ce-adeb-5143e8282d23%2Fbarometer-in-context-strengthening-the-human-rights-system-20231208.pdf%5C%22%3EOpen%20Society%20Barometer%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%93%20a%20survey%20of%20over%2036%2C000%20people%20in%2030%20countries%20%E2%80%93%20found%20that%20the%20vast%20majority%20agreed%20that%20human%20rights%20have%20been%20a%20%E2%80%9Cforce%20for%20good.%E2%80%9D%20In%20other%20words%2C%20the%20silent%20majority%20holds%20to%20the%20human%20rights%20principles%20that%20ensure%20progress%20and%20justice%20across%20all%20societies%2C%20and%20which%20keep%20our%20world%20safe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20I%20am%20pleased%20to%20launch%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohchr.org%2Fen%2Fdocuments%2Foutcome-documents%2Fhuman-rights-path-solutions%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHuman%20Rights%3A%20A%20Path%20for%20Solutions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9C%2C%20the%20distillation%20of%20the%20work%20that%20has%20gone%20into%20our%20commemoration%20year%2C%20in%20the%20hope%20that%20it%20will%20inform%20the%20Summit%20of%20the%20Future.%20It%20sets%20out%20eight%20messages%20to%20guide%20renewed%20action%20for%20peace%3B%20economies%20that%20work%20for%20people%20and%20planet%3B%20effective%20governance%3B%20and%20guardrails%20for%20digital%20and%20scientific%20progress.%20Itbroadens%20the%20way%20we%20think%20about%20rights%2C%20in%20ways%20that%20can%20transform%20societies%20and%20our%20global%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Secretary-General%E2%80%99s%20announcement%20of%20the%20UN%E2%80%99s%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3EProtection%20Pledge%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20and%20the%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3EAgenda%20for%20Protection%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20will%20ensure%20that%20the%20entire%20UN%20gives%20priority%20to%20advancing%20human%20rights%20in%20every%20circumstance%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20challenging.%20I%20look%20forward%20to%20working%20with%20colleagues%20across%20the%20UN%20to%20implement%20this%20Pledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20will%20address%20various%20country%20situations%20throughout%20this%20Council%20session%2C%20and%20in%20particular%2C%20in%20the%20global%20update%20next%20Monday.%20But%20this%20morning%20I%20would%20like%20to%20flag%20two%20overarching%20concerns%20that%20have%20potential%20impact%20on%20all%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20negotiations%20on%20treaties%20on%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3Epandemic%20prevention%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0and%20on%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3Ecybercrime%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20as%20well%20as%20on%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3Eplastic%20pollution%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3B%20and%20global%20discussions%20about%20the%20regulation%20of%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3Eartificial%20intelligence%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%93%20all%20these%20talks%20tare%20currently%20underway%2C%20but%20they%20are%20not%20sufficiently%20taking%20into%20account%20human%20rights%20obligations%2C%20and%20the%20human%20rights%20harms%20that%20could%20be%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20I%20am%20disturbed%20by%20attempts%20to%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3Eundermine%20the%20legitimacy%20and%20work%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20other%20institutions.%20They%20include%20disinformation%20that%20targets%20UN%20humanitarian%20organizations%2C%20UN%20peacekeepers%20and%20my%20Office.%20The%20UN%20has%20become%20a%20lightning%20rod%20for%20manipulative%20propaganda%20and%20a%20scapegoat%20for%20policy%20failures.%20This%20is%20profoundly%20destructive%20of%20the%20common%20good%2C%20and%20it%20callously%20betrays%20the%20many%20people%20whose%20lives%20rely%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20is%20uniquely%20equipped%20to%20enable%20States%20to%20discuss%20and%20resolve%20pressing%20global%20issues%20%E2%80%93%20and%20this%20convening%20power%20is%20particularly%20vital%20now%2C%20when%20the%20magnitude%20of%20conflict%2C%20planetary%20peril%20and%20digital%20transformation%20requires%20urgent%20solutions.%20UN%20humanitarian%20agencies%20assist%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20people%20to%20stay%20alive.%20The%20UN%E2%80%99s%20development%20and%20peace%20work%20is%20absolutely%20crucial%20to%20all%20nations.%20My%20Office%20is%20mandated%20to%20monitor%20and%20report%20on%20human%20rights%20because%20States%20have%20agreed%20that%20rights%20and%20justice%20are%20the%20best%2C%20and%20only%2C%20way%20forward.%20The%20work%20of%20opening%20dialogues%20and%20protecting%20rights%20is%20not%20comfortable%20for%20everyone%20%E2%80%93%20but%20it%20is%20essential%20to%20all%20of%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20need%20to%20overcome%20the%20binary%20view%20that%20if%20you%20are%20not%20for%20us%2C%20and%20against%20our%20enemies%2C%20then%20you%20too%20must%20be%20an%20enemy.%20Within%20countries%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9Cus%20versus%20them%E2%80%9D%20illogic%20is%20creating%20increasingly%20dangerous%20and%20combustible%20divisions%2C%20especially%20in%20pre-electoral%20periods%2C%20of%20which%20there%20are%20many%20this%20year.%20All%20this%20is%20a%20politics%20of%20distraction%2C%20of%20warmongering%2C%20which%20slowly%20numbs%20our%20deepest%20sense%20of%20compassion.%20Especially%20at%20a%20time%20of%20deep%20division%20and%20fear%2C%20seeing%20the%20humanity%20in%20the%20other%20is%20the%20lifeline%20that%20can%20tug%20us%20away%20from%20disaster.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20draw%20strength%20and%20hope%20from%20last%20year%E2%80%99s%20powerful%20tributes%20to%20the%20Universal%20Declaration%20of%20Human%20Rights%20%E2%80%93%20the%20testimonies%20we%20heard%20from%20so%20many%20people%2C%20and%20the%20significant%20pledges%20that%20were%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20power%20of%20human%20rights%20is%20rooted%20in%20their%20universality%20%E2%80%93%20the%20equal%20value%20of%20every%20human%20life%20that%20is%20at%20their%20core.%20The%20same%20human%20rights%20standards%20must%20be%20deployed%20everywhere%2C%20and%20they%20must%20be%20benchmarks%20for%20future%20progress%20%E2%80%93%20not%20high-water%20marks%20from%20which%20we%20can%20recede.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20human%20being%20is%20born%20equal.%20All%20victims%20are%20equally%20deserving%20of%20justice.%20No-one%20can%20be%20left%20behind.%20And%20nobody%20is%20above%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThank%20you%2C%20Mr%20President.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709112561000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F28140350%2Fimage1170x530cropped.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fun-human-rights-councils-55th-summit-kicks-off-with-renewed-action-for-peace%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22United%20Nations%C2%A0High%20Commissioner%20for%20Human%20Rights%2C%C2%A0Volker%20T%C3%BCrk%2C%20released%20a%20new%20vision%20statement%20offering%20solutions%20to%20pressing%20human%20rights%20concerns%20globally.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fun-human-rights-councils-55th-summit-kicks-off-with-renewed-action-for-peace%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22With%20Eyes%20on%20Gaza%2C%20Ukraine%2C%20UN%20Chief%20Launches%20Rights%20Protection%20Pledge%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F28144500%2Fimage1170x530cropped-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20all-out%20Israeli%20offensive%20on%20Rafah%20would%20spell%20the%20end%20for%20UN-led%20humanitarian%20relief%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza%2C%20UN%20Secretary-General%20Ant%C3%B3nio%20Guterres%20warned%20on%20Monday%2C%20in%20a%20wide-ranging%20call%20to%20the%20international%20community%20to%20fulfil%20its%20%E2%80%9Cprimary%20responsibility%E2%80%9D%20of%20promoting%20and%20protecting%20human%20rights%20everywhere%20and%20for%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohchr.org%2FEN%2FHRBodies%2FHRC%2FPages%2FHome.aspx%5C%22%3EHuman%20Rights%20Council%3C