rm%20of%20the%2015-member%20body%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Ccomposition%20and%20working%20methods%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20call%20for%20reasoned%20and%20long-term%20solutions%20to%20these%20conflicts%20and%20other%20serious%20threats%20to%20human%20rights%20around%20the%20world%2C%20the%20UN%20chief%20emphasized%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Fen%2Fcommon-agenda%2Fsummit-of-the-future%5C%22%3ESummit%20of%20the%20Future%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20September%20would%20be%20the%20ideal%20opportunity%20for%20Member%20States%20%E2%80%9Cto%20step%20up%20and%20re-commit%20to%20working%20for%20peace%20and%20security%20rooted%20in%20human%20rights%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProtection%20pledge%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr.%20Guterres%20also%20pledged%20the%20global%20body%E2%80%99s%20system-wide%20support%20to%20all%20governments%20in%20this%20endeavour%2C%20announcing%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20Agenda%20for%20Protection%2C%20in%20partnership%20with%20the%20UN%20human%20rights%20office%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohchr.org%2FEN%2Fpages%2Fhome.aspx%5C%22%3EOHCHR%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnder%20this%20Agenda%2C%20the%20United%20Nations%2C%20across%20the%20full%20spectrum%20of%20our%20work%2C%20will%20act%20as%20one%20to%20prevent%20human%20rights%20violations%20and%20to%20identify%20and%20respond%20to%20them%20when%20they%20take%20place%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Secretary-General%20said.%20%E2%80%9CThat%20is%20the%20Protection%20Pledge%20of%20all%20United%20Nations%20bodies%3A%20to%20do%20their%20utmost%20to%20protect%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisinformation%20target%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWelcoming%20the%20UN%20chief%E2%80%99s%20initiative%20and%20offering%20to%20help%20advance%20people%E2%80%99s%20fundamental%20rights%20%E2%80%9Cin%20every%20circumstance%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20challenging%E2%80%9D%2C%20UN%20High%20Commissioner%20for%20Human%20Rights%20T%C3%BCrk%20cautioned%20that%20the%20global%20body%E2%80%99s%20work%20was%20at%20serious%20risk%20from%20%E2%80%9Ccontinued%20attempts%20to%20undermine%20the%20legitimacy%20and%20work%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20and%20other%20institutions%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr.%20T%C3%BCrk%20explained%20that%20these%20attempts%20%E2%80%9Cinclude%20disinformation%20that%20targets%20UN%20humanitarian%20organizations%2C%20UN%20peacekeepers%20and%20my%20Office.%20The%20UN%20has%20become%20a%20lightning%20rod%20for%20manipulative%20propaganda%20and%20a%20scapegoat%20for%20policy%20failures%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20malign%20influence%20was%20%E2%80%9Cprofoundly%20destructive%20of%20the%20common%20good%2C%20and%20it%20callously%20betrays%20the%20many%20people%20whose%20lives%20rely%20on%20it%E2%80%9D%2C%20insisted%20the%20UN%20High%20Commissioner%20for%20Human%20Rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EOpening%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FHRC55%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23HRC55%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20clear%20message%20to%20Governments%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERemember%20the%20faces%2C%20the%20pain%20of%20those%20being%20battered%20by%20conflicts%20around%20the%20world%20%26amp%3B%20uphold%20the%20human%20rights%20commitments%20that%20can%20tug%20us%20away%20from%20disaster.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERights%20%26amp%3B%20justice%20are%20our%20lifeline%2C%20the%20best%20%26amp%3B%20only%20way%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Volker%20T%C3%BCrk%20(%40volker_turk)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fvolker_turk%2Fstatus%2F1762044556458025092%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2026%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGeneral%20Assembly%20chief%E2%80%99s%20alert%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEchoing%20warnings%20that%20international%20humanitarian%20law%20and%20even%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Fen%2Fcharter-united-nations%2Findex.html%5C%22%3EUN%20Charter%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20coming%20under%20increasing%20threat%20around%20the%20world%2C%20the%20head%20of%20the%20UN%20General%20Assembly%2C%20Mr.%20Francis%2C%20told%20the%20Human%20Rights%20Council%20that%20it%20was%20time%20for%20all%20global%20citizens%20to%20%E2%80%9Cdo%20our%20part%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%2075%20years%20after%20the%20adoption%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Fen%2Funiversal-declaration-human-rights%2F%5C%22%3EUniversal%20Declaration%20of%20Human%20Rights%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9Chumanity%E2%80%99s%20cherished%20Magna%20Carta%E2%80%9D%20%C2%A0%E2%80%93%20%C2%A0conflict%20and%20the%20impact%20of%20climate%C2%A0change%20%E2%80%9Cincluding%20the%20existential%20threat%20of%20sea-level%20rise%E2%80%9D%20had%20left%20300%20million%20people%20in%20dire%20need%20of%20humanitarian%20assistance%2C%20some%20114%20million%20of%20them%20being%20refugees%20and%20other%20displaced%20people%2C%20he%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20must%20not%20simply%20stand%20by%20as%20callous%20observers%20lest%20we%20be%20seen%20as%20complicit%20in%20the%20expanding%20web%20of%20dehumanization%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20must%20do%20our%20part.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20the%20crisis%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20the%20UN%20General%20Assembly%20President%20said%20that%20the%20suffering%20of%20innocent%20civilians%20in%20Gaza%20had%20reached%20an%20%E2%80%9Cunbearable%20tipping%20point%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E80%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20enclave%E2%80%99s%20population%20had%20been%20displaced%20and%20was%20now%20%E2%80%9Cteetering%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20starvation%20and%20trapped%20in%20the%20depths%20of%20an%20impending%20though%20avoidable%20public%20health%20catastrophe%E2%80%9D%2C%20Mr.%20Francis%20told%20the%20forum%E2%80%99s%2047%20Member%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20war%20continues%20in%20Gaza%2C%20triggered%20by%20Hamas-led%20attacks%20that%20left%20some%201%2C200%20dead%20and%20more%20than%20250%20taken%20hostage%20on%207%20October%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20most%20vulnerable%20suffer%20most%E2%80%9D%2C%20Mr.%20Francis%20continued.%20%E2%80%9CHostages%20and%20their%20families%20are%20living%20in%20anguish%2C%20women%20and%20children%20are%20facing%20desperate%20and%20uncertain%20futures%2C%20and%20innocent%20civilians%20are%20unjustly%20caught%20in%20life%20threatening%20crossfire.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20the%20name%20of%20humanity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20help%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20%E2%80%93%20not%20only%20in%20Gaza%20but%20in%20Haiti%2C%20Myanmar%2C%20Sudan%2C%20the%20wider%20Sahel%20and%20Yemen%20%E2%80%93%20the%20General%20Assembly%20President%20insisted%3A%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20must%20not%20fail%20the%20victims%20%E2%80%93%20the%20victims%20of%20human%20rights%20violations%E2%80%A6%20We%20must%20never%20tolerate%20or%20ignore%20the%20flagrant%20disregard%20for%20the%20rights%20and%20freedoms%20our%20forebearers%20worked%20so%20arduously%20to%20define%20and%20to%20codify.%20Nor%20should%20we%20ignore%20the%20systemic%20impunity%20with%20which%20it%20is%20perpetrated.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr.%20Francis%20also%20insisted%20on%20the%20need%20for%20an%20%E2%80%9Cimmediate%20humanitarian%20ceasefire%E2%80%9D%20in%20Gaza%20and%20for%20humanitarian%20corridors%20to%20deliver%20aid%20to%20some%201.5%20million%20homeless%20Palestinians%20%E2%80%9Cin%20the%20name%20of%20humanity%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20appeal%20by%20the%20President%20of%20the%20General%20Assembly%20came%20days%20after%20receiving%20a%20letter%20from%20the%20head%20of%20the%20UN%20agency%20for%20Palestinians%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unrwa.org%2F%5C%22%3EUNRWA%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20warning%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmonumental%20disaster%E2%80%9D%20in%20Gaza%20and%20the%20West%20Bank%20amid%20repeated%20Israeli%20calls%20to%20dismantle%20it%20and%20the%20freezing%20of%20%24450%20million%20in%20funding%20by%20dozens%20of%20donors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20implore%C2%A0%20donor%20States%20to%20uphold%20and%20sustain%20their%20contributions%20to%20the%20critical%20funding%20necessary%20for%20UNRWA%20to%20discharge%20its%20mandated%20responsibilities%20to%20the%20Palestinians.%20Even%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20the%20current%20extraordinary%20challenges%2C%20UNRWA%20has%20been%20and%20continues%20to%20be%20an%20indispensable%20lifeline%20of%20support%20to%20the%20Palestinians%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr.%20Francis%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.un.org%2Fen%2Fstory%2F2024%2F02%2F1146942%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20UN%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709112095000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F28144500%2Fimage1170x530cropped-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fwith-eyes-on-gaza-ukraine-un-chief-launches-rights-protection-pledge%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20UN%20chief%20said%20that%20any%20further%20extension%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20ground%20operation%20in%20the%20south%20of%20Gaza%20%E2%80%9Cwould%20not%20only%20be%20terrifying%20for%20more%20than%20a%20million%20Palestinian%20civilians%20sheltering%20there%3B%20it%20would%20put%20the%20final%20nail%20in%20the%20coffin%20of%20our%20aid%20programmes%E2%80%9D.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fwith-eyes-on-gaza-ukraine-un-chief-launches-rights-protection-pledge%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22North%20Korea's%20first%20spy%20satellite%20is%20'alive'%2C%20can%20manoeuvre%2C%20expert%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A170