government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fcji-ranjan-gogoi-rajya-sabha-nomination%5C%22%3Enominated%3C%2Fa%3E%20former%20Chief%20Justice%20Ranjan%20Gogoi%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20barely%20four%20months%20after%20he%20retired%20as%20CJI%20from%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20Justice%20Ashok%20Bhushan%2C%20who%20retired%20in%20July%202021%20was%20made%20head%20of%20the%20National%20Company%20Law%20Appellate%20Tribunal%20later%20that%20year%20%E2%80%93%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fonly-one-of-5-sc-judges-who-passed-ayodhya-verdict-to-attend-ram-temple-ceremony%5C%22%3Eattended%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Ram%20temple%20consecration%20ceremony%20earlier%20this%20year.%20In%202021%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcontroversial-judge-who-praised-modi-to-be-nhrc-chief-opposition-leader-dissents%5C%22%3Eproposed%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20name%20of%20controversial%20former%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%2C%20Arun%20Kumar%20Mishra%2C%20as%20the%20chairperson%20of%20the%20National%20Human%20Rights%20Commission.%20In%202023%2C%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fretired-sc-judge-s-abdul-nazeer-appointed-as-governor-of-andhra-pradesh%5C%22%3Eappointed%3C%2Fa%3E%20former%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%20Justice%20S.%20Abdul%20Nazeer%20as%20the%20governor%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20four%20months%20after%20he%20retired.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Khanwilkar%20has%20authored%20key%20judgments%20with%20wide-ranging%20impact%20on%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E377%2C%20Aadhaar%2C%20Sabarimala%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20Justice%20Khanwilkar%20had%20been%20part%20of%20the%20five-judge%20constitution%20bench%20headed%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20Dipak%20Misra%20and%20also%20comprising%20Justices%20Rohinton%20Fali%20Nariman%2C%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20and%20Indu%20Malhotra%2C%20that%20decriminalised%20homosexuality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20same%20year%2C%202018%2C%20a%20bench%20with%20Justice%20Khanwilkar%20in%20it%20upheld%20the%20constitutional%20validity%20of%20the%20Aadhaar%20Act.%20The%20majority%20opinion%2C%20authored%20by%20Justice%20Sikri%20was%20on%20behalf%20of%20then%20CJI%20Misra%20and%20Justice%20Khanwilkar.%20The%20petitioners%20had%20said%20that%20the%20exercise%20infringed%20upon%20the%20right%20to%20privacy%20of%20citizens%2C%20something%20that%20the%20court%20did%20not%20agree%20with.%20Since%20then%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.economictimes.com%2Fwealth%2Fsave%2Fthis-new-aadhaar-related-banking-fraud-is-on-the-rise-why-you-need-to-lock-your-aadhaar-biometrics-now%2Farticleshow%2F104575645.cms%5C%22%3EAadhaar%20frauds%20have%20frequently%20made%20news%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20government%20has%20issued%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.economictimes.com%2Fwealth%2Fsave%2Faadhaar-fraud-how-to-prevent-misuse-of-aadhaar-card-details-govt-shares-tips%2Farticleshow%2F103535246.cms%5C%22%3Eguidelines%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20appear%20to%20have%20little%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Khanwilkar%20was%20also%20part%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20which%20in%202018%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsabarimala-review-petition-verdict%23%3A~%3Atext%3DSeptember%252028%252C%25202018%253A%2520The%2520Supreme%2CMalhotra%2520delivers%2520the%2520dissenting%2520judgment.%5C%22%3Eallowed%3C%2Fa%3E%20entry%20of%20women%20into%20the%20Sabarimala%20temple%20in%20Kerala%2C%20saying%20that%20banning%20women%E2%80%99s%20entry%20into%20the%20shrine%20is%20gender%20discrimination%20and%20the%20practice%20violates%20rights%20of%20Hindu%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGujarat%20riots%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Khanwilkar%20was%20part%20of%20the%20bench%20in%202022%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fgujarat-riots-zakia-jafri-plea-supreme-court-clean-chit-modi%5C%22%3Edismissed%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20plea%20of%20Zakia%20Jafri%2C%20the%20wife%20of%20slain%20MP%20Ehsan%20Jafri%2C%20challenging%20the%20Special%20Investigation%20Team%E2%80%99s%20(SIT)%20clean%20chit%20to%2064%20people%2C%20including%20then%20chief%20minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20in%20the%202002%20Gujarat%20riots%20case.%20On%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20verdict%2C%20the%20Gujarat%20Police%20had%20on%20the%20following%20day%2C%20arrested%20activist%20Teesta%20Setalvad%20and%20former%20IPS%20officer%20R.%20B.%20Sreekumar%20on%20charges%20of%20fabricating%20evidence%20linked%20to%20the%20riots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBy%20arresting%20and%20detaining%20Teesta%20and%20constituting%20an%20SIT%20apparently%20to%20investigate%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20malign%20the%20state%20of%20Gujarat%20and%20some%20other%20issues%2C%20I%20wonder%20who%20is%20keeping%20the%20pot%20boiling%2C%E2%80%9D%20former%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%2C%20Justice%20Madan%20Lokur%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fgujarat-police-arrest-teesta-setalvad-activist-who-pursued-2002-riots-case-against-modi%5C%22%3Ewritten%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20controversial%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFCRA%2C%20PMLA%2C%20UAPA%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20Justice%20Khanwilkar%2C%20heading%20a%20three-judge%20bench%2C%20upheld%20the%20Foreign%20Contribution%20(Regulation)%20Amendment%20Act%2C%202020.%20The%20Act%20was%20introduced%20to%20regulate%20NGOs%E2%80%99%20access%20to%20foreign%20donors.%20The%20Modi%20government%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fas-three-more-ngos-lose-fcra-licence-a-relook-at-the-govts-funding-restrictions%5C%22%3Efrequently%20stripped%20organisations%20critical%20of%20it%20off%20its%20FCRA%20licences%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20same%20year%2C%20two%20days%20before%20his%20retirement%2C%20Justice%20Khanwilkar%20delivered%20a%20judgment%20that%20give%20enormous%20powers%20to%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20%E2%80%93%20often%20believed%20to%20be%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20central%20agency%20of%20choice%20in%20the%20alleged%20intimidation%20of%20opposition%20leaders%20and%20activists.%20The%20court%20said%20Section%2019%20that%20deals%20with%20the%20power%20to%20arrest%20does%20not%20suffer%20from%20the%20%E2%80%9Cvice%20of%20arbitrariness%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20Section%205%20of%20the%20Act%20relating%20to%20the%20attachment%20of%20property%20of%20those%20involved%20in%20money%20laundering%20is%20constitutionally%20valid.%20The%20apex%20court%20also%20said%20the%20supply%20of%20Enforcement%20Case%20Information%20Report%20(ECIR)%20in%20every%20case%20to%20the%20person%20concerned%20is%20not%20mandatory.%20The%20ECIR%20is%20the%20ED%E2%80%99s%20equivalent%20of%20a%20police%20FIR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20legal%20scholar%20Gautam%20Bhatia%20had%20noted%20that%20no%20discussion%20of%20Justice%20Khanwilkar%E2%80%99s%20legacy%20can%20not%20include%20the%202019%20judgment%20in%20%3Cem%3ENational%20Investigation%20Agency%20vs%20Zahoor%20Ahmad%20Shah%20Watali%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20involved%20the%20interpretation%20of%20Section%2043(D)(5)%20of%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20Prevention%20Act%2C%20which%20bars%20the%20grant%20of%20bail%20if%20it%20appears%20that%20the%20police%20version%20(through%20the%20case%20diary%20or%20the%20chargesheet)%20against%20the%20accused%20is%2C%20on%20the%20face%20of%20it%2C%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Bhatia%E2%80%99s%20words%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Watali%2C%20Justice%20Khanwilkar%20barred%20all%20courts%20from%20%E2%80%9Cexamining%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9Cdissecting%E2%80%9D%20the%20evidence%2C%20he%20effectively%20made%20the%20grant%20of%20bail%20in%20UAPA%20cases%20borderline%20impossible.%20As%20Sekhri%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheproofofguilt.blogspot.com%2F2019%2F04%2Fbail-in-terror-cases-zahoor-watali-and.html%5C%22%3Ewrote%20at%20the%20time%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20%E2%80%9Cactively%20chose%20a%20legal%20position%20that%20makes%20lengthy%20undertrial%20detention%20more%20likely.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709109059000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F29155631%2FScreenshot-2022-07-29-at-3.56.25-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fjustice-khanwilkar-lokpal-fcra-pmla-uapa-aadhaar-modi%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Justice%20Khanwilkar's%20appointment%20continues%20the%20controversial%20tradition%20of%20top%20post-retirement%20positions%20going%20to%20judges%20of%20the%20highest%20court%20of%20the%20country%20after%20retirement.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fjustice-khanwilkar-lokpal-fcra-pmla-uapa-aadhaar-modi%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Zelenskyy%20to%20rally%20for%20support%2C%20weapons%20at%20Balkan%20security%20meet%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709108428000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108068328%2Cimgsize-707865.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fukrainian-president-volodymyr-zelenskyy-seeks-support-and-weapons-at-balkan-security-meet%2Farticleshow%2F108068187.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108068187.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fukrainian-president-volodymyr-zelenskyy-seeks-support-and-weapons-at-balkan-security-meet%2Farticleshow%2F108068187.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fukrainian-president-volodymyr-zelenskyy-seeks-support-and-weapons-at-balkan-security-meet%2Famp_articleshow%2F108068187.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fukrainian-president-volodymyr-zelenskyy-seeks-support-and-weapons-at-balkan-security-meet%2Famp_articleshow%2F108068187.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manipur%20Assembly%20Session%20Begins%20Amid%20Tight%20Security%3B%20Previous%20Session%20Had%20Lasted%2011%20Minutes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F07195859%2Fmanipur_assembly_session_2_20150625_1176793276.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Amid%20tight%20security%2C%20the%20winter%20session%20of%20the%20Manipur%20assembly%20began%20Wednesday%2C%20February%2028%2C%20in%20Imphal.%20This%20is%20the%20second%20time%20the%20House%20has%20met%20since%20ethnic%20violence%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-violence-reasons-failure-and-solution-q-and-a%5C%22%3Ebroke%20out%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20north-eastern%20state%20in%20May%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20previous%20session%2C%20held%20on%20August%2029%2C%202023%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-assemblys-one-day-session-adjourned-after-11-minutes%5C%22%3Eended%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20just%20eleven%20minutes%20of%20business.%20Neither%20the%2010%20Kuki%20MLAs%20nor%20the%20majority%20of%20the%2010%20Naga%20MLAs%20took%20part%20in%20that%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESignificantly%2C%20the%20session%20had%20ended%20without%20putting%20on%20record%20the%20ongoing%20violence%20that%20had%20led%20to%20the%20absence%20of%20so%20many%20MLAs%20from%20the%20House.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20session%20turned%20into%20an%20exercise%20by%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20merely%20to%20keep%20the%20Opposition%E2%80%99s%20demand%20for%20the%20President%E2%80%99s%20Rule%20in%20Manipur%20at%20bay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20a%20constitutional%20norm%2C%20a%20state%20assembly%20has%20to%20be%20in%20session%20every%20six%20months%2C%20unless%20there%20is%20direct%20central%20rule%20in%20that%20state%20due%20to%20the%20failure%20of%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20or%20some%20other%20pressing%20reason.%20Prior%20to%20the%20August%20session%2C%20the%20Manipur%20assembly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-assembly-monsoon-session-anusuiya-uikey%5C%22%3Ehad%20met%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20first%20week%20of%20March%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20too%2C%20in%20order%20to%20keep%20Manipur%20out%20of%20the%20President%E2%80%99s%20Rule%2C%20a%20session%20had%20to%20be%20held%20within%20the%20last%20week%20of%20February.%20As%20per%20the%20Speaker%E2%80%99s%20announcement%2C%20the%20winter%20session%20will%20go%20on%20until%20March%205.%20It%E2%80%99ll%20have%20a%20total%20number%20of%20five%20sittings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20only%20one%20Kuki%20MLA%20has%20written%20to%20the%20Speaker%20seeking%20leave%20of%20absence%20from%20the%20session%2C%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20nine%20MLAs%20from%20the%20community%2C%20too%2C%20are%20likely%20to%20skip%20it.%20The%20MLA%20who%20has%20written%20to%20the%20Speaker%20a%20day%20before%20the%20session%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifp.co.in%2Fmanipur%2Fmanipur-one-kuki-mla-seeks-leave%5C%22%3EHaokholet%20Kipgen%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20represents%20the%20Kuki-dominated%20Saitu%20constituency%20in%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20Kangpokpi%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20yet%20clear%20how%20many%20among%20the%2010%20Naga%20MLAs%20will%20attend%20the%20current%20session.%20On%20February%2023%2C%20an%20informal%20meeting%20of%20the%20Kuki%20and%20Naga%20MLAs%20had%20taken%20place%20in%20Guwahati.%20Since%20it%20was%20a%20closed%20door%20meeting%2C%20it%20is%20not%20clear%20yet%20what%20exactly%20was%20discussed%20in%20it.%20However%2C%20a%20Kuki%20leader%2C%20speaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity%2C%20said%20attempts%20were%20made%20by%20some%20Naga%20leaders%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20the%20Centre%20to%20break%20the%20ice%20between%20the%20Kuki%20legislators%20and%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20so%20that%20they%20attend%20the%20current%20session%20and%20also%20help%20find%20a%20solution%20to%20the%20ongoing%20Manipur%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20a%20Kuki%20MLA%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20Paolienlal%20Haokip%2C%20got%20angry%20as%20the%20meeting%20was%20not%20to%20take%20%3Cem%3E(sic)%3C%2Fem%3E%20any%20concrete%20decision%20on%20a%20separate%20administration%20for%20the%20Kukis%2C%20and%20he%20eventually%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20meeting%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20person%20cited%20above.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20earlier%20assembly%20session%2C%20Haokip%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmanipur-as-violence-rages-on-mlas-divided-over-whether-or-not-to-hold-special-assembly-session%5C%22%3Ehad%20told%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWho%20would%20give%20assurance%20of%20safety%20and%20security%20of%20the%20Kuki%20MLAs%20going%20to%20Imphal%20to%20attend%20the%20assembly%20session%3F%20At%20this%20point%2C%20I%20would%20say%20it%20is%20not%20possible%20and%20also%20not%20necessary%20to%20participate%20in%20it%20as%20the%20separation%20of%20the%20state%20is%20complete.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3ESangai%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20soon%20after%20the%20February%2023%20Guwahati%20meeting%2C%20a%20Naga%20MLA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesangaiexpress.com%2FEncyc%2F2024%2F2%2F24%2FBy-Our-Staff-ReporterIMPHAL-Feb-23-With-the-fifth-session-of-the-12th-State-Legislative-Assembly-set-to-b.html%5C%22%3Ehad%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CChief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20has%20knowledge%20of%20them%20(the%20Naga%20MLAs)%20attending%20the%20meeting.%20%3Cem%3E(sic)%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20coinciding%20with%20the%20start%20of%20the%20session%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20powerful%20civil%20society%20group%20from%20the%20Meitei%20community%2C%20COCOMI%2C%20or%20the%20Coordinating%20Committee%20on%20Manipur%20Integrity%2C%20has%20asked%20all%20women%20groups%20of%20the%20valley%20areas%20to%20stage%20a%20protest%20for%20an%20hour%20during%20the%20day%20in%20their%20locality%2C%20and%20to%20wear%20red%20outfits%20and%20carry%20out%20a%20torch%20rally%20each%20in%20the%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20COCOMI%20protest%20is%20aimed%20at%20pushing%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20(MHA)%20to%20not%20renew%20the%20suspension%20of%20operation%20agreement%20with%20the%20Kuki%20armed%20groups.%20On%20February%2029%2C%20the%20six-month%20extension%20of%20the%20ceasefire%20with%20the%20Kuki%20groups%20will%20come%20up%20for%20an%20extension%20with%20the%20MHA.%20The%20Biren%20Singh%20government%20has%20already%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20ceasefire%20last%20year%2C%20weeks%20before%20the%20ethnic%20strife%20unfolded%20between%20the%20Meiteis%20and%20the%20Kukis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECOCOMI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifp.co.in%2Fmanipur%2Fcocomi-proposes-protests-in-keithels%5C%22%3Ehas%20also%20submitted%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20memorandum%20to%20the%20MHA%20seeking%20an%20end%20to%20the%20extension%20of%20the%20ceasefire%20agreement%20with%20the%20Kuki%20groups.%20Note%20that%20the%20Centre%20is%20in%20peace%20talks%20with%20the%20Kuki%20groups.%20The%20argument%20of%20the%20Meitei%20group%20has%20been%20that%20Kuki%20militants%20have%20been%20breaking%20the%20suspension%20of%20operation%20agreement%20and%20taking%20part%20in%20the%20ethnic%20fight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20last%20week%E2%80%99s%20arson%20at%20various%20offices%20of%20civil%20society%20groups%20in%20Imphal%2C%20the%20COCOMI%20office%20was%20also%20torched.%20Calling%20the%20incidents%20unfortunate%2C%20COCOMI%20coordinator%20Somorendra%20Thokchom%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesangaiexpress.com%2FEncyc%2F2024%2F2%2F28%2FBy-Our-Staff-ReporterIMPHAL-Feb-27-With-Assembly-session-all-set-to-begin-the-Coordinating-Committee-on.html%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20reporters%20in%20Imphal%2C%20on%20February%2027%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20more%20disappointing%20is%20that%20no%20one%20has%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20the%20series%20of%20attacks%20(one%20journalist%20was%20also%20attacked)%20and%20the%20complete%20silence%20of%20the%20government%20over%20the%20matter.%E2%80%9D%20He%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%202%2C470%20affidavits%20gathered%20by%20COCOMI%20in%20connection%20with%20Manipur%20violence%20were%20also%20gutted%20in%20the%20fire.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709108098000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F07195859%2Fmanipur_assembly_session_2_20150625_1176793276.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-assembly-session-begins-amid-tight-security-previous-session-had-lasted-11-minutes%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20is%20the%20second%20time%20the%20House%20has%20met%20since%20ethnic%20violence%20broke%20out%20in%20the%20north-eastern%20state%20in%20May%20last%20year.%20The%20previous%20session%20was%20held%20on%20August%2029%2C%202023.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-assembly-session-begins-amid-tight-security-previous-session-had-lasted-11-minutes%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elephant%20spins%20tourist%20around%20before%20slamming%20her%20to%20ground%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709107440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F02%2F70x70%2Fskynews-india-jaipur-elephant_6471869.jpg%3F20240228104054%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Ftourists-leg-broken-after-elephant-attack-13082708%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20tourist%20had%20her%20leg%20broken%20after%20being%20grabbed%20by%20an%20elephant%20and%20slammed%20to%20the%20ground.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A109%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Ftourists-leg-broken-after-elephant-attack-13082708%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Ftourists-leg-broken-after-elephant-attack-13082708%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Ftourists-leg-broken-after-elephant-attack-13082708%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Danger%20of%20Reading%20Too%20Much%20Into%20IQ%20Tests%20and%20the%20Crucial%20Cognitive%20Skills%20They%20Don%E2%80%99t%26nbsp%3BMeasure%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F28131036%2F1636530118phpWsuZ5B.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20people%20object%20to%20intelligence%20tests.%20Some%20say%20IQ%20test%20scores%20are%20too%20often%20abused.%20They%20says%20it%E2%80%99s%20unfair%20that%20when%20children%20%E2%80%9Cfail%E2%80%9D%20these%20tests%20it%20can%20mean%20they%20receive%20a%20worse%20secondary%20education%20than%20their%20more%20successful%20peers%20%E2%80%93%20sentencing%20them%20to%20a%20lifetime%20of%20disadvantage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20object%20to%20IQ%20tests%20for%20quite%20personal%20reasons%20and%20remember%20how%20stressed%20they%20were%20by%20sitting%20a%20test.%20Many%20doubt%20their%20result%20was%20a%20fair%20reflection%20of%20their%20future%20potential.%20But%20how%20useful%20are%20IQ%20tests%20really%20%E2%80%93%20and%20what%20skills%20and%20qualities%20do%20they%20miss%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%2030%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20discovered%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhomepages.abdn.ac.uk%2Fj.crawford%2Fpages%2Fdept%2Fpdfs%2FIntelligence_2000_Stability_IQ.pdf%5C%22%3Ehalf-forgotten%2C%20unique%20archive%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20more%20than%2089%2C000%20IQ-type%20tests%20from%201932.%20This%20comprised%20a%20near-complete%20national%20sample%20of%20Scottish%20children%20born%20in%201921%20who%20%E2%80%93%20at%20the%20time%20%E2%80%93%20would%20have%20been%20about%2076%20years%20old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20aim%20was%20simple%3A%20to%20find%20local%20people%20to%20match%20with%20the%20archive%20and%20compare%20their%20current%20mental%20ability%20with%20their%20test%20result%20from%201932.%20A%20picture%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdoi.org%2F10.1136%2Fbmj.322.7290.819%5C%22%3Equickly%20emerged%3C%2Fa%3E%20linking%20lower%20IQ%20scores%20with%20earlier%20than%20expected%20age%20at%20death%20and%20earlier%20onset%20dementia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20world%20war%20yielded%20some%20strong%20unexpected%20anomalies.%20Young%20men%20with%20higher%20childhood%20IQ%20scores%20more%20often%20died%20on%20active%20service.%20Girls%20with%20higher%20scores%20more%20often%20moved%20away%20from%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20cycled%20around%20Aberdeen%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20its%20social%20history%2C%20becoming%20familiar%20with%20the%20primary%20schools%20where%20the%20children%20had%20sat%20their%20tests%20in%201932.%20Average%20IQ%20scores%20often%20differed%20substantially%20between%20schools.%20Those%20pupils%20attending%20schools%20in%20overcrowded%20districts%20tended%20to%20perform%20less%20well%20on%20the%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20later%20research%20showed%20that%20people%20with%20higher%20IQ%20were%20engaging%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bmj.com%2Fcontent%2F363%2Fbmj.k4925%5C%22%3Emore%20intellectually%20stimulating%20activities%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20such%20as%20reading%20complex%20novels%20or%20learning%20musical%20instruments.%20But%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20know%20whether%20having%20a%20high%20IQ%20leads%20people%20to%20seek%20out%20such%20activities%20or%20whether%20intellectually%20curious%20people%20develop%20higher%20IQ%20because%20they%20engage%20in%20cognitively%20complex%20tasks%20throughout%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20that%E2%80%99s%20an%20important%20question.%20People%20from%20poorer%20backgrounds%2C%20such%20as%20the%20disadvantaged%20neighbourhoods%20in%20the%20city%20of%20Aberdeen%2C%20may%20not%20have%20the%20opportunity%20to%20pursue%20intellectual%20interests%20due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20time%20and%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20better%20inform%20my%20work%2C%20I%20sought%20out%20local%20residents%20with%20long%20experience%20of%20teaching%20in%20Aberdeen.%20Their%20views%20were%20echoed%20by%20current%20workers%20in%20public%20health%20and%20psychology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeachers%20warned%20me%20not%20to%20forget%20that%20IQ%20tests%20have%20been%20used%20over%20the%20years%20to%20advance%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvia.library.depaul.edu%2Fcgi%2Fviewcontent.cgi%3Farticle%3D1270%26context%3Dlaw-review%5C%22%3Escientific%20racism%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20that%20they%20feared%20that%20before%20too%20long%2C%20right-wing%20advocates%20of%20IQ%20testing%20would%20want%20to%20use%20these%20rediscovered%20Scottish%20data%20to%20search%20for%20the%20genetic%20basis%20of%20intelligence.%20Alarmed%20and%20now%20forewarned%2C%20I%20looked%20back%20at%20the%20reasons%20for%20undertaking%20the%201932%20survey%20of%20the%20mental%20ability%20of%20Scottish%20schoolchildren.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20was%20funded%20by%20the%20Eugenics%20Society%20(eugenics%20is%20the%20science%20of%20improving%20the%20human%20race%20through%20the%20selection%20of%20%E2%80%9Cgood%E2%80%9D%20hereditary%20traits)%20with%20some%20help%20from%20the%20Rockefeller%20Foundation.%20Their%20shared%20priority%20was%20to%20show%20a%20link%20between%20large%20family%20size%20and%20below%20average%20mental%20ability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20this%20negative%20relationship%20between%20a%20mothers%E2%80%99%20IQ%20and%20having%20children%20was%20easy%20to%20show.%20But%20post-1945%20educational%20reforms%2C%20which%20led%20to%20more%20girls%20completing%20higher%20education%2C%20produced%20much%20more%20complex%20relationships%20between%20maternal%20IQ%2C%20educational%20achievements%2C%20age%20at%20first%20childbirth%20and%20lifetime%20fertility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20fed%20into%20contemporary%20public%20concerns%20that%20the%20average%20mental%20ability%20of%20the%20general%20population%20was%20lowered%20by%20the%20loss%20of%20so%20many%20young%20men%20of%20presumed%20above%20average%20ability%20during%20the%20first%20world%20war%20war.%20Newspapers%20argued%20that%20schoolboys%20would%20need%20to%20be%20assessed%20and%20selected%20to%20better%20educate%20those%20most%20likely%20to%20benefit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20only%20goes%20to%20show%20that%20while%20IQ%20tests%20can%20tell%20us%20something%20about%20academic%20success%20or%20dementia%20risk%2C%20they%20miss%20a%20lot%20of%20a%20nuance.%20There%E2%80%99s%20no%20denying%20they%20have%20long%20been%20used%20for%20murky%20reasons%20%E2%80%93%20often%20as%20an%20excuse%20to%20direct%20less%20funding%20to%20certain%20types%20of%20school%2C%20thereby%20creating%20a%20two-tier%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20majority%20of%20children%2C%20those%20who%20do%20not%20take%20or%20pass%20IQ-style%20entrance%20exams%20to%20private%20or%20grammar%20schools%2C%20will%20have%20many%20qualities%20not%20measured%20on%20an%20IQ%20test.%20They%20may%20also%20just%20be%20late%20developers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20IQ%20tests%20don%E2%80%99t%20measure%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20do%20IQ%20tests%20miss%3F%20Research%20suggests%20that%20IQ%20scores%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fiq-tests-are-humans-getting-smarter-158837%5C%22%3Erose%20by%20about%203%20points%20per%20decade%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20much%20of%20the%2020th%20century%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpsycnet.apa.org%2Frecord%2F2012-26835-000%5C%22%3Emay%20have%20dropped%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20past%2030%20years%20or%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20experts%20argue%20this%20reflects%20changes%20in%20the%20school%20curriculum%20or%20maybe%20just%20the%20complexity%20of%20modern%20life.%20The%20acquisition%20of%20%E2%80%9Ccontent%20knowledge%E2%80%9D%20(reading%20and%20memorising)%20once%20formed%20a%20cornerstone%20of%20public%20examinations%20and%20is%20related%20to%20IQ%20test%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20know%20for%20example%20that%20working%20memory%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fabs%2Fpii%2FS1041608002000493%5C%22%3Eis%20related%20to%3C%2Fa%3E%20IQ%20test%20performance.%20But%20research%20has%20since%20uncovered%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdoi.org%2F10.1111%2Fj.1467-9280.2005.01641.x%5C%22%3Eself-discipline%20is%20actually%20better%20predictor%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20exam%20results%20than%20IQ.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENowadays%2C%20children%20in%20the%20west%20are%20taught%20collective%20scientific%20problem-solving%2C%20combined%20with%20interpersonal%20skills%20and%20teamwork%2C%20which%20requires%20less%20memorisation%20(rote%20learning).%20This%20may%20actually%20make%20students%20less%20likely%20to%20score%20highly%20on%20IQ%20tests%2C%20even%20though%20these%20methods%20are%20helping%20humanity%20as%20a%20whole%20get%20smarter.%20Knowledge%20keeps%20growing%2C%20often%20as%20a%20result%20of%20giant%20research%20collaborations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20type%20of%20%E2%80%9Cprocedural%20learning%E2%80%9D%20leads%20to%20mature%20self-awareness%2C%20emotional%20stability%2C%20recognition%20of%20the%20thoughts%20and%20feelings%20of%20others%20and%20an%20understanding%20of%20an%20individual%E2%80%99s%20impact%20on%20the%20performance%20of%20a%20group.%20Critically%2C%20a%20lack%20of%20these%20skills%20can%20hinder%20rational%20thinking.%20Research%20shows%20that%20when%20we%20ignore%20or%20fail%20to%20understand%20our%20feelings%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Foro.open.ac.uk%2F31984%2F%23%3A%257E%3Atext%3DWe%2520conclude%2520that%2520emotions%2520and%2Cfor%2520trader%2520behavior%2520and%2520performance.%5C%22%3Ewe%20are%20more%20easily%20manipulated%20by%20them%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHigh%20IQ%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20necessarily%20protect%20against%20bias%20or%20error%20either.%20In%20fact%2C%20research%20shows%20that%20people%20with%20high%20IQ%20can%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thetimes.co.uk%2Farticle%2Freview-the-intelligence-trap-why-smart-people-do-stupid-things-and-how-to-make-wiser-decisions-by-david-robson-impressive-and-readable-tgr72mshs%2F%5C%22%3Eparticularly%20vulnerable%20to%20mistakes%3C%2Fa%3E%20such%20as%20spotting%20patterns%20even%20when%20there%20aren%E2%80%99t%20any%2C%20or%20they%20are%20irrelevant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20may%20lead%20to%20confirmation%20bias%20and%20difficulty%20giving%20up%20on%20an%20idea%2C%20solution%20or%20project%20even%20when%20it%20is%20no%20longer%20working.%20This%20can%20also%20get%20in%20the%20way%20of%20rational%20reasoning.%20But%20such%20weaknesses%20are%20missed%20by%20IQ%20testing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(min-width%3A%201466px)%20754px%2C%20(max-width%3A%20599px)%20100vw%2C%20(min-width%3A%20600px)%20600px%2C%20237px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fimages.theconversation.com%2Ffiles%2F577001%2Foriginal%2Ffile-20240221-30-nfj86z.jpg%3Fixlib%3Drb-1.1.0%26q%3D45%26auto%3Dformat%26w%3D237%26fit%3Dclip%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Image%20of%20Albert%20Einstein.%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22353%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fimages.theconversation.com%2Ffiles%2F577001%2Foriginal%2Ffile-20240221-30-nfj86z.jpg%3Fixlib%3Drb-1.1.0%26amp%3Bq%3D45%26amp%3Bauto%3Dformat%26amp%3Bw%3D600%26amp%3Bh%3D800%26amp%3Bfit%3Dcrop%26amp%3Bdpr%3D1%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fimages.theconversation.com%2Ffiles%2F577001%2F