99929937.cms%5C%22%3Especulating%20about%20his%20IQ%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Yet%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.weforum.org%2Fagenda%2F2019%2F08%2Falbert-einstein-quotes-inspiring-clever-funny-famous%2F%23%3A%257E%3Atext%3D%25E2%2580%259CThe%2520important%2520thing%2520is%2520not%2Cof%2520this%2520mystery%2520every%2520day.%25E2%2580%259D%5C%22%3Eoften%20credited%20curiosity%20and%20intuition%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20core%20driving%20forces%20of%20scientific%20success%20%E2%80%93%20and%20these%20are%20not%20qualities%20measured%20by%20an%20IQ%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ethos%20of%20a%20modern%20school%20is%20rightly%20not%20driven%20by%20a%20preference%20to%20educate%20only%20those%20children%20who%20on%20selection%20meet%20a%20minimum%20standard%20on%20a%20mental%20test.%20Schools%20acknowledge%20that%20educational%20outcomes%20are%20not%20determined%20solely%20by%20any%20innate%20ability%20but%20are%20equally%20affected%20by%20all%20prior%20experiences%20that%20affect%20emotional%20competences%2C%20motivation%2C%20intellectual%20curiosity%2C%20insightfulness%20and%20intuitive%20reasoning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20local%20participants%20in%20the%201932%20survey%20were%20interviewed%20in%20late%20life%2C%20they%20spoke%20warmly%20of%20their%20schooldays%20%E2%80%93%20particularly%20about%20friendships.%20They%20rarely%20mentioned%20their%20education%20though.%20The%20learning%20of%20content%20knowledge%2C%20with%20threats%20of%20physical%20punishments%2C%20simply%20weren%E2%80%99t%20well%20regarded.%20Some%20remembered%20sitting%20the%20IQ%20test%20in%201932%20and%20were%20pleased%20most%20schools%20no%20longer%20test%20children%20that%20way.%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Conversation%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcounter.theconversation.com%2Fcontent%2F223570%2Fcount.gif%3Fdistributor%3Drepublish-lightbox-basic%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fprofiles%2Flawrence-whalley-615876%5C%22%3ELawrence%20Whalley%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Emeritus%20Professor%20of%20Mental%20Health%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Finstitutions%2Funiversity-of-aberdeen-962%5C%22%3EUniversity%20of%20Aberdeen%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20republished%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%5C%22%3EThe%20Conversation%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20a%20Creative%20Commons%20license.%20Read%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fiq-tests-the-danger-of-reading-too-much-into-them-and-the-crucial-cognitive-skills-they-dont-measure-223570%5C%22%3Eoriginal%20article%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709107334000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F28131036%2F1636530118phpWsuZ5B.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fscience%2Fthe-danger-of-reading-too-much-into-iq-tests-and-the-crucial-cognitive-skills-they-dont-measure%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Many%20great%20leaps%20in%20human%20ingenuity%20were%20driven%20by%20creativity%2C%20collaboration%2C%20intuition%20or%20curiosity%20rather%20than%20just%20individual%20IQ.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fscience%2Fthe-danger-of-reading-too-much-into-iq-tests-and-the-crucial-cognitive-skills-they-dont-measure%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22JP%20Morgan%20Executive%20Alleges%20Caste%20Discrimination%20in%20Gujarat%20Housing%20Complex%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F28124724%2FScreenshot-2024-02-28-at-12.47.13-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EA%20robust%20business%20district%20with%20vast%20acres%20of%20commercial%20and%20residential%20spaces%2C%20the%20Gift%20City%20is%20rapidly%20consolidating%20its%20position%20as%20a%20powerhouse%20of%20financial%20and%20IT%20services.%20Its%20cutting-edge%20infrastructure%20continues%20to%20attract%20numerous%20startups.%20What%20furthers%20the%20Gift%20City%E2%80%99s%20allure%20is%20the%20job%20boom%20it%20promises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20vision%20made%20a%20vice-president%20of%20JP%20Morgan%2C%20Anirudh%20Kejriwal%2C%20choose%20Gujarat%20over%20Singapore%20when%20he%20got%20an%20opportunity.%20Originally%20from%20Rajasthan%2C%20Anirudh%20has%20graduated%20from%20IIT%20Guwahati.%20He%20was%20born%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20this%20pan-national%20exposure%20makes%20him%20a%20true%20Indian%20exposed%20to%20different%20cultures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnirudh%20decided%20to%20buy%20a%20house%20near%20Koba%20in%20Gandhinagar%20which%20is%20close%20to%20GIFT%20city%20from%20where%20he%20has%20been%20functioning%20for%20about%20three%20months.%20%E2%80%9C%20I%20zeroed%20in%20on%20a%20house%20that%20I%20like%20at%20Sant%20Vihar%20I%20society.%20The%20house%20was%20going%20to%20cost%20me%20Rs%2070%20lacs.%20I%20gave%20Rs%2035%20lacs%20via%20a%20cheque%20to%20the%20house%20owner%2C%20Baldevbhai%20Patel%20from%20whom%20I%20was%20going%20to%20buy%20the%20house%20in%20a%20resale%20deed%E2%80%9D%2C%20Anirudh%20told%20%3Cem%3EVibes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20house%20owner%20kept%20on%20delaying%20giving%20him%20the%20No%20Objection%20Certificate%20(NOC).%20According%20to%20Anirudh%2C%20the%20society%20which%20has%20a%20majority%20of%20Patels%20did%20not%20want%20a%20non%20Gujarati%20with%20the%20surname%20Kejriwal%20buying%20a%20house.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20a%20Hindu%3B%20I%20am%20a%20vegetarian%2C%20I%20told%20him%E2%80%9D%2C%20Anirudh%20added%2C%20saying%20that%20he%20was%20discriminated%20against%20by%20the%20housing%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnirudh%20took%20to%20X%20to%20express%20his%20anguish.%20He%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20living%20in%20Mumbai%20for%20years%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20move%20to%20Gujarat%2C%20choosing%20it%20over%20an%20opportunity%20in%20Singapore.%20I%20was%20captivated%20by%20the%20promise%20of%20GIFT%20City%20and%20the%20grand%20vision%20our%20prime%20minister%20and%20government%20laid%20out%20for%20us.%20It%20inspired%20me%20so%20much%20that%20I%20took%20a%20big%20step%20and%20decided%20to%20buy%20my%20first%20house%20here%2C%20dreaming%20of%20a%20future%20filled%20with%20hope%20and%20growth.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20facing%20unexpected%20challenges%20with%20my%20dream%20home%2C%20barred%20from%20moving%20in%2C%20not%20because%20of%20anything%20I%20have%20done%2C%20but%20because%20I%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20born%20Gujarati.%20Worse%20yet%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20warned%20that%20even%20if%20I%20manage%20to%20get%20in%2C%20happiness%20will%20be%20out%20of%20reach%2C%20and%20troubles%20will%20follow.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20bitter%20pill%20to%20swallow.%20Choosing%20Gujarat%2C%20leaving%20behind%20my%20life%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20the%20chance%20to%20move%20to%20Singapore%2C%20I%20never%20thought%20I%E2%80%99d%20face%20such%20discrimination.%20This%20experience%20has%20been%20nothing%20short%20of%20a%20nightmare.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Anirudh%2C%20it%20is%20because%20of%20his%20caste%20and%20community%20that%20he%20is%20being%20discriminated%20against.%20Anirudh%20said%20he%20is%20seeking%20legal%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Flets-talk-about-housing-discrimination%5C%22%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20Talk%20About%20Housing%20Discrimination%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20%3Cem%3EVibes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20visited%20Sant%20Vihar%20Society%20and%20though%20the%20majority%20of%20residents%20are%20indeed%20Patels%2C%20there%20are%20few%20others%20also%20who%20have%20purchased%20houses.%20There%20are%2092%20flats%20in%20the%20complex.%20The%20society%20chairman%2C%20Laljibhai%20Patel%20claimed%20that%20this%20was%20not%20an%20issue%20of%20caste%20or%20community%20discrimination%20but%20some%20personal%20problem%20between%20the%20house%20owner%20and%20the%20buyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnirudh%20maintains%20that%20he%20has%20been%20barred%20from%20buying%20the%20flat%20because%20of%20%E2%80%9Cbeing%20a%20Kejriwal%E2%80%9D.%20His%20fault%3F%20He%20was%20a%20Mumbai-kar%2C%20not%20a%20born%20Gujarati.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20situation%20escalated%20quickly%20with%20nearly%2030%20people%20gathering%2C%20threatening%20me%20with%20dire%20consequences%20if%20I%20proceeded%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kejriwal%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Kejriwal%20is%20determined%20to%20reclaim%20his%20rights%20and%20even%20pursue%20legal%20options%20if%20necessary.%20%E2%80%9CAll%20my%20preparations%2C%20from%20financial%20investments%20to%20personal%20arrangements%2C%20are%20now%20in%20jeopardy%20due%20to%20this%20discrimination.%20The%20vision%20of%20an%20inclusive%20India%20feels%20tarnished%20in%20the%20very%20state%20leading%20India%E2%80%99s%20development%20narrative%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESympathies%20poured%20in%20on%20social%20media%2C%20with%20one%20user%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20not%20surprised%2C%20despite%20all%20the%20claims%20of%20modernity%20the%20thinking%20of%20many%20people%20here%20is%20extremely%20backward.%20Caste-based%20discrimination%20is%20rampant%20in%20the%20real%20estate%20market%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20user%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6This%20is%20one%20of%20the%20sad%20realities%20of%20staying%20in%20Gujarat!%20Hope%20you%20and%20your%20family%20are%20fine!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EVibes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20contacted%20Baldevbhai%20Patel%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20house.%20He%20admitted%20that%20Anirudh%20Kejriwal%20has%20given%20him%20a%20cheque%20of%20Rs%2035%20lacs.%20%E2%80%9CI%20do%20not%20want%20to%20get%20into%20details.%20I%20will%20be%20returning%20his%20amount%20soon.%20I%20will%20not%20be%20selling%20the%20house%E2%