20health%20of%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELearning%20about%20this%20problem%20prompted%20Rahul%20Arepaka%2C%20an%20engineering%20student%20at%20Mahindra%20University%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20to%20develop%20a%20solution.%20He%20built%20an%20AI-powered%20laser-weeding%20implement%20called%20%E2%80%98Rakshak%E2%80%99%20through%20his%20company%2C%20Harvested%20Robotics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20farmer%20spends%20almost%20Rs%2015%2C000%20for%20weeding%2C%20which%20has%20to%20be%20done%20at%20least%20three%20to%20four%20times%20during%20an%20entire%20season.%20So%20the%20total%20cost%20sums%20up%20to%20almost%20Rs%2060%2C000.%20The%20other%20option%20is%20using%20chemicals%2C%20but%20I%20wanted%20to%20build%20a%20solution%20that%20is%20good%20for%20the%20farmer%20as%20well%20as%20the%20planet%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rahul%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPrecision%20laser%20technology%20to%20kill%20weeds%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20960px)%20100vw%2C%20960px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Frakshak1-min-1709042611.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rakshak%20is%20an%20AI-powered%20laser-weeding%20implement%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Frakshak1-min-1709042611.jpeg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Frakshak1-min-1709042611-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Frakshak1-min-1709042611-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Frakshak1-min-1709042611-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Frakshak1-min-1709042611-640x853.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Frakshak1-min-1709042611-150x200.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343339%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERakshak%20is%20an%20AI-powered%20laser-weeding%20implement%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20%E2%80%94%20who%20is%20now%20in%20the%20final%20year%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329484%2Fbengaluru-engineer-innovates-artificial-intelligence-powered-robot-sprayers-that-reduce-pesticides-costs-for-farmers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecomputer%20science%20engineering%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20participated%20in%20many%20robotics%20competitions%20along%20with%20his%20friends%2C%20including%20the%20World%20Robotics%20Olympiad.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20building%20farming%20robots%20and%20realised%20that%20weeds%20are%20a%20huge%20problem.%20During%20internships%20at%20companies%20like%20FarmBot%2C%20we%20developed%20laser-based%20weed%20elimination%20solutions%20as%20proof%20of%20concept.%20Through%20this%20experience%2C%20I%20identified%20a%20gap%20in%20the%20Indian%20market%20for%20a%20laser%20weeder%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rahul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20using%20chemicals%20or%20hiring%20manual%20labour%2C%20Rahul%20decided%20to%20build%20laser%20technology%20for%20weed%20management.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhat%20started%20as%20a%20brainstorming%20session%20in%20December%202022%20evolved%20into%20a%20concrete%20vision%20within%20a%20few%20months.%20Through%20his%20university%E2%80%99s%20incubation%20programme%2C%20he%20received%20an%20initial%20funding%20of%20Rs%205%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeaming%20up%20with%20three%20friends%2C%20also%20final-year%20engineering%20students%20from%20different%20disciplines%20like%20mechanical%20and%20electronics%2C%20they%20embarked%20on%20developing%20a%20laser%20technology%20to%20combat%20weeds%20in%20June%202023.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOver%20the%20past%208%20months%2C%20they%20have%20received%20a%20total%20investment%20of%20Rs%2018%20lakh%20from%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%20incubation%20centre%20to%20further%20develop%20this%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERakshak%20is%20a%20tractor-mounted%20laser%20weeder%20built%20using%20robotic%20platforms%20that%20utilise%20precision%20laser%20technology%20for%20weed%20eradication%2C%20which%20is%20paired%20with%20individual%20weed%20recognition%20through%20deep%20learning%20algorithms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20are%20some%20players%20globally%20who%20have%20built%20similar%20solutions%2C%20what%20differentiates%20Harvested%20Robotics%20is%20the%20power%20source%20of%20the%20laser%2C%20explains%20Rahul.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20burn%20weeds%20in%20India%2C%20you%20have%20to%20use%20at%20least%20200%20watts%20of%20laser%20source%20to%20burn%20it%20quickly.%20The%20global%20players%20use%20a%201%2C200-watt%20laser%2C%20which%20costs%20them%20%2440%2C000%20just%20for%20the%20laser%20%E2%80%94%20a%20restrictive%20cost.%20These%20lasers%20also%20have%20a%20very%20high%20maintenance%20cost%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2022-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20solve%20this%20problem%2C%20instead%20of%20relying%20on%20one%20big%20power%20source%2C%20Rahul%20and%20the%20team%20used%20a%20bunch%20of%20smaller%20laser%20sources%2C%20which%20they%20combined%20to%20get%20the%20same%20result.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20used%20five%20different%20laser%20sources%20to%20get%20200%20watts%20on%20the%20ground.%20This%20way%2C%20we%20were%20able%20to%20significantly%20reduce%20the%20cost%2C%20while%20ensuring%20even%20power%20distribution%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20it%20works%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fembed%2Ffeed%2Fupdate%2Furn%3Ali%3AugcPost%3A7148330471074975744%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22