0up%2C%20I%20always%20saw%20them%20showing%20kindness%20to%20animals.%20They%20never%20explicitly%20instructed%20me%20to%20be%20kind%20to%20animals.%20It%E2%80%99s%20just%20something%20I%20imbibed%20by%20watching%20them.%20Eventually%2C%20there%20came%20a%20time%20when%20my%20mother%20would%20tell%20me%2C%20%E2%80%98Guddi%2C%20you%20must%20start%20a%20shelter%E2%80%99.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20I%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338562%2Fmumbai-police-cid-first-quadruple-murder-case-indian-sherlock-holmes-vaidyanath-sami%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20Mumbai%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20more%20concerned%20with%20raising%20my%20daughter.%20However%2C%20my%20mother%20would%20keep%20insisting%20that%20I%20should%20start%20an%20animal%20shelter%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Sarah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20moved%20to%20Chennai%20and%20got%20PK%20home%2C%20my%20mother%20was%20very%20happy.%20Also%2C%20since%20I%20had%20more%20time%20for%20myself%20after%20moving%20to%20Chennai%2C%20I%20told%20my%20mother%20that%20I%20would%20think%20about%20opening%20a%20dog%20shelter.%20In%202016%2C%20however%2C%20my%20mother%20suddenly%20passed%20away.%20To%20make%20matters%20worse%2C%20my%20aunt%20also%20passed%20away%20within%20a%20year%20of%20my%20mother%E2%80%99s%20death%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FSnapinsta.app_310794014_474810804702986_2181452240036379895_n_1080-1708958487.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Daaman%20offers%20a%20home%20for%20injured%20and%20abandoned%20dogs.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FSnapinsta.app_310794014_474810804702986_2181452240036379895_n_1080-1708958487.jpg%201080w%2C%20ht