20few%20abandoned%20breeds.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20will%20come%20and%20tie%20their%20Rottweilers%2C%20Labradors%2C%20Great%20Danes%20and%20German%20Shepherds%20to%20the%20gate%20and%20go%20away.%20People%20sometimes%20leave%20a%20cardboard%20box%20with%20five%20newborn%20indie%20puppies%20taken%20away%20from%20their%20mother%20at%20our%20gate%20as%20well.%20Who%20adopts%20them%3F%20Where%20do%20I%20find%20homes%20for%20these%20breeds%3F%20We%E2%80%99ve%20not%20had%20very%20good%20luck%20with%20breeds%20we%20have%20given%20out%20for%20adoption.%20I%20will%20not%20give%20a%20dog%20for%20adoption%20until%20and%20unless%20I%20know%20the%20person%20or%20someone%20recommends%20the%20%E2%80%98dog-parents%E2%80%99%20to%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Sarah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20example%2C%20we%20recently%20had%20one%20Dalmatian%20puppy%20%E2%80%98Simi%E2%80%99%20who%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20a%20hole%20in%20her%20heart%20and%20doctors%20said%20she%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20survive%20this%20condition.%20Thankfully%2C%20she%20has%20been%20with%20us%20for%20about%20eight%20to%20nine%20months%20now.%20Forget%20about%20paying%20us%20for%20her%20upkeep%2C%20the%20people%20who%20dropped%20her%20here%20haven%E2%80%99t%20even%20called%20to%20check%20up%20on%20her%20once.%20We%20are%20so%20busy%2024%2F7%20that%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20chase%20people%20down%20for%20funds.%20The%20need%20to%20create%20and%20maintain%20a%20sizable%20corpus%20of%20funds%20is%20so%20important%20for%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarah%E2%80%99s%20shelter%20also%20gets%20calls%20from%20people%20all%20over%20India%2C%20asking%20her%20whether%20she%20can%20admit%20their%20paraplegic%20dogs.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20from%20Kerala%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Hyderabad%20and%20even%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20call%20us%20to%20ask%20whether%20they%20can%20admit%20paraplegic%20dogs%20into%20our%20shelter%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20