of%20Chennai-based%20Madras%20Animal%20Rescue%20Society%2C%20and%20her%20husband%20Gerry%20run%20a%20shelter%20for%20340%20paraplegic%2C%20disabled%20and%20abandoned%20dogs%20near%20Mahabalipuram.%20They%20need%20your%20help%20to%20keep%20this%20shelter%20running.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Rinchen%20Norbu%20Wangchuk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A31%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F343165%2Fchennai-street-dogs-shelter-for-paraplegic-abandoned-disabled-sarah-iyer-madras-animal-rescue-society%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Born%20Out%20of%20a%20Mom%E2%80%99s%20Mission%20To%20Build%20a%20Toxin-Free%20Home%2C%20This%20Brand%20Earns%20Her%20Rs%203%20Crore%2FMonth%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20turn%20back%20the%20clock%2C%20approximately%20three%20years.%20On%2022%20March%2C%202020%2C%20India%20entered%20its%20first%20pandemic-induced%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F261522%2Fquarantine-home-baker-noida-cakes-breads-shweta-joshi-youtube%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elockdown%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20restricting%20us%20all%20to%20our%20homes.%20It%20was%20a%20period%20when%20families%20came%20together%20to%20cook%2C%20clean%2C%20and%20tackle%20household%20chores%20collectively.%20Even%20the%20children%2C%20with%20their%20newfound%20time%20at%20home%2C%20lent%20a%20helping%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20similar%20scene%20unfolded%20at%20Simran%20Khara%E2%80%99s%20house%20in%20Delhi.%20The%2042-year-old%2C%20along%20with%20her%20husband%20and%20their%20then%20five-year-old%20daughter%2C%20spent%20much%20of%20their%20time%20on%20household%20chores.%20After%20a%20few%20days%2C%20Simran%20started%20studying%20the%20labels%20of%20the%20dishwashing%20and%20floor%20cleaning%20products%20she%20was%20using%20at%20home.%20She%20recognised%20the%20presence%20of%20harmful%20chemicals%20in%20these%20cleaners%2C%20which%20posed%20risks%20to%20her%20daughter%20and%20even%20the%20surfaces%20they%20cleaned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20longer%20at%20ease%20with%20her%20daughter%20participating%20in%20cleaning%20activities%20due%20to%20the%20potential%20exposure%20to%20these%20toxic%20chemicals%2C%20Simran%2C%20a%20concerned%20mother%20%E2%80%94%20and%20an%20MBA%20graduate%20with%2014%20years%20of%20corporate%20experience%20%E2%80%94%20resolved%20to%20develop%20a%20line%20of%20eco-friendly%20home%20cleaners%20that%20would%20prioritise%20child%20and%20pet%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20months%20of%20research%2C%20Simran%20Khara%2C%20the%20former%20CEO%20of%20Juggernaut%20Books%2C%20launched%20Koparo%20Clean%20in%20February%202021.%20Koparo%20Clean%20is%20a%20home-care%20product%20brandboasting%20of%20%E2%80%9Cnatural%E2%80%9D%20formulations%20crafted%20from%20plant-based%20ingredients%20such%20as%20coconuts%20(%3Cem%3Ekopra%3C%2Fem%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20entrepreneurial%20journey%20gained%20national%20attention%20when%20she%20appeared%20on%20Shark%20Tank%20Season%203%2C%20where%20she%20secured%20a%20substantial%20investment%20of%20Rs%2070%20lakh%20from%20%E2%80%98Sharks%E2%80%99%20Vineeta%20Singh%20and%20Aman%20Gupta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIn%20search%20of%20a%20toxin-free%20cleaning%20product%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201067px)%20100vw%2C%201067px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkoparo-1708954181.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221067%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Simran%20started%20Koparo%20as%20she%20wanted%20her%20daughter%20to%20be%20exposed%20to%20toxin-free%20cleaners%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkoparo-1708954181.jpeg%201067w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkoparo-1708954181-200x300.jpeg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-med