a.com%2F63445%2Fhearing-impairments-balavidyalaya-school-chennai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebenefit%20from%20hearing%20aids%3C%2Fa%3E.%20For%20those%20with%20profound%20hearing%20loss%2C%20Cochlear%20Implants%20(CI)%20offer%20a%20solution.%20These%20electronic%20devices%20serve%20to%20replace%20the%20function%20of%20the%20damaged%20inner%20ear%2C%20facilitating%20the%20sense%20of%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20enables%20children%20to%20engage%20with%20the%20auditory%20world%20and%20lead%20lives%20similar%20to%20other%20children%20in%20every%20aspect.%20However%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20Cochlear%20Implant%20(CI)%20surgery%20is%20expensive%20for%20a%20large%20portion%20of%20the%20population%20in%20India.%20To%20assist%20children%20in%20regaining%20their%20hearing%20abilities%20and%20leading%20fulfilling%20lives%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F341889%2Fhans-foundation-bal-aarogya-karyakram-childhood-cancer-paediatric-oncology-leukaemia-lymphoma%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Hans%20Foundation%20%3C%2Fa%3E(THF)%20runs%20the%20Cochlear%20Implant%20Programme.%20Through%20this%20initiative%2C%20they%20have%20already%20helped%20over%20900%20children%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20two-hour%20surgery%20that%20can%20change%20lives%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202560px)%20100vw%2C%202560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG_1342-min-1708783870-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Hans%20Foundation%20(THF)%20has%20helped%20over%20900%20children%20with%20its%20Cochlear%20Implant%20Programme.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG_1342-min-1708783870-scaled.jpg%202560w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com