%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVivek%20was%20recently%20recognised%20for%20his%20remarkable%20efforts%20to%20transform%20the%20Chandrapur%20district.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20this%2C%20we%20have%20utilised%20MGNREGA%20and%20Swachh%20Bharat%20Abhiyan%20funds.%20We%20used%20the%20amount%20for%20basic%20leveling%20of%20the%20ground%2C%20installing%20LED%20lights%2C%20setting%20up%20toilets%20and%20recreational%20rooms%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20received%20good%20feedback%20on%20the%20complexes%20as%20they%20are%20built%20near%20the%20schools.%20Many%20students%20have%20started%20playing%20basketball%20and%20volleyball%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20their%20lives.%20A%20large%20number%20of%20these%20tribal%20students%20did%20not%20even%20know%20the%20names%20of%20these%20sports%20initially%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20they%20are%20preparing%20for%20the%20Khelo%20Chand%20Fit%20India%20competition%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20all%2C%20the%20district%20utilised%20at%20least%20Rs%2025%20lakhs%20to%20prepare%20each%20playground.%20It%20is%20estimated%20that%20at%20least%2010%2C000%20rural%20students%20are%20availing%20these%20sports%20complexes%20and%20open%20science%20parks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20his%20remarkable%20works%2C%20the%20IAS%20officer%20was%20recently%20awarded%20the%20Bal%20Snehi%20Award%20from%20the%20Integrated%20Child%20Development%20Services%20(ICDS)%20department%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20at%20the%20district%E2%80%99s%20transformation%2C%20Vivek%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20inspired%20to%20become%20an%20IAS%20officer%20in%20college%20as%20the%20canvas%20of%20this%20role%20is%20really%20big.%20We%20can%20change%20people%E2%80%99s%20lives.%20It%20is%20extremely%20satisfying%20to%20see%20that%20today%2C%20I%20am%20actually%20able%20to%20see%20that